T02TD1676E:216b-1: tsa tur t'am g'artha a'a lo ka n'a ma /
T02TD1676E:216b-3: yan lag bzhi'i don snang bar byed pa zhes bya ba /
T02TD1676E:216b-4: bcom ldan 'das ngang la rdo rje 'dzin pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1676E:216b-5: mkha' mnyam gsal ba gnyis med pa'i //
T02TD1676E:216b-6: yon tan rin chen sna tshogs gzhi //
T02TD1676E:216b-7: thams cad rang bzhin bde chen sku //
T02TD1676E:216b-8: bkod pa kun snang rol ston 'dud //
T02TD1676E:216b-9: bstan pa'i snying po dri med bka' //
T02TD1676E:216b-10: gsang don gsang ba kun gyi mchog / bsdu zhing de ngon gsal mdzad pa'i //
T02TD1676E:216b-11: mchog rnams kun la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1676E:216b-12: dpal ldan bde mchog rgyud dag las //
T02TD1676E:216b-13: rim 'jug sgrub chen don bkod pa'i //
T02TD1676E:216b-14: tshig don rtogs dka'i rim pa dag / rnam gsum dgu yi gzhung gsal phyir //
T02TD1676E:216b-15: bsnyen sgrub cho ga'i rim rgyas par //
T02TD1676E:217a-2: dam pa'i rjes 'brangs mtha' gnyis bsal //
T02TD1676E:217a-3: gzhung bral 'khrul sogs dgag phyir bshad //
T02TD1676E:217a-4: bskal pa bye ba grangs med par //
T02TD1676E:217a-5: sangs rgyas thams cad ma thob pa //
T02TD1676E:217a-6: phyag rgya'i cho ga gang dag gis //
T02TD1676E:217a-8: de ni bdag gis brtag par bya //
T02TD1676E:217a-9: sangs rgyas kun dag bde ba'i mchog //
T02TD1676E:217a-10: bdag nyid bzhin du bsgrubs pa las //
T02TD1676E:217a-11: sangs rgyas kun dag bde mchog go //
T02TD1676E:217a-12: rnal 'byor yang dag ma yin sems //
T02TD1676E:217a-13: lha la dmigs par byed pa dag / rnal 'byor gzugs brnyan rang bzhin te //
T02TD1676E:217a-14: lugs ma la sogs rnal 'byor skye //
T02TD1676E:217a-15: yang dag mchog sems rnal 'byor pa //
T02TD1676E:217a-16: lha la dmigs par byed pa dag / rang gi dam tshig bdag sbyor bas //
T02TD1676E:217a-18: gzugs brnyan lugs ma la sogs la //
T02TD1676E:217a-20: byang chub sems la rab brtson na ;
T02TD1676E:217a-22: chos rnams thams cad snang grol dbyings //
T02TD1676E:217a-23: kun gsal stong nyid zung 'jug dngos //
T02TD1676E:217a-24: rang bzhin ma bcos lhun gyis grub //
T02TD1676E:217a-25: bde ba chen po mchog gi rgya //
T02TD1676E:217a-26: byang sems mkha' dbyings dag pa las //
T02TD1676E:217a-27: yon tan ma rtsal kun 'byung snang //
T02TD1676E:217a-28: sna tshogs snang ba ris ma 'grub //
T02TD1676E:217a-29: rtog dpyod zhen chags yul las 'das //
T02TD1676E:217a-30: dbu mar yang ni mi dmigs te //
T02TD1676E:217a-31: shes rab pha rol phyin sbyor ba //
T02TD1676E:217a-32: thabs kyi snying rje'i bdag nyid rnams //
T02TD1676E:217a-33: de bas de ni snying rje'i thabs //
T02TD1676E:217a-34: shes rab pha rol phyin bar gsal //
T02TD1676E:217a-35: 'di ni rnal 'byor bcom ldan 'das rdo rje sems dpa' de bzhin gshegs //
T02TD1676E:217a-36: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam sbyor ba //
T02TD1676E:217a-37: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde ba'i mchog / yang dag grub pa gcig pu nyid //
T02TD1676E:217a-38: ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin du sbyar //
T02TD1676E:217a-39: rtog pa'i chog thams cad la //
T02TD1676E:217a-40: grub ba dam ba mchog gi mchog / sna tshogs las kyi sbyor ba yi ;
T02TD1676E:217a-42: sems can rnams ni 'dul ba dang //
T02TD1676E:217a-43: bde ba thams cad bsgrub pa'i phyir //
T02TD1676E:217a-44: bcom ldan rnal 'byor de nyid ni //
T02TD1676E:217a-45: sangs rgyas thams cad rnam 'phrul bas //
T02TD1676E:217a-46: sems can kun don rnam 'phrul nas //
T02TD1676E:217b-0: 'das @217b dus bskal pa rim bzhin du //
T02TD1676E:217b-1: log pa'i lam zhugs rnam drug pos //
T02TD1676E:217b-2: bdag gzhan gnyis ga phung byed cing //
T02TD1676E:217b-3: dregs byed chen por gyur pa la //
T02TD1676E:217b-4: thabs gzhan dag gis mi 'dul phyir //
T02TD1676E:217b-5: sangs rgyas thugs rje chen po yis //
T02TD1676E:217b-6: dgongs mdzad gsang ba bla ma'i mchog /
T02TD1676E:217b-7: rnam 'phrul chen po bstan pa yin //
T02TD1676E:217b-8: sems dpa' sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos //
T02TD1676E:217b-9: rdo rje sems dpa' bde ba'i mchog / gsang ba mchog gi dgyes pa la //
T02TD1676E:217b-10: thams cad bdag nyid rtag tu bzhugs /'di ni rang byung bcom ldan 'das //
T02TD1676E:217b-11: gcig pu rab tu che ba'i lha //
T02TD1676E:217b-12: rgyal ba kun gyi dgongs mdzad mchog /'khor lo gsang ba'i rgyud chen dag / rim bzhin brda don gsal mdzad cing //
T02TD1676E:217b-13: nges skyes phyag rgyas gtan la dbab //
T02TD1676E:217b-14: shes bya'i dkyil 'khor gsal gyur nas //
T02TD1676E:217b-15: rten mchog gi ni don sbyar nas //
T02TD1676E:217b-16: yan lag bzhi snang bcu drug tshogs //
T02TD1676E:217b-17: rgyu rkyen tshogs 'bras mdzad bcas rdzogs //
T02TD1676E:217b-18: gang zhig yun rings spyang pa'i mthus //
T02TD1676E:217b-19: snying rje chen po'i goms shugs can //
T02TD1676E:217b-20: dad brtson lta bas blogs la zing //
T02TD1676E:217b-21: des brtags dkyil 'khor dbang thob pas //
T02TD1676E:217b-22: smin lam rdzogs byed 'gyur med gnas //
T02TD1676E:217b-23: bla mas bsgo ba'i don bzhin spyod ;
T02TD1676E:217b-24: / bdag gzhan don sgrub lam la gnas //
T02TD1676E:217b-25: blo gros mchog gyur gsang ba'i snod //
T02TD1676E:217b-26: dkyil 'khor theg par ma zhugs shing //
T02TD1676E:217b-27: dam tshig spangs shing gsang don rmongs //
T02TD1676E:217b-28: shes rab che dang snying rje bral //
T02TD1676E:217b-29: log sman gus pa med spangs bya //
T02TD1676E:217b-30: gang du 'bras bu phun tshogs shing ;
T02TD1676E:217b-31: / dben pa'i dgon pa nyams dga' ba //
T02TD1676E:217b-32: gzhan dbang dgra yi tsher ma med //
T02TD1676E:217b-33: chu mchog shing gis mdzes byas par //
T02TD1676E:217b-34: kun du sna tshogs skal bzang por //
T02TD1676E:217b-35: kun du sna tshogs bde mchog gis //
T02TD1676E:217b-36: kun du sna tshogs dgos pa rnams //
T02TD1676E:217b-37: ci bde bar ni bsgrub par bya //
T02TD1676E:217b-38: rten dang dgon pa gtsug lag khang //
T02TD1676E:217b-39: ri yi rtse rnams thams cad du //
T02TD1676E:217b-40: rnam pa du ma sna tshogs pa'i //
T02TD1676E:217b-41: sangs rgyas dgongs pa bsgrub par bya //
T02TD1676E:217b-42: padma'i skyed mos tshal dga' dang //
T02TD1676E:217b-43: chu bo dag gi mdo dag tu //
T02TD1676E:218a-2: padmo skye mos tshal nyid du //
T02TD1676E:218a-3: rnam pa sna chogs du ma yis //
T02TD1676E:218a-4: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa bsgrub par bya / mkhar ni rnam pa sna tshogs dang //
T02TD1676E:218a-5: de bzhin chu bo'i 'gram dag gam //
T02TD1676E:218a-6: rgyal khams gzhan las grub pa ru //
T02TD1676E:218a-7: rdo rje rta ni bsgrub par bya ;
T02TD1676E:218a-8: / yul 'khor yo byad rgyan bcas dang //
T02TD1676E:218a-9: cha lugs rnam pa sna tshogs kyis //
T02TD1676E:218a-10: gnas kyi sa bzhi mdzes byas te //
T02TD1676E:218a-11: sgrub pa'i skyes bu dbye ba las //
T02TD1676E:218a-12: sgrub pa ram pa sna tshogs kyis //
T02TD1676E:218a-13: bdag gzhan bya ba sna tshogs 'grub //
T02TD1676E:218a-14: gzhan don dmigs pa'i las la ni //
T02TD1676E:218a-15: slob dpon de nyid bcu sogs shes //
T02TD1676E:218a-16: tshad ldan rang rgyud dag pa yis //
T02TD1676E:218a-17: dkyil 'khor dbang bskur sgrub pa dang //
T02TD1676E:218a-18: phrin las tshogs bsags bsrung don du //
T02TD1676E:218a-19: bsnyen 'gro bsnyen pa rdzogs byas pas //
T02TD1676E:218a-20: sa gzhi sas bon la 'jug cing //
T02TD1676E:218a-21: yang dag dkyil 'khor rgyas pa yi //
T02TD1676E:218a-22: gzhung bzhin 'jug par bya ba ste //
T02TD1676E:218a-23: rtog pa sna tshogs las 'phros pa'o //
T02TD1676E:218a-24: bdag don bya ba de las gzhan //
T02TD1676E:218a-25: sa gzhi sta gon sngon brtsams phyir //
T02TD1676E:218a-26: bdag nyid rang gi lhar sbyor bas //
T02TD1676E:218a-27: lus ngag yid gsum mthu bskyed cing //
T02TD1676E:218a-28: bdag dang 'gro ba spyang byas nas //
T02TD1676E:218a-29: rang bzhin dag pa'i rnam par bsam//
T02TD1676E:218a-30: bya ba'i rgyud sogs gsungs pa yi //
T02TD1676E:218a-31: gtor sbyin chen po'i cho ga yis //
T02TD1676E:218a-32: mgron tshogs bzhi po tshim byas nas //
T02TD1676E:218a-33: bsgo ba'i phrin las drag tu bya //
T02TD1676E:218a-34: phyogs bzhir srung ba'i stegs bu la //
T02TD1676E:218a-35: bsrung ba'i yi ge brtsams te gzhag / yang dag gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
T02TD1676E:218a-36: gsang ba'i dam can so so nas //
T02TD1676E:218a-37: 'di ba las ni ma gtogs shing //
T02TD1676E:218a-38: nyan pa las ni mi dbang ba'i //
T02TD1676E:218a-39: bgegs dang 'byung po thams cad kun //
T02TD1676E:218a-40: da lta nyid du so sor dangs //
T02TD1676E:218a-41: ji ste bka' las 'das gyur na //
T02TD1676E:218a-42: rdo rje 'dzin rgyal khros nas kyang //
T02TD1676E:218a-43: rdo rje mtshon chen 'bar ba yis //
T02TD1676E:218a-44: gtan du brlag cing phung bar 'gyur //
T02TD1676E:218a-45: h'um badzra dzva la ram yam /
T02TD1676E:218a-46: kham tsa kra bi shva h'um phat phat /
T02TD1676E:218a-47: thabs dang shes rab sgrub pa pos //
T02TD1676E:218a-48: phyi dang nang gi bskang bshags kyis //
T02TD1676E:218a-49: rin chen snod mdzes dri yang bsgribs //
T02TD1676E:218a-50: rnam dag ris gsal ji bzhin pa'o //
T02TD1676E:218a-51: thugs ka'i 'od zer spro bsdu yis //
T02TD1676E:218b-0: dkyil @218b 'khor mdun du dgu ga bya ste //
T02TD1676E:218b-1: dga' chen dpal las byung ba yi //
T02TD1676E:218b-2: se gol dpung mgor lan gsum gtogs //
T02TD1676E:218b-3: rdo rje bcing skyo'i se gol gyis //
T02TD1676E:218b-4: sangs rgyas thams cad bsdu bar bya //
T02TD1676E:218b-5: aom badzra sa m'a dza: h'um /
T02TD1676E:218b-6: aom thams cad spros bral de nyid che //
T02TD1676E:218b-7: mkha' mnyam ye shes rtogs med mchog / gnyis snang so sor smin dgongs mdzad //
T02TD1676E:218b-8: thugs rjes smon lam thabs mkhas pa //
T02TD1676E:218b-9: dbang po'i gzhu bzhin cing 'dul ston //
T02TD1676E:218b-10: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sras dang bcas //
T02TD1676E:218b-11: lha mo dag mchog dam pa'i lha //
T02TD1676E:218b-12: dkyil 'khor tshogs rnams dgongs su gsol ;
T02TD1676E:218b-14: aom ae hye hi ma h'a ka ru ni ka sa ma ya stvam /
T02TD1676E:218b-15: sna tshogs gar las byung ba yi //
T02TD1676E:218b-16: rdo rje thal mo spyi bor sbyar //
T02TD1676E:218b-17: aom rdo rje rgyal po yon tan mchog / byang chub mchog ston 'dren mdzad cing //
T02TD1676E:218b-18: nyon mongs mcho skems sgron mas brgyan //
T02TD1676E:218b-19: thugs rje can la skyabs su mchi //
T02TD1676E:218b-20: phyogs bcu kun na bzhugs pa yi //
T02TD1676E:218b-21: rdzogs sangs thub pa sras tshogs bcas //
T02TD1676E:218b-22: thugs rje chen po mnga' rnams la //
T02TD1676E:218b-23: gus par phyag 'tshal skyabs su mchi //
T02TD1676E:218b-26: mtshon cha drug gi tshul 'dra yi //
T02TD1676E:218b-27: thal mo kha yi gnas su gtug aom na ma: sarba tro ta h'um /
T02TD1676E:218b-29: mchod pa so so'i rjes mthun par //
T02TD1676E:218b-30: lha mo gar bcas phyag rgya bcing //
T02TD1676E:218b-31: aom stong gsum mi mjed gnas 'di dang //
T02TD1676E:218b-32: gzhan yang phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi //
T02TD1676E:218b-33: las kyi longs spyod mngon rgyud dang //
T02TD1676E:218b-34: sangs rgyas yon tan snang ba yi //
T02TD1676E:218b-35: mchod rdzas bzang po khyad par can //
T02TD1676E:218b-36: dngos su sbyar tshogs sems kyis sprul //
T02TD1676E:218b-37: me tog gzugs mdzes kha dog dang //
T02TD1676E:218b-38: dbyibs rnams sna tshogs mtha' yas mchog / bdug spos dri mchog khyad par can //
T02TD1676E:218b-39: so so'i rgyu las byung ba'i dri //
T02TD1676E:218b-40: mar me rin chen shing gi 'ong //
T02TD1676E:218b-41: mun pa'i tshogs 'joms gsal byed rgyun //
T02TD1676E:218b-42: dri mchog bzang pos sbyar ba chu //
T02TD1676E:218b-43: rnam rtog dri ma dag byed rgyun //
T02TD1676E:218b-44: bza' btung sna tshogs rgyu las byung //
T02TD1676E:218b-45: tshim byed ro ma mchog brgya ldan rdzas //
T02TD1676E:218b-46: yan lag brgyad ldan khrus kyi chu //
T02TD1676E:219a-1: bde'i mchod / dkyil 'khor kun la legs 'bul na //
T02TD1676E:219a-2: mgon po thugs rje can gyis bzhes //
T02TD1676E:219a-5: aom badzra a'a lo ke hr'i:/
T02TD1676E:219a-7: aom badzra na wi tye trem /
T02TD1676E:219a-8: aom badza a'a ha ra hi //
T02TD1676E:219a-9: sman dang 'bru yi rnam pa dang ;
T02TD1676E:219a-10: / bla re na bza' rgyal mtshan gdugs //
T02TD1676E:219a-11: ba dan phreng ba sna tshogs dang //
T02TD1676E:219a-12: do shal dbung rgyan sor gdub spras //
T02TD1676E:219a-13: dam pa rnams kyi longs spyod rkyen //
T02TD1676E:219a-14: bsod nams mthu las byung ba yi //
T02TD1676E:219a-15: yon tan thams cad 'byung ba'i gnas //
T02TD1676E:219a-16: nor bu rin chen 'khor lo'i mchog blon po dmag dpon btsun mo bzang //
T02TD1676E:219a-17: rta mchog glang po rin chen mchog / rnam spras nye ba'i rin chen bdun //
T02TD1676E:219a-18: bkra shis rdzas mtshog bcu drug mchog / bum pa bzang po rgyan la sogs //
T02TD1676E:219a-19: pha ta'i phreng ba mdzes sogs rnams //
T02TD1676E:219a-21: mgon po thugs rje can gyis bzhes //
T02TD1676E:219a-22: aom na ma: sarba ta th'a ga te bhyo //
T02TD1676E:219a-23: bi shv'a mu khe bhyi: sarva tad kham au tga te sphar na hi mam ga ga na kham sb'a h'a /
T02TD1676E:219a-24: aom rigs lnga'i dam tshig rdzas chen po //
T02TD1676E:219a-25: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i dbyings //
T02TD1676E:219a-26: rgyud lnga'i sems can kun grol zhing //
T02TD1676E:219a-27: rgyud lnga'i sems can bdud rtsi 'di//
T02TD1676E:219a-28: 'gro ba drug po dag / lha tshogs lha mor bcas 'gyur bas //
T02TD1676E:219a-29: rgyan rnams kun gyis legs mdzes par //
T02TD1676E:219a-30: glu dbyangs tshigs su bcas pa dang //
T02TD1676E:219a-31: khro tshogs gar gyis bskyod byas pa'i //
T02TD1676E:219a-32: stong gsum rdul snyed sprul byas rnams //
T02TD1676E:219a-34: mgon po thugs rje can gyis bzhes //
T02TD1676E:219a-35: aom na ma: sarba ta th'a ga te bhyo //
T02TD1676E:219a-36: bi shv'a mu khe bhyi: sarba ta da kham autga te spha ra na hi mam ga ga na kham sv'a h'a /
T02TD1676E:219a-37: aom rigs lnga'i dma tshig rdzas chen po //
T02TD1676E:219a-38: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i dbyings //
T02TD1676E:219a-39: rgyud lnga'i sems can kun grol zhing //
T02TD1676E:219a-40: rgyud lnga'i sems can bdud rtsi 'di //
T02TD1676E:219a-41: snying po tshim byed bcud kyi mchog / byang chub sems sogs bde ba'i rgyun //
T02TD1676E:219a-42: ma lus kun gyi reg bya las //
T02TD1676E:219a-43: rol pa sna tshogs snang ba dang //
T02TD1676E:219a-44: srid gsum brtan g-yo'i dngos po dang //
T02TD1676E:219a-45: nyon mongs sgo gsum spyod tshogs dang //
T02TD1676E:219a-46: phung po khams dang skye mched kyi //
T02TD1676E:219b-0: gzugs @219b bzang mchod sprin thams cad kun //
T02TD1676E:219b-1: sku lnga rigs lnga ye shes lnga //
T02TD1676E:219b-2: lha mo sras bcas ngo bo nyid //
T02TD1676E:219b-4: sna tshogs dngos med byang chub sems //
T02TD1676E:219b-5: gnyis su med par 'bul lags na //
T02TD1676E:219b-6: mnyam nyid blang dor med pas bzhes //
T02TD1676E:219b-8: sarba panytsa r'a sa ya na aa mri te h'um phat /
T02TD1676E:219b-9: aom bo dhi tsitta ma h'a su kha h'um //
T02TD1676E:219b-10: brda med rtse gcig sems nges par //
T02TD1676E:219b-11: rdo rje thal mo snying gar sbyar //
T02TD1676E:219b-12: h'um bdag dang mtha' yas sems can gyi //
T02TD1676E:219b-13: mgon po'i spyan sngar bshags pa ni //
T02TD1676E:219b-14: thog ma med nas dud 'di'i bar //
T02TD1676E:219b-15: mi dge las kyi dbang song ste //
T02TD1676E:219b-16: nyon mongs sgo gsum skyes pa yi //
T02TD1676E:219b-17: mi dge bcu dang mtshams med lnga //
T02TD1676E:219b-18: lta log sgro skur zhen log gis //
T02TD1676E:219b-19: rnam grol lam las gol gyur dang //
T02TD1676E:219b-20: nyon mongs nye ba'i nyon mongs tshogs //
T02TD1676E:219b-21: shes dang mi spangs gzhan gzung dang //
T02TD1676E:219b-22: bgyid dang bgyid dang bgyid du stsal ba dang //
T02TD1676E:219b-23: gang gzhan rjes su yi rang bshags //
T02TD1676E:219b-24: mgon po rnam kyi spyan lam du //
T02TD1676E:219b-25: rang bzhin kha na ma tho sdig //
T02TD1676E:219b-26: mi 'chab rim bzhin nges bshags shing //
T02TD1676E:219b-27: phyis kyang mi byed sdom pa gzung //
T02TD1676E:219b-28: bcas sdom so sor thar pa las //
T02TD1676E:219b-29: rtsa ba yan lag nyams pa dang //
T02TD1676E:219b-30: skyabs 'gro mkhan sogs slob dpon spangs //
T02TD1676E:219b-31: dad pa'i dge 'dun dbyen sogs dang //
T02TD1676E:219b-32: log tsho nyes byas phra la sogs //
T02TD1676E:219b-33: tshul khrims zhig 'gyur las rnams bshags //
T02TD1676E:219b-34: h'um byang chub sems sogs ma skyes shing //
T02TD1676E:219b-35: sdom pa rnams par spangs pa dang //
T02TD1676E:219b-36: pha rol phyin gzhung nyams pa yi //
T02TD1676E:219b-37: log pa'i lam la zhugs pa dang //
T02TD1676E:219b-38: tshangs pa'i gnas nas bsdu ba bzhi //
T02TD1676E:219b-39: lam sogs sum cu rtsa bdun dang //
T02TD1676E:219b-41: smod spangs sdig rnams dus 'dir bshags //
T02TD1676E:219b-42: h'um gsang ldan rdo rje che ge mos //
T02TD1676E:219b-43: rdo rje slob dpon smod 'gal zhing //
T02TD1676E:219b-44: lha spangs mched la 'khus pa dang //
T02TD1676E:219b-45: sngags dang phyag rgya spang pa dang //
T02TD1676E:219b-46: snod min gsad ba bsgrags la sogs //
T02TD1676E:219b-47: gnyis gsum nyi shu rtsa brgyad tshogs //
T02TD1676E:219b-48: yan lag cha shas nyams las 'das //
T02TD1676E:219b-49: 'gyod sems des par bshad par bgyi //
T02TD1676E:220a-0: aom na ma: k'a ya w'a ka tsitta sarba p'a pam shuddha shuddha h'um @220a * //
T02TD1676E:220a-2: 'das dang da ltar ma byon tshogs //
T02TD1676E:220a-3: rgyal ba sras dang bcas rnams kyi //
T02TD1676E:220a-4: dad brtson shes rab che bskyed cing /
T02TD1676E:220a-5: rgyu 'bras tshogs gnyis bsags byas nas //
T02TD1676E:220a-6: mdzad pa bcu gnyis la sogs dang //
T02TD1676E:220a-7: khyad par gsad sngags mdzad pa yis //
T02TD1676E:220a-8: 'gro rnams lam gnyis mdzad thob la //
T02TD1676E:220a-9: bdag gi rjes su yi rang ngo //
T02TD1676E:220a-10: lam gzhan 'phags pa rang rgyal dang //
T02TD1676E:220a-11: nyan thos so so skye bo yi //
T02TD1676E:220a-12: dge bsam sgom sogs gang spyad la //
T02TD1676E:220a-13: phrag dog med par rjes ye rang //
T02TD1676E:220a-14: phyogs rnams kun na bzhugs pa yi //
T02TD1676E:220a-15: mgon po thugs rje'i dbang gis ni ;
T02TD1676E:220a-16: ;'gro ba'i mos pa bzhin ston cing //
T02TD1676E:220a-17: sngon gyi smon lam ji lta bar //
T02TD1676E:220a-18: dam chos btsun par mdzad pa'i ched //
T02TD1676E:220a-19: bskul ba'i sa bla bzhugs pa dang //
T02TD1676E:220a-20: ji ltar tshangs pa'i rgyal tshogs kyis //
T02TD1676E:220a-22: gser gyi 'khor lo stong ldan phul //
T02TD1676E:220a-24: rgyal ba bde gshegs bcom ldan 'das //
T02TD1676E:220a-25: thogs ma 'di nas tha ma'i bar //
T02TD1676E:220a-26: mdzad pa rnam gsum mthar phyin nas //
T02TD1676E:220a-27: sku lnga ye shes chen por ni //
T02TD1676E:220a-28: myur du sprul pa bsdu bzhed rnams //
T02TD1676E:220a-29: 'gro rnams kun gyi don slad du //
T02TD1676E:220a-30: bskal ba ji srid gnas kyi bar ;
T02TD1676E:220a-31: / gzugs mang sprul sku'i tshul bzhugs shing //
T02TD1676E:220a-33: bkra shis tshogs kyis rgyas mdzad cing //
T02TD1676E:220a-34: rtag tu nyi zla sgrib gsal ltar //
T02TD1676E:220a-35: snyoms mdzad 'gro ba'i mun sel mdzod //
T02TD1676E:220a-37: de lta de ltar 'gro ba rnams ;
T02TD1676E:220a-38: / sdug bsngal rgyu dang de nyid las //
T02TD1676E:220a-39: bsgral zhing thar bar byas nas ni //
T02TD1676E:220a-40: bde tshogs ldan par bya ba dang //
T02TD1676E:220a-41: bla med 'bras bu bskyed bya'i phyir //
T02TD1676E:220a-42: dang po thabs kyis bdag bsgral nas //
T02TD1676E:220a-43: smon lam rdzu 'phrul dpag med dang //
T02TD1676E:220a-44: zhi gnas lhag mthong mngon shes sogs //
T02TD1676E:220a-45: thogs pa med par 'byung ba yis //
T02TD1676E:220a-46: myur du mthu stobs brtas gyur nas //
T02TD1676E:220a-47: g-yel med 'gro don brtson byed cing //
T02TD1676E:220a-48: thams cad dbugs dbyung byas nas ni //
T02TD1676E:220a-49: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i gnas bkod pa'o //
T02TD1676E:220a-50: phyogs bcu dag na bzhugs pa yi //
T02TD1676E:220a-51: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' dang //
T02TD1676E:220b-0: bla ma rdo rje @220b lcam dral dang //
T02TD1676E:220b-1: dkyil 'khor tshogs rnams dgongs su gsol //
T02TD1676E:220b-2: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba yis //
T02TD1676E:220b-3: skye ba 'di dang gzhan dag tu //
T02TD1676E:220b-4: dge rtsa spyi dang khyad par don //
T02TD1676E:220b-5: sngon bgyis bgyid la rjes yi dang //
T02TD1676E:220b-6: ji ltar sngon gyi de bzhin gshegs //
T02TD1676E:220b-7: rgyal ba sras bcas tshogs gyur pas//
T02TD1676E:220b-8: bla na med pa'i byang chub tu //
T02TD1676E:220b-9: thugs mchog rin chen bskyed pa ltar //
T02TD1676E:220b-10: bla med yang dag rdzogs pa yi //
T02TD1676E:220b-11: byang chub chen por sems bskyed de //
T02TD1676E:220b-12: rgyal ba rnams kyi rjes su slob //
T02TD1676E:220b-13: mdor na 'gro ba ma lus pa //
T02TD1676E:220b-14: sku gsum 'bras bu thob bya'i phyir //
T02TD1676E:220b-15: dkyil 'khor drug gi sprul pa yis //
T02TD1676E:220b-16: rnam par rol pa'i don gnas bya //
T02TD1676E:220b-17: de las byung ba'i 'bras bzang mchog / kun mkhyen gnas mchog snyoms mdzad pa //
T02TD1676E:220b-18: dngos rnams gang la'ang chang med de //
T02TD1676E:220b-19: byang chub sems dpa'i las chen pos //
T02TD1676E:220b-21: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i gnas thob shog / sna tshogs snang grags rnam grol ba //
T02TD1676E:220b-22: dbyings na cho 'phrul dgag med kyang //
T02TD1676E:220b-23: de yi cho 'phrul de nyid pas //
T02TD1676E:220b-24: nam mkha'i mtha' ltar sngon dang bral //
T02TD1676E:220b-25: 'khor gsum yongs su dag par ni //
T02TD1676E:220b-26: mnyam nyid bde ba zhen po'i dang //
T02TD1676E:220b-28: don nyid ngo bo lhun grub shog / rdo rje khu tshur gnyis gzhibs te //
T02TD1676E:220b-29: mthe ba chen bsgrengs nas g-yob par bya //
T02TD1676E:220b-31: rdo rje thal mos lan gsum du //
T02TD1676E:220b-32: mi dra smad gnyis brdab par bya //
T02TD1676E:220b-35: mnyam snyoms nyid du dmigs nas kyang //
T02TD1676E:220b-36: byams pa'i sems ni nyer gnas pas //
T02TD1676E:220b-37: sdug bsngal gsum dang brgyad dag gis //
T02TD1676E:220b-38: gdungs pa'i nyam thag gang yin pa //
T02TD1676E:220b-39: de dag sdug bsngal med 'dod phyir //
T02TD1676E:220b-40: sems can grangs med skur sprul nas //
T02TD1676E:220b-42: dpag med srul pas don mthun tshul //
T02TD1676E:220b-43: byams pa chen pos khyab par bya //
T02TD1676E:220b-44: rnam gsum snying rje chen po yis //
T02TD1676E:220b-45: de dag bde ba thob byas te //
T02TD1676E:220b-46: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga sogs kyi //
T02TD1676E:220b-47: bde ba dag la sprul bya ste //
T02TD1676E:220b-48: yid bzhin nor bu rin chen ltar //
T02TD1676E:220b-49: sems can grangs med skur sprul nas //
T02TD1676E:221a-2: don ldan dga' ba chen po'i blos //
T02TD1676E:221a-3: reg pas 'gro ba'i bag chags kun //
T02TD1676E:221a-4: rim gyis byang sems lam rnam bdun //
T02TD1676E:221a-5: myur bar byang chub rdzogs mthar phyin //
T02TD1676E:221a-6: sku dang ye shes phun sum tshogs //
T02TD1676E:221a-7: bkod pa'i yon tan dpag med snang ;
T02TD1676E:221a-8: / gzhir gyur btang snyoms chen po'i blos //
T02TD1676E:221a-9: ngan pa'i mtshan rtags rnam bral nas //
T02TD1676E:221a-10: gsal sems snyoms gnas bral ba med //
T02TD1676E:221a-11: rang bzhin byang sems mnyam pa'i dbyings //
T02TD1676E:221a-12: mi rtog ting 'dzin chen po yis //
T02TD1676E:221a-13: mtha' las grol ba'i sems nyid bskyed //
T02TD1676E:221a-14: 'di ni tshangs pa'i gnas bzhi las //
T02TD1676E:221a-15: mchog tu gyur pa'i tshad med bzhi //
T02TD1676E:221a-16: snying po sngags kyis spro byas la //
T02TD1676E:221a-17: rig bcas 'od zer khyab par gnas //
T02TD1676E:221a-18: phyogs gzhan rtog pa sna tshogs kyis //
T02TD1676E:221a-19: rkang dang sreg mnan cho ga dang //
T02TD1676E:221a-20: gsar bu shis bar byas pa'i las //
T02TD1676E:221a-21: las kyi cho ga gzhan bstan pa'o //
T02TD1676E:221a-22: rdo rje sems dpa'i sbyor ba yis //
T02TD1676E:221a-23: dga' ba'i rdo rje las byung ba'i //
T02TD1676E:221a-24: dpung mgor se gol brdab byas nas //
T02TD1676E:221a-25: rdo rje bcing kyo'i se go la sgras //
T02TD1676E:221a-26: 'jig rten khams ni ma lus pa //
T02TD1676E:221a-27: sangs rgyas rdo rje 'dzin bcas kun //
T02TD1676E:221a-28: dam tshig mchog gi gsang sngags kyis //
T02TD1676E:221a-29: til gyi gong bu bzhin du rgyas ;
T02TD1676E:221a-30: / shin tu gdug cing gtum pa la //
T02TD1676E:221a-31: zhi bas phan par mi 'gyur te //
T02TD1676E:221a-32: shes rab thabs kyi rnal 'byor pas //
T02TD1676E:221a-33: khro bor de bzhin gshegs kun mdzad //
T02TD1676E:221a-34: khro bo'i tshul can khros pas kyang //
T02TD1676E:221a-35: 'jig rten gsum dag sreg byed na //
T02TD1676E:221a-36: sangs rgyas thams cad khros pa yis //
T02TD1676E:221a-37: khams gsum ma lus smos ci dgos //
T02TD1676E:221a-38: de nas sna rtse'i rtsa mo la //
T02TD1676E:221a-39: yid ni brtan par yang dag zung //
T02TD1676E:221a-40: sna yi dbugs rings dro ba las //
T02TD1676E:221a-41: rgyal bas phyag rgya'i sbyor ba 'byung //
T02TD1676E:221a-42: bcom ldan de nyid rnal 'byor pas //
T02TD1676E:221a-43: rdo rje khro bor bsgyur nas phyung //
T02TD1676E:221a-44: dpal chen rdo rje he ru ka //
T02TD1676E:221a-46: sems dpa' sngon mo 'bar ba'i dang //
T02TD1676E:221a-48: dur khrod kyi ni me dang 'dra //
T02TD1676E:221a-50: thod pa mang po'i dbu rgyan can //
T02TD1676E:221a-51: 'jigs pa chen po'i dus ltar drag / dur khrod bzhin du rab tu 'jigs //
T02TD1676E:221b-0: khro la sogs @221b pa'i tshul ldan pa //
T02TD1676E:221b-1: zhal rnams sna tshogs 'gyur ba dang //
T02TD1676E:221b-2: smin ma khro gnyer bcas par bsgyur //
T02TD1676E:221b-3: 'bar ba'i lta bas gar byas pas //
T02TD1676E:221b-4: gu lang dbang chen de dbang bcas //
T02TD1676E:221b-5: nyi zla gshin rje'i tshangs par bcas //
T02TD1676E:221b-6: gnas bcas dag ni 'bar bcas nas //
T02TD1676E:221b-7: thal ba bzhin du rab tu bshig / rdo rje rdo rje kha tv'am ga //
T02TD1676E:221b-8: dril bu'i sgra ni gsil ba yis //
T02TD1676E:221b-9: thams cad phab nas slar yang ni //
T02TD1676E:221b-10: thal bar gyur pa'ang 'tsho bar byed //
T02TD1676E:221b-11: g-yas gnyis lcags kyu ral gri ste //
T02TD1676E:221b-12: g-yon gnyis zhags pa thod pa thogs //
T02TD1676E:221b-13: 'og ma gnyis kyis mda' dang gzhu //
T02TD1676E:221b-14: brkyang bskum nyi ma'i gdan la gnas //
T02TD1676E:221b-15: de yi 'bar ba'i nyi ma las //
T02TD1676E:221b-16: byung ba'i grib ma mi zad pa //
T02TD1676E:221b-17: bskyed nas ma lus bdud la sogs //
T02TD1676E:221b-18: gdug pa rnams kyi khrag za nu sa //
T02TD1676E:221b-19: rang sngags 'od zer g-yo ba'i mthus //
T02TD1676E:221b-20: shin tu bgegs med sa mthong nas //
T02TD1676E:221b-21: rdo rje sa gzhir sogs bsgom //
T02TD1676E:221b-23: 'dod pa'i rgyal po dregs chen pos //
T02TD1676E:221b-24: sumbha ni yi sngags brjod cing //
T02TD1676E:221b-25: brjid gnon khro ba chen po'i tshul //
T02TD1676E:221b-26: phyogs bcu'i bgegs rnams bkug mdzad nas //
T02TD1676E:221b-27: pho mor bsnol te nyi mar bkod //
T02TD1676E:221b-28: so so'i tshogs bcas myos par mdzad //
T02TD1676E:221b-31: gri hn'a pa ya gri hn'a pa ya /
T02TD1676E:221b-32: a'a na ya ho: bha ga p'an /
T02TD1676E:221b-35: y'a ma ya dza:ba ru na ye dza:/
T02TD1676E:221b-44: aa dhi pa ta na ye dza:/
T02TD1676E:221b-45: ye shes che las spul pa'i sku //
T02TD1676E:221b-46: zhal gsum phyag drug 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
T02TD1676E:221b-47: g-yas dkar g-yon dmar mthing nag sku //
T02TD1676E:221b-48: rdo rje thod khrag ral gri zhags //
T02TD1676E:221b-49: tho ba lcags kyu g-yas dang g-yon //
T02TD1676E:221b-50: dur khrod 'jigs pa'i cha lugs brgyan //
T02TD1676E:221b-51: aom badzra kro dha bi dz'a ya h'um /
T02TD1676E:221b-52: ha na ha na h'um phat /
T02TD1676E:221b-53: aom badzra kro dha ya m'anta ka h'um tishtha tishtha h'um phat /
T02TD1676E:221b-54: aom badzra kro dha ha ya gri wa h'um /
T02TD1676E:221b-55: hu lu hu lu h'um phat /
T02TD1676E:221b-56: aom badzra krodha aa mri ta kunda li h'um tstshinda tstshinda h'um phat //
T02TD1676E:221b-57: aom badzra kro dha n'i la danda h'um da ha da ha h'um phat //
T02TD1676E:221b-58: aom badzra kro dha a'ar+ya a'a tsa la h'um //
T02TD1676E:221b-60: aom badzra kro dha aa ba ra ji te h'um /
T02TD1676E:222a-1: badzra kro dha tree lo gya bidza ya h'um binda binda h'um phat /
T02TD1676E:222a-2: aom badzra kro dha h'um ka ra h'um gardza kardza h'um phat /
T02TD1676E:222a-3: aom badzra kro dha ma h'a ba la h'um spho ta spho ta h'um phat /
T02TD1676E:222a-4: rdo rje bdud rtsi rnam 'phrul bas //
T02TD1676E:222a-5: rdo rje tho ba phyag bsnams shing //
T02TD1676E:222a-6: phyogs mtshams steng 'og btab nas ni //
T02TD1676E:222a-7: rang gi gnas su nges par 'debs //
T02TD1676E:222a-8: aom badzra gha gha gh'a ta ya gh'a ta ya sarba dusht'an phat /
T02TD1676E:222a-9: badzra dha ro a'a dzny'a pa ya ti /
T02TD1676E:222a-10: k'a ya b'aka tsitta badzra k'i la ya h'um phat //
T02TD1676E:222a-11: aom phyogs bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor rnams //
T02TD1676E:222a-13: rigs mthun khro bo'i 'khor tshogs dang //
T02TD1676E:222a-14: dbang bskur rigs kyi skus brgyan pa'o //
T02TD1676E:222a-15: sangs rgyas kun gyi dam tshig dpal //
T02TD1676E:222a-16: rdo rje sems dpa' snang ba bde //
T02TD1676E:222a-17: de bzhin gshegs pa'i lha rdzas mchog / rin chen rgyan la sogs pas brgyan //
T02TD1676E:222a-18: dril bu rgyal mtshan mchog ldan pa'i //
T02TD1676E:222a-19: bla re dam pa bres pas na //
T02TD1676E:222a-20: rdo rje tshig dang mchod la sogs //
T02TD1676E:222a-21: glu dang sil snyan rnam par 'phrul //
T02TD1676E:222a-22: me tog bdug pa'i sbyor ba dang //
T02TD1676E:222a-23: mar me dri la sogs par ldan //
T02TD1676E:222a-24: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam sbyor ba //
T02TD1676E:222a-25: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde mchog sgrub //
T02TD1676E:222a-26: me tog dkar dang dmar ba dang //
T02TD1676E:222a-27: mthing gser po kun bsdus pa //
T02TD1676E:222a-28: me tog phyag rgya mchog 'di ni //
T02TD1676E:222a-30: rgya skyegs mthing ga ljang gu'i mchog / tshon sna bzhi yis btses pa dang //
T02TD1676E:222a-31: dkar po lnga yi phyag rgya dag / snga ma bzhin du mnyam par 'gyur //
T02TD1676E:222a-32: khams las byung ba thams cad dang //
T02TD1676E:222a-33: srog dang rtsa ba de bzhin te //
T02TD1676E:222a-34: rnam par mdzas shing dri zhim pa //
T02TD1676E:222a-35: snga ma bzhin du mnyam pa 'grub //
T02TD1676E:222a-36: tsandan gnyis dang gla rtsi dang //
T02TD1676E:222a-37: ga pur na ka la la gyi //
T02TD1676E:222a-38: bdug pa bu ram dang sbyar ba //
T02TD1676E:222a-39: las rnams thams cad rab sgrub pa'o //
T02TD1676E:222a-40: gandha dri dang gu gul dag / sardza ga pur gla rtsi dang //
T02TD1676E:222a-41: rdzas 'di dag la btsos pa'i mar //
T02TD1676E:222a-42: me mar byas na snang ba skyed //
T02TD1676E:222a-43: tsandan gum kum pri ka dang //
T02TD1676E:222a-44: ga bur dang ni gla rtsi dag / btsos pa'i bdug pa bsgrub pa ste //
T02TD1676E:222a-45: spos kyi phyag rgyas spos mchog 'gyur //
T02TD1676E:222a-46: kakko la dang sug smel dang //
T02TD1676E:222a-47: gla sgang ga bur gla rtsi dang //
T02TD1676E:222a-48: 'di dag zhib tu btags pa ni //
T02TD1676E:222a-49: seng ldeng bu ram dag dang sbyar //
T02TD1676E:222a-50: shing tsha pa tra lo 'dra dang //
T02TD1676E:222b-0: na le sham dang ga @222b pur sbyar //
T02TD1676E:222b-1: ha sa ka ri shing mngar gyis //
T02TD1676E:222b-2: spus pa kha yi spos yin no //
T02TD1676E:222b-3: me tog dmar po sangs rgyas la //
T02TD1676E:222b-4: rdo rje can la sna tshogs pa //
T02TD1676E:222b-5: 'jig rten dbang la kha dog dkar //
T02TD1676E:222b-6: ser po mkha' las byung ba la //
T02TD1676E:222b-7: tsandan bdug pa sangs rgyas la //
T02TD1676E:222b-8: rdo rje can la tu rushka //
T02TD1676E:222b-9: spyan ras gzigs la ka pi ta //
T02TD1676E:222b-10: lce pog rdo rje nyi ma la //
T02TD1676E:222b-11: mar me'i phreng ba sangs rgyas la //
T02TD1676E:222b-12: rdo rje can la mar me bdun //
T02TD1676E:222b-13: spyan ras gzigs la mar me brgya //
T02TD1676E:222b-14: stong ni rdo rje nyi ma la //
T02TD1676E:222b-15: sangs rgyas rnams la tsandan spos //
T02TD1676E:222b-16: rdo rje can la gur gum yin //
T02TD1676E:222b-17: spyan ras gzigs la tsandan dmar //
T02TD1676E:222b-18: ga pur rdo rje nyi ma la ;
T02TD1676E:222b-19: / me tog kun dang bdug pa kun //
T02TD1676E:222b-20: de bzhin mar me thams cad dang //
T02TD1676E:222b-21: spos rnams thams cad ji snyed pa //
T02TD1676E:222b-22: rdo rje rta la dbul du rung //
T02TD1676E:222b-23: sgeg mo dang ni na chung dang //
T02TD1676E:222b-24: mos dang de bzhin bdud rtsi dang //
T02TD1676E:222b-25: gcig pu dpa' dang 'dod chags sra //
T02TD1676E:222b-26: g-yon can bran mo de bzhin te //
T02TD1676E:222b-27: lan tshva la sogs ro kun dang //
T02TD1676E:222b-28: ka ra la sogs bdud rtsi sbyin //
T02TD1676E:222b-29: bdag nyid kun gyi ro 'grub pa //
T02TD1676E:222b-30: sha dang tshang du ldan pa yi //
T02TD1676E:222b-31: bza' ba sna tshogs 'grub pa ni //
T02TD1676E:222b-32: dga' ba'i longs spyod skal mchog ste //
T02TD1676E:222b-33: tshe yi dam tshig rab tu bsgrub //
T02TD1676E:222b-34: aa mra smin dang rgun 'brum dang //
T02TD1676E:222b-35: pa na se dang na le kar //
T02TD1676E:222b-36: aa ka ru la sogs pa yi //
T02TD1676E:222b-38: khar sbrang rtsis byugs pa yi //
T02TD1676E:222b-39: aa mra la sogs tshi gu byug / ha sa ka ri mar la sogs //
T02TD1676E:222b-40: mnyam pa'i dri yis bsku bar bya //
T02TD1676E:222b-41: yung dang rgya skyegs la sogs pa'i //
T02TD1676E:222b-42: tshon gyis mthun par kha bsgyur nas //
T02TD1676E:222b-43: shun pa gro ga la sogs byas //
T02TD1676E:222b-44: mchod pa'i tshe na dbul bar bya //
T02TD1676E:222b-45: sangs rgyas rnams la bshos dbul ba //
T02TD1676E:222b-46: sha dang chang ni rnam par spangs //
T02TD1676E:222b-47: glu dang sil snyan grub pa dang //
T02TD1676E:222b-48: gdugs dang rgyal mtshan ba dan dang //
T02TD1676E:222b-49: sha dang chang du bcas pa ni //
T02TD1676E:222b-50: gtor ma'i mchog ste tshogs pa'o //
T02TD1676E:222b-53: rdo rje las ni dpal grub pa'o //
T02TD1676E:222b-54: bshos dang gtor ma dkar po dang //
T02TD1676E:222b-55: padma me tog ldan pa ni //
T02TD1676E:222b-56: spyan ras gzigs dbang gtso bo la //
T02TD1676E:222b-57: phul na dgos pa thams cad 'grub //
T02TD1676E:222b-58: rgyal po kha zas la sogs pa //
T02TD1676E:222b-59: sha dang chang du ldan pa dang //
T02TD1676E:223a-0: glu dang sil snyan skal bzang @223a * //
T02TD1676E:223a-1: dag / rdo rje nyi ma'i 'khor la 'bul //
T02TD1676E:223a-2: kha zas kun gyi ro kun dang //
T02TD1676E:223a-3: sha dang sha yi mchog rnams dang //
T02TD1676E:223a-4: sha yi sbyor ba sha skam dang //
T02TD1676E:223a-5: bshos dag rdo rje lha la dbul //
T02TD1676E:223a-6: gzhan yang bza' btung longs spyod tshogs //
T02TD1676E:223a-7: g-yos kyi ston mo mang du bsham //
T02TD1676E:223a-8: dkyil 'khor chen po'i phyogs kun nas //
T02TD1676E:223a-9: spos chen sil snyan phreng thogs shing //
T02TD1676E:223a-10: gar dbyangs dro thabs drag 'gyur rtse //
T02TD1676E:223a-11: gzings bstod dga' ba'i bzhin rgyas spyod //
T02TD1676E:223a-12: h'um 'phags mchog thugs rje'i dus la bab //
T02TD1676E:223a-13: khyad par bstan pa'i dus la bab //
T02TD1676E:223a-14: dam tshig bskang ba'i dus la bab //
T02TD1676E:223a-15: dngos grub stsal ba'i dus la bab //
T02TD1676E:223a-16: mthu chen mthu stobs bcom ldan 'das //
T02TD1676E:223a-17: byin chen byin rlobs bcom ldan 'das //
T02TD1676E:223a-18: dbyin chen dbang bskur bcom ldan 'das //
T02TD1676E:223a-19: dngos grub mchog stsol bcom ldan 'das //
T02TD1676E:223a-20: bdag gi las rnams gang sgrub pa //
T02TD1676E:223a-22: / aa la la ho bha ga b'an /
T02TD1676E:223a-25: aom ye nas rnam pa kun ldan pa'i //
T02TD1676E:223a-27: gsal la brtan pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
T02TD1676E:223a-28: gnyis med brda yis mtshan par byos //
T02TD1676E:223a-29: aom stong gsum stong gi 'jig rten na //
T02TD1676E:223a-30: phyogs bzhi'i dkyil 'khor dbus rnams kyi //
T02TD1676E:223a-31: skye 'gro rdul snyed gnas pa kun //
T02TD1676E:223a-32: bde gshegs lnga yi dkyil 'khor dbyings //
T02TD1676E:223a-33: phyogs dus kun nas tshogs pa'i lha //
T02TD1676E:223a-34: gnyis su med pas phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1676E:223a-38: ta th'a ga to gu ru pa ti aa la la ho //
T02TD1676E:223a-39: lus ngag spyi dang khyad par gyi //
T02TD1676E:223a-40: gsang sngags brda yi phyag rgya 'dzin //
T02TD1676E:223a-41: byin rlabs mtshan ma gsal grub phyir //
T02TD1676E:223a-42: phyag rgya'i mtshan nyid spyad par bya //
T02TD1676E:223a-43: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
T02TD1676E:223a-44: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad du //
T02TD1676E:223a-45: dam tshig rtags kyi mtshan ma yi //
T02TD1676E:223a-46: dpal gyi chas brgyad rgyan dang bcas //
T02TD1676E:223a-48: thugs rjes rtsad nas gcod pa'i phyir //
T02TD1676E:223a-49: spyi dang khyad par rtags dag dang //
T02TD1676E:223a-50: don gyi sgo nas gzhom par mdzad //
T02TD1676E:223a-51: sems nyid bde ba chen po'i gnas //
T02TD1676E:223a-52: phung po dur khrod gzhal yas khang //
T02TD1676E:223a-53: dga' ba chen po'i glu dang gar //
T02TD1676E:223a-54: dngos kyang mchod pa'i rdzas su bsngo //
T02TD1676E:223b-0: @223b dbang bsgyur chen po'i ting 'dzin sogs //
T02TD1676E:223b-1: thams cad tshul bzhin byin brlabs te //
T02TD1676E:223b-2: cir yang gyur pa'i yig 'bru las //
T02TD1676E:223b-3: 'bar pa'i khang pa rnam par brjid //
T02TD1676E:223b-4: rang 'od sa bon so so las //
T02TD1676E:223b-5: bkod pa'i rgyan gyi dkyil 'khor che //
T02TD1676E:223b-6: sku gsung thugs kyi gsang chen pos //
T02TD1676E:223b-7: bsgrub rdzas de dag byin gyis brlabs //
T02TD1676E:223b-8: kro dhe shva ri dag byed kyis //
T02TD1676E:223b-9: mtshan ma'i gnas kun spyang bar bya //
T02TD1676E:223b-10: mtshan ldan padma'i pho brang du //
T02TD1676E:223b-11: 'chi med lcags kyu tshogs pa dag / dpa' bo 'bru dgu'i 'phro 'du yis //
T02TD1676E:223b-12: thams cad bdud rtsi byang chub sems //
T02TD1676E:223b-13: mchod dang gtor tshogs zhal zas rnams //
T02TD1676E:223b-14: kun bzang dkyil 'khor rnam par dag / aom ma h'a badzra tsakra mandala h'um //
T02TD1676E:223b-15: h'um aom hi hri tram ham /
T02TD1676E:223b-17: aom mah'a kro dheshva ri sarba trab phyam shva dha ya a'a:h'um /
T02TD1676E:223b-18: aom a'a:h'um sarba panytsa aa mri te h'um hri tha /
T02TD1676E:223b-19: aom te dzo ba lim te bha la bha ti gu hya sa ma ya sv'a h'a /
T02TD1676E:223b-20: so so'i ting 'dzin phyag rgya dang //
T02TD1676E:223b-21: sngags kyis gsal bar byas nas ni //
T02TD1676E:223b-22: sgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor gnas rnams su //
T02TD1676E:223b-23: de dag so sor dgod par bya //
T02TD1676E:223b-25: bsnyen sgrub yan lag rnam bzhi yis //
T02TD1676E:223b-26: las kun 'bras bu'i gnas sbyor ba'i //
T02TD1676E:223b-27: phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor bsgrub par bya //
T02TD1676E:223b-28: dang po chos kyi dbyings nyid la //
T02TD1676E:223b-29: dmigs pa med pa'i don gyis bsgom //
T02TD1676E:223b-30: dngos po med par bdag sbyor bas //
T02TD1676E:223b-31: nam mkha' kun dang mnyam sbyor ba'o //
T02TD1676E:223b-32: aom ma h'a sh'u n+ya t'a dzny'a na badzra sv'a bh'a wa a'atma ko& ham //
T02TD1676E:223b-33: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes kyis //
T02TD1676E:223b-34: thams cad du yang khyab byas la //
T02TD1676E:223b-35: chos kun stong gsal rang bzhin med ;
T02TD1676E:223b-36: / mi dmigs snying rje chen po'i ngang //
T02TD1676E:223b-37: aom dharma dh'a tu sva bh'a wa a'atma ko& ham /
T02TD1676E:223b-38: rdo rje sems dpa'i ting 'dzin gyis //
T02TD1676E:223b-39: mkha' dbyings sna tshogs la gnas nas //
T02TD1676E:223b-40: cir yang gyur pa'i yig 'bru bsam //
T02TD1676E:223b-42: ma lus nye bar khyab byas te //
T02TD1676E:223b-43: re zhing dam pa'i tshul du dgongs //
T02TD1676E:223b-44: ae 'byung 'a kha' dbyigs gru gsum dkar //
T02TD1676E:223b-45: gyen bsgreng bzang po'i mkha' dbyings nas //
T02TD1676E:223b-47: dud kha sra mkhregs sgrol ma'i mkha' //
T02TD1676E:223b-48: bam las chu dkyil dkar zhing zlum //
T02TD1676E:223b-49: bum pas mtshan pa m'am k'i //
T02TD1676E:224a-2: gru bzhi spyan ma rdo rjes mtshan //
T02TD1676E:224a-3: kham las sna tshogs can gyi mtsho //
T02TD1676E:224a-4: lcags ri mu khyud nor bus mtshan //
T02TD1676E:224a-5: sum las ri rab bang rim lcog / rin chen sna tshogs rgyu las grub //
T02TD1676E:224a-6: ram las med kyil dkar ser 'bar //
T02TD1676E:224a-7: zur mang gos dkar nam mkha'i dbyings //
T02TD1676E:224a-8: sra mkhregs rdo rje'i gzhi stengs la //
T02TD1676E:224a-10: de dbus bhr'um las gzhal yas khang //
T02TD1676E:224a-11: ye shes rin chen sna tshogs rgyan //
T02TD1676E:224a-12: nang gi dkyil 'khor gnas rnams su //
T02TD1676E:224a-13: re'u mig 'khor lo mtshungs pa brgyad //
T02TD1676E:224a-14: rdo rje phreng ba'i tshogs gyis brgyan //
T02TD1676E:224a-15: sna tshogs padma gdan gyis mtshan //
T02TD1676E:224a-16: dkyil 'khor phyi rim gnas brgyad du //
T02TD1676E:224a-17: dur khrod shing dang zhing skyong dang //
T02TD1676E:224a-18: phyogs skyong rnal 'byor mtsho dang sprin //
T02TD1676E:224a-19: klu rgyal de dag gnas brgyad du //
T02TD1676E:224a-20: sha za 'byung po gshin rje dang //
T02TD1676E:224a-21: mkha' 'gro bya khyi ro langs dang //
T02TD1676E:224a-22: ce spyang khros pa'i sgra 'byin cing //
T02TD1676E:224a-23: ro yi tshogs la longs spyod mdzad //
T02TD1676E:224a-24: rang 'byung mchod rten dang bcas pa //
T02TD1676E:224a-25: phreng ba rim gsum phyi rol gyi //
T02TD1676E:224a-26: ra ba'i mtshams su gnas pa las //
T02TD1676E:224a-27: kun 'byung rgyan gyis mtshan spras pa'o //
T02TD1676E:224a-28: de dbus 'khor lo'i lte ba la //
T02TD1676E:224a-29: pad zla nyi ma'i gdan stengs su //
T02TD1676E:224a-30: dpal mchog dang po gnas mdzad nas //
T02TD1676E:224a-32: chos rnams thams cad rnam brtags na //
T02TD1676E:224a-33: dngos med mtshan ma kun dang bral //
T02TD1676E:224a-34: zla dkyil a'a li bcu drug bzhi //
T02TD1676E:224a-37: nyis 'gyur mtshan dang dpe byad gsal //
T02TD1676E:224a-38: de dag 'od du gyur pa la //
T02TD1676E:224a-39: 'od phung kha dog sna lnga nyid //
T02TD1676E:224a-40: h'um las rdo rje rtse lnga pa //
T02TD1676E:224a-41: dkar po bum par h'um gis mtshan //
T02TD1676E:224a-42: thog ma tha ma med pa'i dbyings //
T02TD1676E:224a-43: dang po rdo rje chen po yin //
T02TD1676E:224a-46: dkyil 'khor drug gi las mdzad nas ;
T02TD1676E:224a-47: / sku gsung thugs dbyings zhugs pa las //
T02TD1676E:224a-48: 'od zer phreng mdzes brjid pa'i mchog / de las sku mchog phyag rgya yis //
T02TD1676E:224a-49: sngags kyi yi ge brjod par bya //
T02TD1676E:224a-50: aom ma h'a su kha badzra sa tva aa //
T02TD1676E:224a-53: de dag ye shes byang chub sems //
T02TD1676E:224a-54: mngon byang lnga yi bdag nyid do //
T02TD1676E:224b-1: ri bo nyi ma'i mdangs chags pa //
T02TD1676E:224b-2: bzhin 'dzum snuem zhing nyams tshogs rgyas //
T02TD1676E:224b-3: chags tshul dar la bab pa bzhin //
T02TD1676E:224b-4: zhal phyag mtshungs zhing sngon dmar ser //
T02TD1676E:224b-5: g-yas na rdo rje rtse lnga 'bar //
T02TD1676E:224b-6: g-yon pa kha tv'am dril bur bcas //
T02TD1676E:224b-7: 'og ma gnyis kyis mda' dang gzhu //
T02TD1676E:224b-8: rin chen rgyan dang na bza' dang //
T02TD1676E:224b-9: mgul du do shal dpung rgyan dang //
T02TD1676E:224b-10: phyag zhabs gdu bu se mo do //
T02TD1676E:224b-11: mtshan dpe phyag rtsa lnga yis mdzes //
T02TD1676E:224b-12: rdo rje rtse lnga'i phyag rgya ni //
T02TD1676E:224b-13: gnas lnga dag tu gtugs bya ste //
T02TD1676E:224b-14: sngags kyis bde gshegs thams cad kyi //
T02TD1676E:224b-15: sku gsungs thugs sogs rnam par bsam //
T02TD1676E:224b-16: aom nam:sarba ta th'a ga ta k'a ya w'aka tsitta gu na karma badzra sva bh'a wa a'atma ko& ham /
T02TD1676E:224b-17: lus kyi ba spu'i gnas rnams su //
T02TD1676E:224b-18: dkyil 'khor drug gi rdul phran gnas //
T02TD1676E:224b-19: mkha' dbyings dbang phyug phyag rgya yis //
T02TD1676E:224b-20: gnas kun byin gyis brlab par bya //
T02TD1676E:224b-21: aom dharm'a dh'a tu sva bh'a wa a'atma ko& ham /
T02TD1676E:224b-23: gsang gnas h'um dang a'as brgyan te //
T02TD1676E:224b-24: ye shes rdo rje phat dang bcas //
T02TD1676E:224b-25: rtse mo nor bu 'bar bas mtshan //
T02TD1676E:224b-26: rnam thar padma ae dkyil can //
T02TD1676E:224b-27: mdog ser lte ba ze'u 'bru dmar //
T02TD1676E:224b-28: sa ma ya sogs brdas bskul nas //
T02TD1676E:224b-29: dza h'um bam ho:sa rol ba bya //
T02TD1676E:224b-30: aom bra be sha ya phat ;
T02TD1676E:224b-31: aa la la la la ho //
T02TD1676E:224b-32: bde ba chen po'i 'od zer gyis //
T02TD1676E:224b-33: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba mnyes mdzad de //
T02TD1676E:224b-34: 'gro ba'i lus ngag yid rtog sbyangs //
T02TD1676E:224b-35: sku gsung thugs kyi rgyun gyis brjid //
T02TD1676E:224b-36: stong gsum ti la gang 'bru 'dra rnams //
T02TD1676E:224b-37: thams cad 'od kyis slar bsdus nas //
T02TD1676E:224b-38: sangs rgyas drug gi yi ger gyur //
T02TD1676E:224b-39: ba spu'i bu ga kun du thim //
T02TD1676E:224b-40: thugs ka'i gnas su zhu ba dag / bde ba chen po'i gnas nas bab //
T02TD1676E:224b-41: 'dod chags chen po dga' ba'i mes //
T02TD1676E:224b-42: sku dang bcas pa 'od du gyur //
T02TD1676E:224b-43: sngon gyi go mas shugs lha mo bzhis //
T02TD1676E:224b-44: phyogs bzhi nas ni bskul byas te //
T02TD1676E:224b-45: stong ba shin tu rnal 'byor yod med mthu //
T02TD1676E:224b-46: nam mkha' nyid du dam tshigs nye bar gnas //
T02TD1676E:224b-47: bde gshegs bde bar gshegs pa bzhengs su gsol //
T02TD1676E:224b-48: rdo rje sems dpa' skal bzang dpal khod bdag / ye shes gsal ba'i rgyud bskul nas //
T02TD1676E:224b-49: thugs rjes 'gro la dmigs mdzad de //
T02TD1676E:225a-2: rdo rje sems dpa' bzhengs par 'gyur //
T02TD1676E:225a-3: mtshan ma rgyan sogs cha lugs dang //
T02TD1676E:225a-4: sku mdog phyag mtshan snga ma bzhin //
T02TD1676E:225a-5: lus dang ngag sems rdo rje yis //
T02TD1676E:225a-6: mtshan ma'i phyag rgyar ldan byas te //
T02TD1676E:225a-7: thams cad 'byung ba'i sbyor ba yis //
T02TD1676E:225a-8: bdag gi lhar ni bdag nyid bya //
T02TD1676E:225a-10: thugs gsal nyi ma la gnas pa'i //
T02TD1676E:225a-11: ye shes sems dpa' h'um sngags bcas //
T02TD1676E:225a-12: gsang ba'i phyag rgya rnam pa bzhis //
T02TD1676E:225a-13: las kun grub byed dngos grub gsal //
T02TD1676E:225a-15: ye shes dkyil 'khor spyan drangs te //
T02TD1676E:225a-16: thugs ka nas byung lha mo bzhis //
T02TD1676E:225a-17: bdud rtsi bum pas khrus byas nas //
T02TD1676E:225a-18: gnas gsum dbang bskur dri bral byas //
T02TD1676E:225a-19: slar 'dus tshang bug gnas su thim //
T02TD1676E:225a-20: mthe bo sems dpa'i skyil mo krung //
T02TD1676E:225a-21: mdzub mo gnyis ni rtse mo dgug / gung mo gnyis ni mnyam par sgyar //
T02TD1676E:225a-22: lhag ma rdo rje thal mo bya //
T02TD1676E:225a-23: spyi bo dang ni dbral ba dang /
T02TD1676E:225a-24: lhan pa gnyis dang ltag par sbyar //
T02TD1676E:225a-26: sor mo thams cad nang du bsnol //
T02TD1676E:225a-27: rtse mo ngos rnams kun sprad nas //
T02TD1676E:225a-28: mthe bod rdo rjes mnan pa ni //
T02TD1676E:225a-29: sna dang mig phugs lta bu ste //
T02TD1676E:225a-30: gong bzhin mgo bo'i gnas lngar gtugs //
T02TD1676E:225a-31: rin chen thod phreng skur bcas 'gyur ;
T02TD1676E:225a-33: sangs rgyas kun gyi rin chen mchog / dpung rgyan kun du brgyan par bya //
T02TD1676E:225a-34: aom ratna m'a le aa bhi shinytsa tr'am /
T02TD1676E:225a-35: dbu rgyan bcings pas bcings nas ni //
T02TD1676E:225a-36: 'gying zhing mtha' nas grol bar bya //
T02TD1676E:225a-37: aom pa ta lam ba aa bhi shintsa h'um /
T02TD1676E:225a-38: dar gyi mtha' ma dbyangs pa ltar //
T02TD1676E:225a-39: byas nas thal mo brdab par bya //
T02TD1676E:225a-41: khams gsum dag na rin chen gzhan //
T02TD1676E:225a-42: sangs rgyas rin chen lta bu med //
T02TD1676E:225a-43: sangs rgyas kun gyi rin po che //
T02TD1676E:225a-44: dbu rgyan can ni de bas mchog / gzhan gyi nor min mi 'phrog pa //
T02TD1676E:225a-45: lha yi chu ni dag pa ste //
T02TD1676E:225a-46: thod pa'i phreng ba'i dbu rgyan dang /
T02TD1676E:225a-47: sangs rgyas gtsug gi nor bu yi //
T02TD1676E:225a-48: rjes su chags pa'i rnam mang dga' ba'i padmo rnams //
T02TD1676E:225a-49: dga' ba mchod pas gsal bar rjes su mchod byas pas //
T02TD1676E:225a-50: mchog tu rtag pa'i rnal 'byor bde bas bde grub mdzod //
T02TD1676E:225a-51: ae ma'o mchog tu bde ba'i dam tshig ngo bo nyid //
T02TD1676E:225b-0: mchog tu bde ba'i rnal @225b 'byor skal bzang mchog dgyes pa //
T02TD1676E:225b-1: rang gi dam tshig rtag la rol cig rol cig to //
T02TD1676E:225b-2: yab yum gsang gnas h'um dang dza:sa //
T02TD1676E:225b-3: rdo rje padma bskyed byas nas //
T02TD1676E:225b-5: brla yi dbus su gzhug byas te //
T02TD1676E:225b-6: ling ga rdo rjer byin brlabs nas //
T02TD1676E:225b-7: rdo rje sems sogs sku bstod do ;
T02TD1676E:225b-8: / byang chub sems de kun du dag / ma lus nye bar khyab byas nas //
T02TD1676E:225b-9: 'dod par bya bar rab tu mnyes //
T02TD1676E:225b-11: gnas nas so so'i gdan dag la //
T02TD1676E:225b-12: chos kyi snying pos lha rnams bskyed //
T02TD1676E:225b-13: h'um las rdo rje sems dpa' ste //
T02TD1676E:225b-14: skyil krung dbus kyi gdan la'o //
T02TD1676E:225b-15: rdza:las dpal ldan bde mchog ma //
T02TD1676E:225b-16: h'um las ae ma bde mchog ma / bam las lha mo snang mdzad ma //
T02TD1676E:225b-18: 'di dag gtso bo'i phyogs bzhi yi //
T02TD1676E:225b-19: ri'u cha'i gdan la rim bzhin gnas //
T02TD1676E:225b-20: aom las sangs rgyas byang chub ma /

T02TD1676E:225b-22: ham las khams gsum rnam rgyal yin //
T02TD1676E:225b-23: kham las 'dod pa kun mdzad ma'o //

T02TD1676E:225b-25: re'u mig 'khor lo'i rtse la gnas //
T02TD1676E:225b-26: aom las gling bu tr'am pi wang //
T02TD1676E:225b-27: bam las rnga chen rdza rnga ma //
T02TD1676E:225b-28: lha mo 'di bzhi me mtshams kyi //
T02TD1676E:225b-29: 'khor lo'i rtse la rim bzhin gnas //
T02TD1676E:225b-30: aa las me tog a'a spos ma //
T02TD1676E:225b-31: aam las mar me ai dri chab //
T02TD1676E:225b-32: 'di dag mtshams kyi gnas bzhi ru //
T02TD1676E:225b-33: rim pa bzhin du bskyed pa'o //
T02TD1676E:225b-35: rta mgrin 'phang mtho la sogs bskyed //
T02TD1676E:225b-36: bha gar ling+ga bcug byas nas //
T02TD1676E:225b-37: der ni mtshan ma bsgom par bya //
T02TD1676E:225b-38: rdo rje sems dpa' phyag rgya che //
T02TD1676E:225b-39: sku gnyis ldan pa spro bar bya //
T02TD1676E:225b-40: aom ma h'a su kha badzra sa tva a'a: dza:h'um bam ho:/

T02TD1676E:225b-44: 'dul phyir rdo rje sems dpa' ni //

T02TD1676E:225b-48: rin chen phreng mdzes gos rgyan bklubs //
T02TD1676E:225b-49: phyogs bcur 'gro ba'i don dbyung spro //

T02TD1676E:226b-4: gsal 'dzin rlung gi mtshams su gnas //
T02TD1676E:226b-5: aom badzra a'a lo ke dzdza /
T02TD1676E:226b-6: dri chab ljang gu rdo rjes mtshan //
T02TD1676E:226b-7: dga' 'thor dbang ldan mtshams su gnas //

T02TD1676E:226b-10: lcags kyu rta mgo ljang gu shar //

T02TD1676E:228b-11: sna tshogs bsgyur cing de don 'phrul //
T02TD1676E:228b-12: dga' dbyangs bsgyur bas gnas gsum bskyod //
T02TD1676E:228b-13: he badzra ghe te te tem /
T02TD1676E:228b-15: cang te'i tshul ston rnal 'byor pa'i //
T02TD1676E:228b-16: ji ltar dbab pa'i gar byed pas //
T02TD1676E:228b-17: sku gsung theg chen rgyud ston pa'i //
T02TD1676E:228b-18: phyag rgya gar gyis kun las rgyal //
T02TD1676E:228b-19: aom he r'a ti badzra h'a se ha ha pam /
T02TD1676E:228b-21: rdza rnga'i tshul ston rnal 'byor pa //
T02TD1676E:228b-22: ji ltar 'bab pa'i gar byed cing //
T02TD1676E:228b-23: g-yas g-yon mdun rgyab blta ba'i bzhin //
T02TD1676E:228b-24: bzhi sbyor glu bcas kun bstan pa'o //
T02TD1676E:228b-25: aom he r'a ti badzra nri te pe te pe pe pam dza:ma h'a mu dra h'um /
T02TD1676E:228b-26: cang te'u'i tshul ston rnal 'byor pas //
T02TD1676E:228b-27: spyin pa'i mchog gnas rnam par grol //
T02TD1676E:228b-28: gzugs mchog lha rdzas me tog rgya //
T02TD1676E:228b-29: sa gzhi mdun rol g-yas g-yon bstod //
T02TD1676E:228b-30: sna tshogs dpung pa 'thor byed pa'o //
T02TD1676E:228b-33: tshul khrims dri mchog tshim byed pa'i //
T02TD1676E:228b-34: bdud mchog spos legs sbyar ba'i mchog / g-yas skor bteg te phyogs bcur bsgyur //
T02TD1676E:228b-35: mdun du phyogs par sngo byed pa'o //
T02TD1676E:228b-36: aom badzra dh'u pa ma h'a mu dra h'um /
T02TD1676E:228b-37: bzod gsol shes rab ting nge 'dzin //
T02TD1676E:228b-38: mun tshogs gsal byed mar me'i rgya //
T02TD1676E:228b-39: kun du bskor ba'i gar bsgyur zhing //
T02TD1676E:228b-40: thugs ka'i mtshan ma gsal ston pa'o //
T02TD1676E:228b-44: chos kun dag byed byug pa'i dri //
T02TD1676E:228b-45: srin mtheb rang gnas rtse gsum 'thor //
T02TD1676E:228b-46: phyogs kun dngos ni bcos dag 'gyur /
T02TD1676E:228b-49: padma can de'i bdud rtsi bstod //
T02TD1676E:228b-50: myang ba rdub [*rngub?] pa ltar byed pa'i //
T02TD1676E:228b-51: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya rdo rjer bcas //
T02TD1676E:228b-53: aom badzra aam ku sha dza:ma h'a mu dra h'um /
T02TD1676E:228b-54: rdo rje mche ba 'jigs pa'i rgya //
T02TD1676E:228b-55: sna yi myang ba'i rdub [*rngub?] pa yis //
T02TD1676E:229a-0: rin chen zhags bcas gsol ka'i @229a * //
T02TD1676E:229a-2: / rang gi las la sbyor byed pa'o //
T02TD1676E:229a-5: rdo rje lcags sgrog nyi zlar bcas //
T02TD1676E:229a-6: mig btsums zhen par blta ba yis //
T02TD1676E:229a-7: khams gsum kun la gzigs pa'i rgya //
T02TD1676E:229a-8: phyag rgya'i las kyis bsten byed pa'o //
T02TD1676E:229a-9: aom badzra shrim kha le bam /
T02TD1676E:229a-11: mtshan ldan sku mchog bdud rtsis bkang //
T02TD1676E:229a-12: thams cad bdag nyid myang ba yis //
T02TD1676E:229a-13: stong pa gsung dbyangs rgyun mi 'chad //
T02TD1676E:229a-15: aom badzra ghande ho:ma h'a mu dra h'um /
T02TD1676E:229a-16: rdo rje sems dpa' skal bzang dpal khyod bdag / bdag cag sgrub la rtog par mdzad du gsol ;
T02TD1676E:229a-17: / kye de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi bdag nyid bde //
T02TD1676E:229a-18: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma sna tshogs bde ba'i mchog /'gro ba'i rgyud rnams rnam pa sna tshogs 'dul //
T02TD1676E:229a-19: dngos grub bdag la grub par mdzad du gsol //
T02TD1676E:229a-21: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sbyor ba rnams //
T02TD1676E:229a-22: rnam pa sna tshogs gar rnams bstan du gsol //
T02TD1676E:229a-24: kye bde ba chen po'i mchog kun gyi //
T02TD1676E:229a-25: bde bas zung la rnam par 'phrul par mdzad //
T02TD1676E:229a-26: h'um snang bar mdzad du gsol //
T02TD1676E:229a-28: bde gshegs mkha' gro slob ma gzung du gsol //
T02TD1676E:229a-29: mtshan ma'i yi ge padma'i dkyil //
T02TD1676E:229a-30: kun gyi rtse la bsgom byas nas //
T02TD1676E:229a-32: rang sngags chos kyi phyag rgyar bcas //
T02TD1676E:229a-33: aom na mo badzra sarba stu ta sarba tu ddhe bhya:h'um sv'a h'a /
T02TD1676E:229a-34: rdo rje sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor gyi //
T02TD1676E:229a-35: sbyor ba'i sngags kyi mthu dag gis //
T02TD1676E:229a-36: la sogs mchod pa ma lus pa //
T02TD1676E:229a-37: lus pa med par kun la sbyar //
T02TD1676E:229a-38: mdzub mos mthe bo mnan nas ni //
T02TD1676E:229a-39: rang gi mthe bos mdzub mo mnan //
T02TD1676E:229a-40: dpal grub can gyi phyag rgya ste //
T02TD1676E:229a-41: mdzub mo mig gi 'bras bur bya //
T02TD1676E:229a-42: rdo rje thal mo mnyam sbyor nas //
T02TD1676E:229a-43: khong stong du ni byas nas su //
T02TD1676E:229a-44: gsang sngags dam tshig sbyor bzhag ste //
T02TD1676E:229a-45: rim bzhin mtha' nas grol bar bya //
T02TD1676E:229a-46: aom badzra sa tvas ma ya /
T02TD1676E:229a-48: badzra satva tve no pa tishtha /
T02TD1676E:229a-49: dram dho me bha gsu to shyo me bha ba /
T02TD1676E:229a-50: aa nu rakto me bha ba /
T02TD1676E:229a-54: tsittam shre ya: ku ru h'um /
T02TD1676E:229a-59: bdzr'i bha ba ma h'a sa ma ya satva a'a;/
T02TD1676E:229a-60: srin lag mthe'u chung yan lag dbus//
T02TD1676E:229b-0: @229b mthe bo legs par gzhag par bya //
T02TD1676E:229b-1: de nas khu tshur bcings nas ni //
T02TD1676E:229b-2: mdzub mo legs par dgug par bya //
T02TD1676E:229b-3: gsang sngags la sogs sbyor byas pas //
T02TD1676E:229b-4: so so'i las la gzhug bya ste //
T02TD1676E:229b-5: las kyi phyag rgya'i 'ching grol gyis //
T02TD1676E:229b-6: rang gi phrin las kun spyod pa'o //
T02TD1676E:229b-7: dman pa'i phyag rgya rnam pa bzhis//
T02TD1676E:229b-8: dngos grub ba sna tshogs las sbyor ba'o //
T02TD1676E:229b-9: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
T02TD1676E:229b-10: rgyal ba rgya mtsho ye shes kyis //
T02TD1676E:229b-11: srid pa'i rgya mtsho mtha' yas kun //
T02TD1676E:229b-12: kun bzang mchod sbrin mchog tu rol //
T02TD1676E:229b-13: aom na ma:sarba ta th'a ga te bhyo //
T02TD1676E:229b-14: bi shva mu khe bhye:sarba tadkham aung+ga te hi mam ga ga na kham sv'a h'a /
T02TD1676E:229b-15: aom 'byung ba lnga las thams cad 'byung //
T02TD1676E:229b-16: rang las ma byung gang yang med //
T02TD1676E:229b-17: gtsang sme'i dri rtog kun bral ba'i //
T02TD1676E:229b-18: bdud rtsi byang chub sems chen pos //
T02TD1676E:229b-19: bdag sogs gnyis med mchod pa'i phyir //
T02TD1676E:229b-20: mnyam pa chen pos gnas la rol //
T02TD1676E:229b-21: h'um ma h'a su kha bodhi tsitta aa la la ho aa la la ho //
T02TD1676E:229b-22: aom mnyam med mi g-yo mnyam nyid mchog gi chos nyid can //
T02TD1676E:229b-23: thugs rjes bdag nyid 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal sel bar mdzad //
T02TD1676E:229b-24: yon tan mtha' yas dngos grub thams cad sbyin mdzad pa //
T02TD1676E:229b-25: dri med mi g-yo mnyam pa med pa'i chos mchog can //
T02TD1676E:229b-26: aom yon tan shin tu phra ba'i cha la'ang tshad med de //
T02TD1676E:229b-27: dpe ni nam mkha' dang yang bskun [*bsnun?] du yod ma yin //
T02TD1676E:229b-28: dngos grub mtha' yang mnyam med dpe dang bral ba rnams //
T02TD1676E:229b-29: sems can khams las dngos grub mchog rnams nges par stsol //
T02TD1676E:229b-30: aom rtag tu dri ma med pa'i thugs rje shugs las byung //
T02TD1676E:229b-31: smon lam grub pa 'gag pa med pa'i chos nyid can //
T02TD1676E:229b-32: 'gro ba'i don grub rab tu brtson pa mtha' yas pa //
T02TD1676E:229b-33: thugs rje chen po'i bdag nyid rtag tu rnam par snang //
T02TD1676E:229b-34: aom tshad med tshad dang bral ba shin tu rdzogs pa yis //
T02TD1676E:229b-35: bde bar gshegs pa'i go 'phang dam pa brnyes gyur kyang //
T02TD1676E:229b-36: khams gsum rnams la dngos grub mchog tu stsol mdzad cing //
T02TD1676E:229b-37: thugs rje'i spyod pa mi g-yo 'gag par yongs mi 'gyur //
T02TD1676E:229b-38: aom ae ma'o shin tu bzang po'i dngos grub mchog dang ldan //
T02TD1676E:229b-39: mchog sbyin rnams kyi nang na go 'phang mchog brnyes pa //
T02TD1676E:229b-40: khams gsum rnams la rtag tu dngos grub mchog stsol mdzad //
T02TD1676E:229b-41: mgon po dus gsum bsgrib pa med par rab mkhyen pa /
T02TD1676E:230a-0: @230a * // dam tshig mchog gsum dngos grub dam pa bdag la stsol //
T02TD1676E:230a-1: aom phyogs bcu nam mkha'i mtha' klas par //
T02TD1676E:230a-2: sems can kun gyi don sgrub la //
T02TD1676E:230a-3: ji ltar thugs kyi dbang phyug bzhin //
T02TD1676E:230a-4: de nyid spyod par bdag gyur cig //
T02TD1676E:230a-5: ji srid thog ma med dus nas //
T02TD1676E:230a-6: 'khor ba yi ni mthar thug par //
T02TD1676E:230a-7: de srid sems can phan pa nyid //
T02TD1676E:230a-8: mtha' yas spyod par bdag gyur cig / sngags kyi tshul gyis sems can rnams //
T02TD1676E:230a-9: de tshe bdag gis dul 'gyur zhing //
T02TD1676E:230a-10: kun gyis rig 'dzin gnas thong nas //
T02TD1676E:230a-11: de nyid mgon po mthong bar shog / lha rnams kun gyi gnas zhugs pa'i //
T02TD1676E:230a-12: ye shes sems dpa'i sngags 'khor lo //
T02TD1676E:230a-13: nyi zla rten dang brten pa'i sngags //
T02TD1676E:230a-14: 'khor lo'i tshul ldan shes rab thabs //
T02TD1676E:230a-15: yi ge mtshan ma sku yi gnas //
T02TD1676E:230a-16: yan lag rnam gsum ldan byas te //
T02TD1676E:230a-17: gsal ba nyid kyi sgo nas brtsam //
T02TD1676E:230a-19: rtse gcig gnas su 'khor ba dang //
T02TD1676E:230a-20: las dang rgyu dang 'phro ba las //
T02TD1676E:230a-21: mchod bskul las mdzad bsdu byed cing //
T02TD1676E:230a-23: aom badzra satva ma h'a sa ma ya a'a:h'um sv'ah'a /
T02TD1676E:230a-24: thun mong gi gsang sngags yi ge bcu bzhi pa'o //
T02TD1676E:230a-25: so so'i las la snyoms zhugs nas //
T02TD1676E:230a-26: rang gi thun mtshan sngags yig bcas //
T02TD1676E:230a-28: sku gsung thugs kyi gsal grub pa'o //
T02TD1676E:230a-29: aom ma h'a su kha badzra satva a'a:/
T02TD1676E:230a-32: khyad par gyi snying po yi ge bco brgyad pa'o //
T02TD1676E:230a-33: sngags gzhan rim bzhin gsal ldan pas //
T02TD1676E:230a-34: go rims 'khrul med bzlas brjod bya ;
T02TD1676E:230a-35: / las rdzogs mchod bstod bskul byas nas //
T02TD1676E:230a-36: rang gi gnas su bsdu bar bya //
T02TD1676E:230a-37: thun mtshams gzhan du bsam bya ba //
T02TD1676E:230a-38: bzlas brjod khyad par phyed pa'i tshad //
T02TD1676E:230a-39: bzhi'am drug tu rim bzhin bzla //
T02TD1676E:230a-40: kun bzang mchod pa nas brtsams ta //
T02TD1676E:230a-41: de mthar phyin pa'i las rdzogs nas //
T02TD1676E:230a-42: glu gar dbyangs kyis dngos grub bskul //
T02TD1676E:230a-43: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor gsal byas nas //
T02TD1676E:230a-44: tshogs gnyis rdzogs par sgrub byed pa'i //
T02TD1676E:230a-45: tshogs kyi dga' bde'i longs spyod kyis //
T02TD1676E:230a-46: rnal 'byor bcas pa mnyes par bya //
T02TD1676E:230a-47: lha rnams mnyes shing tshim pa dang //
T02TD1676E:230a-48: las kun bsgrub par bya ba'i phyir /
T02TD1676E:230b-0: @230b las rnams ma lus bsdus pa yi //
T02TD1676E:230b-1: sbyin sreg cho ga rgyas par brtsam //
T02TD1676E:230b-3: lhag pa'i mchod pas mnyes byas nas //
T02TD1676E:230b-4: rang gi las la sbyar bya ste //
T02TD1676E:230b-5: dngos grub don phyir mtshams su gzhag / nang par dkyil 'khor mchod bstod cing //
T02TD1676E:230b-6: bskor bcas rgyun du bshags te gdon //
T02TD1676E:230b-7: ye shes dam tshig gnyis med bsdu //
T02TD1676E:230b-8: rdul tshon gtsang ma'i gnas su gzhag / rdo rje sems dpa' dpal sbyor ba //
T02TD1676E:230b-9: ji lta'i gzugs dang dbyibs su ldan //
T02TD1676E:230b-10: bde ba nyid kyis kun du bdag / kun gyis bdag la gzhug par bya //
T02TD1676E:230b-11: chags med cing ma chags med //
T02TD1676E:230b-12: dbu mar yang ni dmigs su med //
T02TD1676E:230b-13: bud med kun gyi rgyu sbyor 'di //
T02TD1676E:230b-14: gnyis su med pa'i theg pa'i mchog / mnyam nyid dkyil 'khor kun gyi gzhi //
T02TD1676E:230b-15: don dam bde ba chen po'i sku //
T02TD1676E:230b-16: de bzhin nyid dang dbyings ye shes kyi //
T02TD1676E:230b-17: lha nyid brtson pas bsgom par bya //
T02TD1676E:230b-18: mdzod gnas dpa' bo'i gzugs brnyan mchog / rin chen sna lnga'i phreng bas 'khrigs //
T02TD1676E:230b-19: tshon gang zla nyi'i gdan la gnas //
T02TD1676E:230b-20: pho brang sgo bzhi gdan padma //
T02TD1676E:230b-21: chos kyi snying po nyid shu gcig //
T02TD1676E:230b-23: mi gsal gsal ba'i rnam par brtag /'phro 'dus rigs kyi skur rdzogs shing //
T02TD1676E:230b-24: rgyan chas cha lugs gsal byas te //
T02TD1676E:230b-25: rang gi phrin las spro byed pa'o //
T02TD1676E:230b-26: phyag rgya bzhi rdzogs dbang bskur ldan //
T02TD1676E:230b-27: ye shes dkyil 'khor gnyis med bstim //
T02TD1676E:230b-28: mchod bstod las la bskul gsal 'grub //
T02TD1676E:230b-29: yun ring mtshan ma lnga yi mthar //
T02TD1676E:230b-30: dkyil 'khor rgyas pa la dmigs te //
T02TD1676E:230b-31: kun gyi gsang ba'i mdzod rgyas par //
T02TD1676E:230b-32: dmigs pa gcig bzhin gsal ba ru //
T02TD1676E:230b-33: brten par gyur nas spro bar bya //
T02TD1676E:230b-34: rgya cher gnas gsum rdo rje la //
T02TD1676E:230b-35: bum pa'i khang par dkyil 'khor bsgom //
T02TD1676E:230b-36: rim bzhin gtso bo'i rnam pa gnas //
T02TD1676E:230b-37: 'khor gyi lha mo mthar thug par //
T02TD1676E:230b-38: dkyil 'khor gnyis med rdzogs pa'i mthar //
T02TD1676E:230b-39: mnyes mdzad 'gro ba'i don la sbyar //
T02TD1676E:230b-40: dpa' bo mtshan ma gsang gsum sngags //
T02TD1676E:231a-0: @231a * // gnas kun bar chad med par brtsam //
T02TD1676E:231a-1: smig rgyu du ba srin bu me //
T02TD1676E:231a-2: mar me zla nyi'i 'od bzhin du //
T02TD1676E:231a-3: thig le rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor gyis //
T02TD1676E:231a-4: phyag rgya chen po'i lam la sbyor //
T02TD1676E:231a-5: gnyis med rol pa'i mkha' gsang du //
T02TD1676E:231a-6: gtso bo'i mtshan ma gsal gyur nas //
T02TD1676E:231a-7: bum par rten dang brten pa'i lha //
T02TD1676E:231a-8: gtso bo nas bzung rim par bsgom //
T02TD1676E:231a-9: phyag rgya rgyan chas cha lugs kyi //
T02TD1676E:231a-10: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor rdzogs pa dang //
T02TD1676E:231a-11: phyag rgya bzhis mtshan dbang bskur 'bras //
T02TD1676E:231a-12: skye mched byin brlabs gsal bar bya //
T02TD1676E:231a-13: ye shes lha dang sbyor gnas nas //
T02TD1676E:231a-14: dman pa'i phyag rgya bzhi yis gdab //
T02TD1676E:231a-15: mchod bstod 'gro ba'i don spro ba //
T02TD1676E:231a-16: rim bzhin mtshan ma lnga yi bar //
T02TD1676E:231a-17: lha rnams kun sbyor gnas rgyas par //
T02TD1676E:231a-18: rnam gcig bskul gsal ji lta bar //
T02TD1676E:231a-19: spro dang bsdu ba'i tshul brtan pa //
T02TD1676E:231a-20: phra rags dkyil 'khor mthar phyin pa'o //
T02TD1676E:231a-21: des ni phrin las dngos grub kyi ;
T02TD1676E:231a-22: / phra mo'i las kun brtsams pas 'grung //
T02TD1676E:231a-23: de ltar thig le phra mo'i tshul //
T02TD1676E:231a-24: dkyil 'khor lha yi rnam dag gi //
T02TD1676E:231a-25: mtshan mas dmigs pa spyang byas te //
T02TD1676E:231a-26: chos sku'i phyag rgya chen por gnas //
T02TD1676E:231a-27: gang zag bzhi yi dbye ba yis //
T02TD1676E:231a-28: rang gi phrin las sbyor ba'i mthus //
T02TD1676E:231a-29: bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi rdzogs te //
T02TD1676E:231a-30: mchog gyur phyag rgya bzhi mthar phyin //
T02TD1676E:231a-31: bsnyen sgrub sbyor ba bzhi dag gis //
T02TD1676E:231a-32: dang po'i dkyil 'khor mnyes byas pa //
T02TD1676E:231a-33: spyi yi bsnyen pa dang po ste //
T02TD1676E:231a-34: thun mong bzhi yi dkyil 'khor yin //
T02TD1676E:231a-36: rdo rje sems dpa' bsgrub 'dod pas ;
T02TD1676E:231a-37: / bar chad med par zhi rgyas dbang //
T02TD1676E:231a-38: phrin las sna tshogs sgo dag nas //
T02TD1676E:231a-39: nye ba'i bsnyen pa brtsam pa'i phyir //
T02TD1676E:231a-41: dang po zhi ba chen po'i las //
T02TD1676E:231a-42: rgyud spyang bsrung zhing lhag gnas dang //
T02TD1676E:231a-43: dngos grub shis pa brtag pa'i phyir //
T02TD1676E:231a-44: rnam snang dkyil 'khor nye bar bsnyen //
T02TD1676E:231a-45: de bzhin nyid nas brtsam bya ste //
T02TD1676E:231a-46: phreng bas brgyan pa'i bar du bsgom //
T02TD1676E:231a-47: nang gi dkyil 'khor dbyings dag ni //
T02TD1676E:231a-48: re'u mig zlum po 'khor los brgyan //
T02TD1676E:231a-49: 'khor lo'i phreng bas rnam par spras //
T02TD1676E:231a-50: sna tshogs padma'i gdan gyis mtshan //
T02TD1676E:231b-0: phyi rol rab @231b dur khrod dang //
T02TD1676E:231b-1: kun 'byung khor yug tu bzhis mtshan //
T02TD1676E:231b-2: mngon par byang chub rnam lnga yis //
T02TD1676E:231b-3: mgon po rgyu yi sems dpa' bskyed //
T02TD1676E:231b-4: sku mdog rgyan cha nas bzung ste //

T02TD1676E:235a-45: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod tshogs dag //
T02TD1676E:235a-46: byin rlabs sngags dang phyag rgyas dbul //

T02TD1676E:235a-51: dkyil 'khor de nyid gang rung gis //
T02TD1676E:235a-52: mtshan ma'i dmigs pa brtan par bya //
T02TD1676E:235b-0: pho brang bkra shis mtshan ldan @235b du ;

T02TD1676E:235b-2: bdud rtsis bkang ba bsgrub pa'i mchog //
T02TD1676E:235b-3: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor phyag rgya ra bcas //
T02TD1676E:235b-4: gsang sngags mtha' rgyan ma nyams par //
T02TD1676E:235b-6: bskul tshig glu dbyangs phyag rgya'i gar //
T02TD1676E:235b-7: bza' btung tshogs bcas rol pas spyad //
T02TD1676E:235b-8: lha mnyes mgron tshim las grub byed //
T02TD1676E:235b-9: tshogs sgrub sbyin sreg lhag ma'i las //
T02TD1676E:235b-10: las rdzogs mchod bstod bskul byas shing //
T02TD1676E:235b-11: rang gi gnas su bsdus nas ni //
T02TD1676E:235b-12: mtshan ma kun dang yongs bral ba'i //
T02TD1676E:235b-13: gnyis med dbyings su gnas par bya ;
T02TD1676E:235b-15: chags pa'i nyes pas mi gos pa //
T02TD1676E:235b-16: rnal 'byor ldan pas de bzhin du //
T02TD1676E:235b-17: gnas kyi nyes pas yong mi gos //
T02TD1676E:235b-18: thams cad rgyas bar bya ba'i phyir //
T02TD1676E:235b-19: rdo rje nyi ma'i tshogs sgrub ste //
T02TD1676E:235b-20: dpal dang bzi mdangs kun grub pa'i //
T02TD1676E:235b-21: rgyas pa'i longs spyod dgod par bya //
T02TD1676E:235b-22: gzhi yi ting 'dzin nas bzung ste //
T02TD1676E:235b-23: phreng bas brgyan pa'i bar du bsgom //
T02TD1676E:235b-24: pho brang nang gi mtshan bcas sogs //
T02TD1676E:235b-25: rin chen 'bar ba cha brgyad pa //
T02TD1676E:235b-26: nyis rim lte ba re'u cha dgu //
T02TD1676E:235b-27: rin chen phreng ba mu khyud 'dzin //
T02TD1676E:235b-28: ka ba mchog brgyad rin chen tog //
T02TD1676E:235b-29: sna bdun padma'i gdan gyis mtshan //
T02TD1676E:235b-30: phyi rol rab dur khrod dang //
T02TD1676E:235b-32: mngon par byang chub rnam lnga yis //
T02TD1676E:235b-33: mgon po rgyu yi sems dpa' bskyed //
T02TD1676E:235b-34: sku mdog rgyan cha nas bzung ste //
T02TD1676E:235b-35: byin rlabs sprul pas dag par bsgom //
T02TD1676E:235b-36: rang 'od rig ma bskyed pa nas //
T02TD1676E:235b-37: lha mos bskul ba'i mthar thug brtsam //
T02TD1676E:235b-38: thugs rjes 'gro ba'i rgyud gzigs te //

T02TD1676E:237a-29: lhag pa'i thugs gnyis dbri dkrol med //
