T02TD1676E:237a-31: aom tsinta ma ni ho ma h'a mu dra hram /
T02TD1676E:237a-32: drag po bskal pas 'khrigs byas nas //
T02TD1676E:237a-33: mi mthun gnas kyi rgyud kun bsreg / kun spyod yon tan mthar phyin pa'i //
T02TD1676E:237a-34: gsung gsum rten bcas 'gro la ston //
T02TD1676E:237a-35: aom badzra ma sh'ama h'a shum mah'a mu dra tram ;
T02TD1676E:237a-36: tram khams gsum kun gyi rgyal srid bdag / sna tshogs mchog gi nor ldan pas //
T02TD1676E:237a-38: rnam mang sangs rgyas kyis 'dul ga / rnam pa sna tshogs 'jal dum las //
T02TD1676E:237a-39: rnam par gyal ba'i rgyal mtshan can //
T02TD1676E:237a-40: rdo rje nyi ma'i rgyal po yi //
T02TD1676E:237a-41: bde mchog sgyu ma bstan du gsol //
T02TD1676E:237a-42: sems can sprin la byang chub sems //
T02TD1676E:237a-43: mchog sbyin sna tshogs char 'bebs pa //
T02TD1676E:237a-44: bdag gi re ba thams cad bsgrub //
T02TD1676E:237a-45: myur ston aa la la la ho //
T02TD1676E:237a-46: mi zad gter gyi dbang bskur ba //
T02TD1676E:237a-47: khyab par bdag la bstan du gsol //
T02TD1676E:237a-48: h'um pa pa ta ta tra tra ta ta /
T02TD1676E:237b-0: rdo rje @237b thal mo mnyam sbyar la //
T02TD1676E:237b-1: mdzub mo mnyam par phyir bkug ste //
T02TD1676E:237b-2: mthe bo rdo rje g-yogs pa ni //
T02TD1676E:237b-3: rdo rje dpal gyi nor bu yin //
T02TD1676E:237b-4: rdo rje khu tshur rin chen mchog /'bebs pa thams cad yongs rdzogs pa'o //
T02TD1676E:237b-5: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod tshogs bdag / byin rlabs sngags dang phyag rgya 'bul //
T02TD1676E:237b-6: mnyam med mi g-yo la sogs pa'i //
T02TD1676E:237b-7: bstod pa'i phyag rgyas mnyes par bya //
T02TD1676E:237b-8: smon lam rgya chen btab byas nas //
T02TD1676E:237b-9: slar brjod thig le phra mo dang //
T02TD1676E:237b-10: dkyil 'khor de nyid gang rung gis //
T02TD1676E:237b-11: mtshon ma'i dkyil 'khor brtan par bya //
T02TD1676E:237b-12: 'byor tshogs yon tan rgyas pa'i phyir //
T02TD1676E:237b-13: rin chen snod bzang legs spras par //
T02TD1676E:237b-14: dkyil 'khor pho brang thig gi sa dbye //
T02TD1676E:237b-15: bza' btung brda sbyor bdud rtsis bkang //
T02TD1676E:237b-17: glu gar dbyangs kyi sprul par bya //
T02TD1676E:237b-18: gnyis med rol pas longs spyod cing //
T02TD1676E:237b-19: rten gyi dkyil 'khor bcang bar bya //
T02TD1676E:237b-20: lha mnyes mgron tshim las grub byed //
T02TD1676E:237b-21: tshogs 'khor sbyin sreg lhag ma'i las //
T02TD1676E:237b-22: las rdzogs mchod bstod bskul byas shing //
T02TD1676E:237b-23: rang gi gnas su bsdus nas ni //
T02TD1676E:237b-24: mtshan ma kun dang yongs bral ba'i //
T02TD1676E:237b-25: mnyam nyid dbyings su gnas par bya //
T02TD1676E:237b-26: shin tu gdug cing drag bo la //
T02TD1676E:237b-27: zhi bas phan par mi 'gyur te ;
T02TD1676E:237b-28: / shes rab thabs kyi sbyor ba ni //
T02TD1676E:237b-29: rnam par rgyal phyir rab tu drag / sna tshogs las rnams brtsam pa'i phyir //
T02TD1676E:237b-30: rta mchog dkyil 'khor mchod bya ste //
T02TD1676E:237b-31: bro gar rgya'i tshigs bcas pas //
T02TD1676E:237b-32: rang gi las gzung rnam par 'phrul //
T02TD1676E:237b-33: de bzhin nyid nas brtsam bya ste //
T02TD1676E:237b-34: phreng bas brgyan pa'i bar du bsgom //
T02TD1676E:237b-35: nang gi dkyil 'khor dbyibs dag ni //
T02TD1676E:237b-37: 'khor los mtshan pa mu khyad mchog //
T02TD1676E:237b-38: rim gnyis rgya gram padma'i gdan //
T02TD1676E:237b-39: phyi rol rab dur khrod dang //
T02TD1676E:237b-40: kun 'byung khor yug grub zhis mtshan //
T02TD1676E:237b-41: mngon par byang chub rnam lnga yis //
T02TD1676E:237b-42: mgon po rgyu yi sems dpa' bskyed //
T02TD1676E:237b-43: sku mdog rgyan cha nas bzung ste //
T02TD1676E:237b-44: byin brlabs rdzogs pas dag par bya //
T02TD1676E:237b-45: rang 'od rig ma bskyed pa nas //
T02TD1676E:237b-46: lha mos bskul ba'i mthar thug brtsam //
T02TD1676E:237b-47: thugs rjes 'gro rgyud gzigs mdzad de //
T02TD1676E:238a-0: ham yig rgya gram las byung @238a * //
T02TD1676E:238a-3: rta mchog ljang ser zhal gsum pa //
T02TD1676E:238a-4: dbus steng rta mgo ljang sngon bcas //
T02TD1676E:238a-5: bgegs ba cas drag tshul zhi mdangs khros //
T02TD1676E:238a-6: lag dang brgyad ba dpa' bo'i mchog / g-yas pas bdan [*bden?] gsum pa'i phyag /'degs pa'i tshul du mdzad pa dang //
T02TD1676E:238a-7: gnyis pa rdo rje rgya gram 'dzin //
T02TD1676E:238a-8: 'og ma gnyis na ral gri mda' //
T02TD1676E:238a-9: g-yon gyi sa sna tshogs padma dang //
T02TD1676E:238a-10: shag ti rtse gcig be chon gzu //
T02TD1676E:238a-11: g-yas kyi rmig pa dang po yis //
T02TD1676E:238a-12: dngos grub gsum dang dpal mo gnon //
T02TD1676E:238a-13: gnyis pas zhi la dga' ba mo //
T02TD1676E:238a-14: g-yon pas drag po khyab 'jug dang /
T02TD1676E:238a-15: gnyis pas tshang pa 'dod pa'i lha //
T02TD1676E:238a-16: rin chen sna tshogs rgyan dang gos //
T02TD1676E:238a-17: khro 'jum phrag rgya lnga yis spras //
T02TD1676E:238a-18: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje dang //
T02TD1676E:238a-19: ye shes sems dpa' sngags dang bcas //
T02TD1676E:238a-20: sangs rgyas kun gyis dbang bskur zhing //
T02TD1676E:238a-21: dbu la rigs kyi bdag pos brgyan //
T02TD1676E:238a-22: sangs rgyas rin chen padmo dbang //
T02TD1676E:238a-23: de bzhin rdo rje rin chen dang //
T02TD1676E:238a-24: yid bzhin nor bu rin chen mchog / rta mchog rab tu 'grub par 'gyur //
T02TD1676E:238a-26: rgya gram phred ba'i phyag rgya dang //
T02TD1676E:238a-27: dar dpyangs dgyes pa'i thal mor bcas //
T02TD1676E:238a-29: / gsang gnas h'um dang aas brgyan te //
T02TD1676E:238a-30: rgya gram 'bar ba phat dang bcas //
T02TD1676E:238a-31: rnam par thar pa ae dkyil can //
T02TD1676E:238a-32: sam aa sogs brdas bskul nas //
T02TD1676E:238a-33: dza:h'um bam ho:sa rol pa bya //
T02TD1676E:238a-35: brla yi dbus su gzhug bya ste //
T02TD1676E:238a-36: ling+ga sna tshogs rdo rje ste ;
T02TD1676E:238a-37: / rta yi rgyal por bdag sngon ba skyed //
T02TD1676E:238a-38: gsang gnas so so'i gdan dag la //
T02TD1676E:238a-39: chos kyi snying pos lha rnams bskyed //
T02TD1676E:238a-40: ham gi rta mchog rgyal po ste //
T02TD1676E:238a-41: gsang gnas dbus kyi gdan la'o //
T02TD1676E:238a-42: dz'i las sna tshogs padma'i rgya //
T02TD1676E:238a-43: ha las sna tshogs rdo rje ma //
T02TD1676E:238a-44: khyad par rta yi lha mo ste ;
T02TD1676E:238a-45: / g-yas g-yon phyogs kyi padma la'o //
T02TD1676E:238a-46: 'khor ga zhan rigs rnams gang rung gi //
T02TD1676E:238a-47: lha mo nyi shu gong ma bzhin //
T02TD1676E:238a-48: bha gar ling+ga bcug nas ni //
T02TD1676E:238a-49: der ni h'um yig bsgom par bya //
T02TD1676E:238a-50: rta mchog rol pa'i gzugs dag ni //
T02TD1676E:238a-51: sku gnyis ldan pas spro bya'o //
T02TD1676E:238a-52: aom sumpha ni sumpha h'um dzdza /
T02TD1676E:238b-0: @238b phyogs bcur don byas 'dus pa dag / gtso bo yab yum la gzug bya //
T02TD1676E:238b-2: mtshan mthun phyag rgya g-yas kyi phyogs /
T02TD1676E:238b-3: aom bhi sha badzra dha bo dzdza:/
T02TD1676E:238b-4: sna tshogs rdo rje ljang sngon 'phro //
T02TD1676E:238b-5: mtshan mthun phyag 'dzin g-yon gyi phyogs //
T02TD1676E:238b-6: aom bham sha badzra sa tva dzdza //
T02TD1676E:238b-7: 'khor gzhan lha mo tshogs bcas pa //
T02TD1676E:238b-8: sna tshogs rdo rje rgyan phreng mdzes //
T02TD1676E:238b-9: byin rlabs dbang bskur rdzogs byas pas //
T02TD1676E:238b-10: dam tshig dkyil 'khor gsal bar snang //
T02TD1676E:238b-11: sbyor bas rang rigs dkyil 'khor bskul //
T02TD1676E:238b-12: sna tshogs tshul gyis mdun du bzhugs //
T02TD1676E:238b-13: dpal ldan rdo rje 'gying ba'i thabs //
T02TD1676E:238b-16: gang ngam 'on te stong yang rung //
T02TD1676E:238b-17: yang na ci 'byor pa yis kyang //
T02TD1676E:238b-18: dam tshig mnyam par bsgrub pa yis //
T02TD1676E:238b-20: tshad med bzhi yi sbyor ba yis //
T02TD1676E:238b-21: lha rnams gnyis su med par bya //
T02TD1676E:238b-22: h'um rnal 'byor de nyid bcom ldan 'das //
T02TD1676E:238b-23: rdo rje sems dpa' de bzhin gshegs //
T02TD1676E:238b-24: drag shul sbyor bas rnams sbyor ba //
T02TD1676E:238b-25: rtag mchog phyag rgyas rab tu gnas //
T02TD1676E:238b-26: thams cad padmo mos pa yis //
T02TD1676E:238b-27: sdig med stobs kyi ngo 'thon du //
T02TD1676E:238b-28: rab tu gnon pa'i stsal dag gis //
T02TD1676E:238b-30: 'dod chags can la g-yem par ston //
T02TD1676E:238b-31: gdug pa rnams las gdug par 'gyur //
T02TD1676E:238b-32: zhi ba rnams la zhi ba'i mchog / drag shul can la drag shul sbyor //
T02TD1676E:238b-33: zhal bzhi pa la phyag bzhi pa //
T02TD1676E:238b-34: zhal bzhi pa la rmig pa bzhin //
T02TD1676E:238b-35: rta mgrin rgyal po chen po ste //
T02TD1676E:238b-37: g-yon pa'i khu tshur mdzub mo yis //
T02TD1676E:238b-39: rdo rjer bcas shing slong ba 'grub //
T02TD1676E:238b-40: g-yas pa sab dan gsum pa byas //
T02TD1676E:238b-41: g-yas dang g-yon pa'i sbyor pa yis //
T02TD1676E:238b-42: brkyang bskum pa yi tshul byas nas //
T02TD1676E:238b-43: khro bo'i skyil mo krung bcas te //
T02TD1676E:238b-44: 'jig rten thams cad rab tu bshig //
T02TD1676E:238b-45: ham myos byed stong pas lhag pa yi //
T02TD1676E:238b-46: bde bar 'dod pa'i gzugs ston pa //
T02TD1676E:238b-47: 'dul ba'i dbang gis gshin rje'i chogs //
T02TD1676E:238b-48: stong pas lhag par rab tu 'jigs //
T02TD1676E:238b-49: zhi ba'i skur yang tshangs pa'i tshogs //
T02TD1676E:238b-50: stong pas shin tu lhag par ston //
T02TD1676E:238b-51: dkyil 'khor kun gyi mchog dag tu //
T02TD1676E:239a-2: thams cad dag par mos pa yis //
T02TD1676E:239a-3: do 'thon stobs kyis non pas gnon //
T02TD1676E:239a-4: ae hi ai hi dbang phyug tshogs //
T02TD1676E:239a-5: thams cad rab shig rab tu shig / rab kyi rtsal gyis non pa yis //
T02TD1676E:239a-6: stobs kyi ngo 'thon dbang phyug gnon //
T02TD1676E:239a-7: sbyor chen hu lu hu lu yi //
T02TD1676E:239a-8: mig gsum pa las gsum grub drongs //
T02TD1676E:239a-9: rab kyi rtsal gyis mngon gnon pa'i //
T02TD1676E:239a-10: stobs kyis po 'thon mthu chen gnon //
T02TD1676E:239a-11: mnyam sbyor ru tra ma snying las //
T02TD1676E:239a-12: dpal mi drongs shes rab drongs shig / rab kyi rtsal gyis gnon pa yis //
T02TD1676E:239a-13: stobs kyi ngo 'thon tshang pa gnon /
T02TD1676E:239a-14: sbyor chen tshangs pa'i sgyu ma las //
T02TD1676E:239a-15: sgrol ma drongs shig smar ta //
T02TD1676E:239a-16: rab kyi rtsal gyis gnon pa yi //
T02TD1676E:239a-17: stobs kyis ngo 'thon dga' dbang gnon //
T02TD1676E:239a-18: mnyam sbyor kun gyis bdag la dga' //
T02TD1676E:239a-19: drongs shig aa la la la ho //
T02TD1676E:239a-20: gdug cig khro la rab gtum pa'i //
T02TD1676E:239a-21: sems can bsgral ba'i phyir bsgrub zhugs //
T02TD1676E:239a-22: aa la la ho aa la la la ho //
T02TD1676E:239a-23: aom su mbha ni sumbha h'um pat /
T02TD1676E:239a-25: mdza' bo mi la bya ba'ang min //
T02TD1676E:239a-26: yongs rtog de dag med kyang bla //
T02TD1676E:239a-27: de 'dra'i mdza' bo sgyu bzhin pas //
T02TD1676E:239a-28: de la mdza' zhes su zhig zer //
T02TD1676E:239a-29: rgol ba mi la byang min //
T02TD1676E:239a-30: yongs su rtog pa med kyang bla //
T02TD1676E:239a-32: de la su zhig pa zhes zer /
T02TD1676E:239a-33: aom shr'i padma ba da ba ma kha yo ge shvari hi hi hi hi ham /
T02TD1676E:239a-34: rdo rje thal mi mnyam sbyar nas //
T02TD1676E:239a-35: mthe'u chung srin lag mnyam par brkyang //
T02TD1676E:239a-36: mdzu ba mo rtse bsnyams bkug pa ni //
T02TD1676E:239a-37: dpal mchog rta zhes grangs pa yi //
T02TD1676E:239a-38: rdo rje khu tshur dpal bcings la //
T02TD1676E:239a-39: sor mo thams cad yongs su bzung //
T02TD1676E:239a-40: de ltar phyag rgya gong ma dang //
T02TD1676E:239a-41: rang rang las la sbyar bar bya //
T02TD1676E:239a-42: phyin nga gsang ba'i mchod tshogs dag / byi rlabs sngags dang phyag rgyas dbul //
T02TD1676E:239a-43: mnyam med mi g-yo la sogs pa'i //
T02TD1676E:239a-44: bstod pa'i phyag rgyas mnyes par bya //
T02TD1676E:239a-45: smon lam rgya chen gdab byas nas //
T02TD1676E:239a-46: bzlas brjod thig le phra mo dang //
T02TD1676E:239a-47: dkyil 'khor de nyid gang rung gis //
T02TD1676E:239a-48: mtshan ma'i dkyil 'khor brtan par bya //
T02TD1676E:239a-49: glu gar bro sngags phyag rgya'i tshogs //
T02TD1676E:239a-50: phrin las rnam bzhi'i bzhin ltar 'dzum //
T02TD1676E:239a-51: las kyi bskul tshig dang bcas pa'i //
T02TD1676E:239b-1: lha mnyes mgron tshim las grub byed //
T02TD1676E:239b-2: tshogs dang sbyin sreg lhag ma'i las //
T02TD1676E:239b-3: las rdzogs mchod bstod bskul byas shing //
T02TD1676E:239b-4: rang gi gnas su bsdus nas ni //
T02TD1676E:239b-5: mtshan ma kun dang yongs bral ba'i //
T02TD1676E:239b-6: mnyam nyid dbyings su gnas par bya //
T02TD1676E:239b-7: thams cad dag par mos pa yis //
T02TD1676E:239b-8: sdig med stobs kyis ngo 'thon du //
T02TD1676E:239b-9: drag shul sbyor bas mnyam sbyar bas //
T02TD1676E:239b-10: 'jig rten thams cad gzhom par byed //
T02TD1676E:239b-11: phyag rgya sgrub pa'i dus su ni //
T02TD1676E:239b-12: snga ma las ni gnas bsgyur te //
T02TD1676E:239b-13: bskal pa me dpung 'khrigs pa bzhen //
T02TD1676E:239b-14: 'bar ba'i tshogs ni rnam par bsam //
T02TD1676E:239b-15: gzhi dang rten pa'i ting 'dzin nyid //
T02TD1676E:239b-16: sbyor ba bzhi yis gsal byas te //
T02TD1676E:239b-17: dam tshig 'phro 'du'i yan lag dag / mngon sum snang ba ltar gnas nas //
T02TD1676E:239b-18: ye shes dkyil 'khor la dmigs shing //
T02TD1676E:239b-19: mdun nas gnyis med dkyil 'khor gyi //
T02TD1676E:239b-20: cho ga rdzogs par spyad byas pas ;
T02TD1676E:239b-21: / ye shes dkyil 'khor bsgrub par bya //
T02TD1676E:239b-22: 'khor bcas mchod pa rdzogs nas ni //
T02TD1676E:239b-23: bsnyen pa'i lung bzhin brtson pas 'bad //
T02TD1676E:239b-24: bsnyen par gnas pa'i dbang thob nas //
T02TD1676E:239b-25: bsgom dbyangs yin ge 'bru brgyad bstan //
T02TD1676E:239b-27: dbyangs drug blangs pas don drug gsal //
T02TD1676E:239b-28: sngags mchog yi ge'i 'bru brjod pas //
T02TD1676E:239b-29: des ni drag po'i dkyil 'khor bskyed //
T02TD1676E:239b-30: dge mchog dngos grub kun bsdus te //
T02TD1676E:239b-31: gnas gsum bskor zhing gsang mchog sgrub //
T02TD1676E:239b-32: khyad par gsang sngags rim pa bzhin //
T02TD1676E:239b-34: mthar phyin gsang sngags rgyal po yis //
T02TD1676E:239b-35: las kyi sbyor ba kun brtsam bya //
T02TD1676E:239b-36: mnyes shing mgron tshim las grub byed //
T02TD1676E:239b-37: tshogs dang sbyin sreg lhag pa'i las //
T02TD1676E:239b-38: las rdzogs mchod bstod bskul byas shing //
T02TD1676E:239b-39: rang gi gnas su bsdus nas ni //
T02TD1676E:239b-40: mtshan ma kun dang yongs bral ba'i //
T02TD1676E:239b-41: mnyam nyid dbyings su gnas par bya //
T02TD1676E:239b-42: thams cad nam mkha'i mtshan nyid de //
T02TD1676E:239b-43: nam mkha' la yang mtshan nyid med //
T02TD1676E:239b-44: khams gsum dag ni ma lus pa //
T02TD1676E:239b-45: thams cad sgyu ma lta bu ste //
T02TD1676E:239b-46: ji ltar sgyu ma thams cad du //
T02TD1676E:239b-47: mthong ba dang ni reg par 'gyur //
T02TD1676E:240a-1: su yod pa ma yin te //
T02TD1676E:240a-2: de bzhin 'gro ba kun gyi tshul //
T02TD1676E:240a-3: dbugs dbyung dkyil 'khor rnam drug dag / sbyor ba bzhi dang ldan par bya //
T02TD1676E:240a-4: sbyor dang rjes su sbyor ba dang //
T02TD1676E:240a-5: shin tu sbyor dang sbyor chen po //
T02TD1676E:240a-6: ye shes tsam la snyoms 'jug pa //
T02TD1676E:240a-7: sbyor ba zhes ni bshad pa yin //
T02TD1676E:240a-8: yum ldan byin brlabs rol pas mchod //
T02TD1676E:240a-9: gzhug pa rjes su sbyor ba'o //
T02TD1676E:240a-10: dag mdzad dkyil 'khor rdzogs byas nas //
T02TD1676E:240a-12: byin brlabs dbang bskur las rdzogs pa //
T02TD1676E:240a-13: sbyor ba chen po zhes bya'o //
T02TD1676E:240a-14: sgrub pa dngos grub tshul bzhin du //
T02TD1676E:240a-15: mtshan brtags gsal ba'i gnas shes pas //
T02TD1676E:240a-16: bdag gzhan don tshogs las sbyar te /
T02TD1676E:240a-17: re dog mtha' kun bral bas blang //
T02TD1676E:240a-18: de bzhin nyid nas brtsam bya ste //
T02TD1676E:240a-19: phreng bas brgyan pa'i bar du bsgom //
T02TD1676E:240a-20: nad gi dkyil 'khor dbyibs dag ni //
T02TD1676E:240a-21: thig bzhis rnam par phye ba la ;
T02TD1676E:240a-22: / so so'i pho brang ji ltar bar //
T02TD1676E:240a-23: rigs bsdus dkyil 'khor rgyas pa'i tshul //
T02TD1676E:240a-24: dbus su rigs bdag 'khor lo ste //
T02TD1676E:240a-25: shar du de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs //
T02TD1676E:240a-26: lho phyogs rdo rje dra po'i tshogs //
T02TD1676E:240a-27: nub tu padma rnam dag chos //
T02TD1676E:240a-28: byang phyogs yon tan rin chen mdzod //
T02TD1676E:240a-29: shar mtshams bzhi dkyil sdud pa'i tshul //
T02TD1676E:240a-30: lho mtshams drag po sreg byed ltar //
T02TD1676E:240a-31: nub mtshams dbang mdzad g-yo ba'i bzhin //
T02TD1676E:240a-32: byang mtshams rgyas pa dbang chen ltar //
T02TD1676E:240a-33: rang dang phreng bas mdzes par bya //
T02TD1676E:240a-34: pho brang kha dog rin chen bzhi //
T02TD1676E:240a-35: sna tshogs padma gdan gyis mtshan //
T02TD1676E:240a-36: phyi rol ra ba dur khrod dang //
T02TD1676E:240a-37: kun 'byung khor yug tu bzhis mtshan //
T02TD1676E:240a-38: mngon par byang chub rnam lnga yis //
T02TD1676E:240a-39: mgon po rgyu yi sems dpa' bskyed //
T02TD1676E:240a-40: sku mdog rgyan cha nas bzung ste //
T02TD1676E:240a-41: byin rlabs rdzogs pas dag par bya //
T02TD1676E:240a-42: rang 'od rig ma bskyed pa nas //
T02TD1676E:240a-43: lha mos bskul ba'i mthar thug bar //
T02TD1676E:240a-44: thugs rjes 'gro rgyud la gzigs nas //
T02TD1676E:240a-46: thig le rin chen sna lnga'i mdangs //
T02TD1676E:240a-47: phyogs mtshams dbus kyi lte ba la //
T02TD1676E:240a-49: sngags kyi phyag rgya chen po'i sku //
T02TD1676E:240a-50: sku mdog phyag chan rgyan cha dang //
T02TD1676E:240b-0: cha lugs @240b so so'i dkyil 'khor bzhin //
T02TD1676E:240b-1: sku gsungs thugs kyi rdo rje dang //
T02TD1676E:240b-2: ye shes sems sems dpa' sngags dang bcas //
T02TD1676E:240b-3: sangs rgyas kun gyis dbang bskur zhing //
T02TD1676E:240b-4: dbu la rigs kyi bdag pos mtshan //
T02TD1676E:240b-5: so so'i dbang bskur phyag rgya dang //
T02TD1676E:240b-6: rang gi gsang sngags bcas pa'o //
T02TD1676E:240b-7: rin chen myu gu la sogs dang //
T02TD1676E:240b-8: dar dbyangs dgyes pa'i thal mor bcas //
T02TD1676E:240b-9: so so'i yum dang 'khril ba las //
T02TD1676E:240b-10: gsang gnas byin rlabs bcas bskul te //
T02TD1676E:240b-11: snyoms 'jug chos kyi snying po las //
T02TD1676E:240b-12: rigs dgu'i dkyil 'khor gsal bar bsgom //
T02TD1676E:240b-13: phyi nang sngags kyis spro mdzad nas ;
T02TD1676E:240b-15: byin rlabs dbang bskur rdzogs byas pas //
T02TD1676E:240b-17: ye shes dkyil 'khor rgyas dmigs pas //
T02TD1676E:240b-18: mdun gyi dkyil 'khor mnyes par bya //
T02TD1676E:240b-19: gnyis med dkyil 'khor rgyas btab nas //
T02TD1676E:240b-20: cho ga lhag mas mnyes par bya //
T02TD1676E:240b-21: rnam shes ye shes bye brag gis //
T02TD1676E:240b-22: dkyil 'khor drug gi rim pa bzhin //
T02TD1676E:240b-23: yi ge gcig pa'i sngags bzlas shing //
T02TD1676E:240b-24: las bzhi'i bskul sngags gsang ba la //
T02TD1676E:240b-25: mtha' brgyan gyur pas gsol gdab cing //
T02TD1676E:240b-27: / glu dbyangs gar gyis bskul bar bya //
T02TD1676E:240b-28: rnam shes ye shes bye brag gis //
T02TD1676E:240b-29: mtshan ma gang rung gsal bar brtag / rdo rjes mi mthun 'joms byed cing //
T02TD1676E:240b-31: mda' yis phra bar 'bigs byed cing //
T02TD1676E:240b-32: ral gris lha min grong khyer 'joms //
T02TD1676E:240b-34: rtse gsum lha dbang du la 'gyur zhing //
T02TD1676E:240b-35: bum pas bkra shis bdud rtsi 'grub //
T02TD1676E:240b-37: nyi mas gser mdog 'od dang ldan //
T02TD1676E:240b-38: lcags kyus srid pa'i rtse mor 'gro //
T02TD1676E:240b-39: nor bus grong khyer rgyas par byed ;
T02TD1676E:240b-40: / me long mngon par shes pa 'grub //
T02TD1676E:240b-41: pi wang sna tshogs gsung sgrogs shing //
T02TD1676E:240b-42: gling bus chos kyi tshig brjod pa'o //
T02TD1676E:240b-43: gzhan yang gzugs sogs mang bshad pa'i //
T02TD1676E:240b-44: yul drug snang ba'i mtshan ma kun //
T02TD1676E:240b-45: ting 'dzin sngags dang las sbyar zhing //
T02TD1676E:241a-2: g-yas g-yon nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor la //
T02TD1676E:241a-3: yab yum sa bon bcu gnyis bsgom //
T02TD1676E:241a-4: zung du spros shing 'dus pa las //
T02TD1676E:241a-5: rigs kyi lha tshogs snyoms 'jug pa'o //
T02TD1676E:241a-6: sor mo phan tshun spyor rdzas bsnol //
T02TD1676E:241a-7: gnyis med rdo rje thal mo'i rgya//
T02TD1676E:241a-8: de rjes rdo rje bsdams pa las //
T02TD1676E:241a-9: g-yon mdzub rtse mo'i nang dag tu //
T02TD1676E:241a-10: g-yas pa'i mthe bo'i mtshan ma gzug / legs bsdams spyod pa dga' chen dpal //
T02TD1676E:241a-11: 'di ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
T02TD1676E:241a-12: thun mong sngon 'gro'i yan lag yin //
T02TD1676E:241a-13: dga' chen dpal gyi rdo rje las //
T02TD1676E:241a-14: gung mo bcings pa'i nang du gzhug / mthe bod mthe'u chung rtse mo can //
T02TD1676E:241a-15: rdo rje'i phyag rgya yongs su bsgyur //
T02TD1676E:241a-16: de las gung mo lcags kyu ni //
T02TD1676E:241a-17: snying gar sbyor ba dgug pa'i mchog / rdo rje bsdams pa byas nas ni //
T02TD1676E:241a-18: gung mo bcings pa'i nang du gzhug / mthe'u chung mthe bo'i rtse mo can //
T02TD1676E:241a-19: rdo rje'i phyag rgya yongs su bsgyur //
T02TD1676E:241a-20: de las gung mo lcags kyu ni //
T02TD1676E:241a-21: rdo rje 'khor lo snang mdzad rgya //
T02TD1676E:241a-22: rdo rje'i rgya bcings sbyor ldan pas //
T02TD1676E:241a-23: thal mo khong stong khebs pa yi //
T02TD1676E:241a-24: rdo rje'i phyag rgya bcings pa las //
T02TD1676E:241a-25: gung mo de bzhin bkug nas ni //
T02TD1676E:241a-26: rdo rje rdo rje zhes brjod de //
T02TD1676E:241a-27: gung mo nam mkha' rdo rje mchog / rdo rje bsdams pa la gnas te //
T02TD1676E:241a-28: rdo rje'i rtse mo de bzhin bsnyams //
T02TD1676E:241a-29: mdzub mo gnyis kyi rtse mo dgug / rdo rje phyag rgya dag byed pa'o //
T02TD1676E:241a-30: rdo rje padmor byas pa las //
T02TD1676E:241a-31: gung mo bcing pa'i dbus na gnas //
T02TD1676E:241a-32: mthe'u chung bsnyams pa'i rtse mo mde'u //
T02TD1676E:241a-33: rdo rje mda' ni yongs su 'phang //
T02TD1676E:241a-34: rdo rje'i phyag rgya yongs bcings na //
T02TD1676E:241a-35: gud mo bcings pa phyi rol gzhag / rdo rje sna tshogs dpal gyi rgya //
T02TD1676E:241a-36: ldang ba thams cad rab sgrub pa'o //
T02TD1676E:241a-37: lta bas mi ngoms pa yi sku //
T02TD1676E:241a-38: thams cad bdag nyid ston par mdzad //
T02TD1676E:241a-39: legs so zhes pa grub pa ni //
T02TD1676E:241a-40: dam pa dag kyang rab tu stsol //
T02TD1676E:241a-41: bsam pa thams cad yongs rdzogs pa'i //
T02TD1676E:241a-42: grub pa kun mchog nyams dga' ba //
T02TD1676E:241a-43: ji ltar 'dod pa'i longs spyod dag / thams cad kyi ni bdag nyid stsol //
T02TD1676E:241a-44: dbang phyug bde ba la sogs drug / sku dang ye shes gsal bar 'grub //
T02TD1676E:241b-0: phan gnod byed pa rnam @241b gnyis pa'i //
T02TD1676E:241b-1: gzugs dang sgra dang dri dag gi //
T02TD1676E:241b-2: mtshan ma rnam gsum snang ba na //
T02TD1676E:241b-3: bye brag tu ni shes par bya //
T02TD1676E:241b-4: gal te dngos grub mi gsal na //
T02TD1676E:241b-5: zhi rgyas dbang dang mngon spyod dang //
T02TD1676E:241b-6: mnan dang bzlog gi las brtsam zhing //
T02TD1676E:241b-7: spogs pa'i cho gas bskyar bar bya //
T02TD1676E:241b-8: lha mnyes mgron tshim las sgrub byed //
T02TD1676E:241b-9: tshogs 'khor sbyin sreg lhag ma'i las //
T02TD1676E:241b-10: las rdzogs rigs kyi sku brten pas //
T02TD1676E:241b-11: dngos grub legs sbyor 'gyur med brtan //
T02TD1676E:241b-12: mchog tu gyur ba'i phyag rgya bzhis //
T02TD1676E:241b-14: bsod nams ye shes tshogs chen po'i /
T02TD1676E:241b-15: cho gas las kun 'grub byed cing //
T02TD1676E:241b-18: rang gi lha yi sbyor ldan pas //
T02TD1676E:241b-19: rdzas rnams spyang zhing byin gyis brlab //
T02TD1676E:241b-20: gru bzhi pa la sgo bzhi pa //
T02TD1676E:241b-21: rta babs bzhi yis mdzes par byas //
T02TD1676E:241b-22: rang gi lha dang 'dra ba yis //
T02TD1676E:241b-23: bud med rnams ni legs bsgrubs pa //
T02TD1676E:241b-24: rdo rje rin chen padma sogs //
T02TD1676E:241b-25: sgo srung dang ni ldan par bya //
T02TD1676E:241b-26: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam sbyor ba //
T02TD1676E:241b-27: sbyor ba'i dbang phyug rnam 'phrul bas //
T02TD1676E:241b-28: rdo rje sems dpa' dpal gyi lha //
T02TD1676E:241b-29: de na rnam par 'phrul pa mdzad //
T02TD1676E:241b-31: sbyor ba snga ma bzhin du gsal //
T02TD1676E:241b-32: skal bzang rang gi phyag rgyas mtshan //
T02TD1676E:241b-33: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor brtag par bya //
T02TD1676E:241b-34: ye shes dkyil 'khor la dmigs shing //
T02TD1676E:241b-35: mdun gyi dkyil 'khor sprul byas la //
T02TD1676E:241b-36: tshad med phyag rgya bzhis bstims nas //
T02TD1676E:241b-37: gsang ba'i phyag rgya bzhi rgyas gdab //
T02TD1676E:241b-38: lha mo kun gyi bde ba'i mchog / mdzes pa'i zhal ni rnam 'gyur zhing //
T02TD1676E:241b-39: bde bar myong pa rab sbyar ba //
T02TD1676E:241b-40: mdzes par blta zhing gar byed pa'o //
T02TD1676E:241b-41: bud med mkhas pa sgyu ma che //
T02TD1676E:241b-42: mdzes pa'i bzhin ni rnam par 'gyur //
T02TD1676E:241b-43: ri mor bcas shing steg pa'i mchog //
T02TD1676E:241b-44: mdzes pas lta ba'i gar byed pa'o //
T02TD1676E:241b-45: sangs rgyas byang chub mnyam spyor ba //
T02TD1676E:241b-46: rab tu dga' bas lta zhing 'dzum //
T02TD1676E:241b-47: shin tu srid pa yang dag bsgrub //
T02TD1676E:241b-48: gsang bar blta la gnas pa'i rgya //
T02TD1676E:241b-49: steg la sogs ba'i nyams dang ldan //
T02TD1676E:241b-50: mdzes pa'i bzhin ni rnam 'gyur zhing //
T02TD1676E:241b-51: rim gror bcas pa steg pa'i mchog //
T02TD1676E:242a-2: mche ba cung zad gtsigs pa'i zhal //
T02TD1676E:242a-3: khro zhing 'dzum dang bcas pa'i bzhin //
T02TD1676E:242a-4: khro las gyur par bcas shing 'dzum //
T02TD1676E:242a-5: gsal bar lta zhing legs par gnas //
T02TD1676E:242a-6: 'dod chags myos pas g-yem spyo ba //
T02TD1676E:242a-7: mdzes pa'i bzhin ni rnam par 'gyur//
T02TD1676E:242a-8: drag po mche ba gnon po gtsigs //
T02TD1676E:242a-10: dngos po kun gyi bde ba mchog //
T02TD1676E:242a-11: rab tu dga' bar blta zhing 'dzum //
T02TD1676E:242a-12: spyi bor rta mgrin 'phang mtho ba //
T02TD1676E:242a-13: mche gtsogs ljang ser kha dog gsal //
T02TD1676E:242a-14: lha mo kun gyi bde ba mchog / mdzes pa'i ma mchu sos mnan cing //
T02TD1676E:242a-15: 'dod chags bde bas g-yem spyo ba //
T02TD1676E:242a-16: steg pa'i ma mchu sos mnan pa'o //
T02TD1676E:242a-17: sbyor ba kun gyi bde ba mchog / mdzes pa'i ma mchu g-yo bar byed //
T02TD1676E:242a-18: sha chen gyi ni ro myang zhing //
T02TD1676E:242a-19: mdzes pa'i ma mchu sos mnan cing //
T02TD1676E:242a-20: bde ba kun gyi ro myang zhing //
T02TD1676E:242a-21: ma mchu rnam par mdzos par bya'o ;
T02TD1676E:242a-22: / bde ba myong bar rab spyor bas //
T02TD1676E:242a-23: zam zim blta ba'i rnam 'gyur bcas //
T02TD1676E:242a-24: bud med mkhas pa sgyu ma mchog / mdzes par lta ba'i gar byed pa'o //
T02TD1676E:242a-25: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i mnyam sbyor ba //
T02TD1676E:242a-26: lta ba rab zhi bde bar gnas //
T02TD1676E:242a-27: smin mtshams khro gnyer 'gyur bar bcas //
T02TD1676E:242a-29: steg pa la sogs ro dang ldan //
T02TD1676E:242a-30: sgeg bcas lta ba'i gar byad pa //
T02TD1676E:242a-32: lta ba gsal bar bde bar gnas //
T02TD1676E:242a-33: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor so so'i rgya //
T02TD1676E:242a-34: phyag rgya gla dang bcas pa dag / h'um la sogs pas sna drangs te//
T02TD1676E:242a-35: mchod tshogs kun la sbyar bar bya //
T02TD1676E:242a-36: de nas tshogs kyi zhal zas rnams //
T02TD1676E:242a-38: rdo rje bla ma chen po dang //
T02TD1676E:242a-39: bdag dang gzhan yang 'dod dgus mchod //
T02TD1676E:242a-40: lha mo mtshan ldan sgyu rtsal can //
T02TD1676E:242a-41: las mkhan grogs dang bcas pa yis //
T02TD1676E:242a-42: padma mtshan ldan dpa' bos bkang //
T02TD1676E:242a-43: bdud rtsi rdzas mchog byin brlabs pas //
T02TD1676E:242a-44: bkra shis dbyangs dang gar tshogs kyis //
T02TD1676E:242a-45: thams cad rnam rtog med par mchod //
T02TD1676E:242a-46: ston mo'i yan lag gzhan dag kyang //
T02TD1676E:242a-47: rim pa bzhin du drang bar bya //
T02TD1676E:242b-0: aom thams cad rnam dag bdud rtsi'i @242b rang bzhin te //
T02TD1676E:242b-1: sku lnga chos lnga gnyis med ngo bo gcig / de phyir dag las dag pa nyid mchod de //
T02TD1676E:242b-2: chos nyid la thim ye shes rnam par rol //
T02TD1676E:242b-5: gar dang dbyangs su bcas pa yis //
T02TD1676E:242b-6: aa ho su kha zhes brjod cing //
T02TD1676E:242b-7: dga' mgu'i tshul gyis blang bar bya //
T02TD1676E:242b-8: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor gsal byas nas //
T02TD1676E:242b-9: lce la so so'i mtshan ma dang //
T02TD1676E:242b-10: chos kyi snying po bsam bya ste //
T02TD1676E:242b-11: rang gi lus la gnas par sbyor //
T02TD1676E:242b-12: dus gsum rab zhi mchog rnams kyis //
T02TD1676E:242b-13: h'um la sogs pa glu blang zhing //
T02TD1676E:242b-14: lha mo'i ka ka sha ta sogs //
T02TD1676E:242b-15: glu rnams rjes su blang bar bya //
T02TD1676E:242b-16: h'um rab tu dga' ba'i rjes su chags pa yi //
T02TD1676E:242b-17: mda' gzhu rab tu phra ba'i rgyas bcas pa'i //
T02TD1676E:242b-18: rab tu dga' ba'i sbyor ba'i bde bas myos //
T02TD1676E:242b-19: bde ba thams cad bdag la grub par mdzod //
T02TD1676E:242b-20: rab tu bde mchog rnam pa sna tshogs rnams //
T02TD1676E:242b-21: rgyal ba'i rgyal mtshan bsgreng ba'i longs spyod dang //
T02TD1676E:242b-22: rab tu dga' ba'i dbang phyug bde mchog grub //
T02TD1676E:242b-23: de bzhin gshegs pa rab bzhugs ho rta mchog / rab tu sna tshogs bde mchog rol cig ho //
T02TD1676E:242b-24: bde bas slong ba rnams rol snang bar mdzod //
T02TD1676E:242b-25: ho de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi mkha' 'gro yi //
T02TD1676E:242b-26: sgyu ma'i tshogs kyis slob ma gzung du gsol //
T02TD1676E:242b-27: aom gyi glu yi phyag rgya ni //
T02TD1676E:242b-28: tshangs pa'i dbyangs kyis ci bder blang //
T02TD1676E:242b-29: aom rdo rje sems dpa' bsdus pa na //
T02TD1676E:242b-30: rdo rje rin chen bla na med //
T02TD1676E:242b-31: rdo rje chos ni gsung ba dang //
T02TD1676E:242b-32: rdo rje las rnams byed par 'gyur //
T02TD1676E:242b-33: rdo rje drag po gang mo che //
T02TD1676E:242b-35: /'brug gi sgra ltar zab ba yi //
T02TD1676E:242b-36: ru lu ru lu'i sgra phyung nas //
T02TD1676E:242b-37: h'um rdo rje las kyi mda' gzhu la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1676E:242b-38: dpal rdo rje chags pa'i dam tshig la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1676E:242b-39: rdo rje kha nvam ga rab tu 'dzin pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1676E:242b-40: dpal rdo rje dril bu rab tu 'khrol ba la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1676E:242b-41: te zhes bya ba glu yi rgya //
T02TD1676E:242b-42: thams cad dag par rab sgrub pa'i //
T02TD1676E:242b-43: te ler rab tu drag cing gzhan drag la //
T02TD1676E:242b-44: drag po'i bud med sku ltar rab tu snang //
T02TD1676E:242b-45: 'gro ba mtha' yas 'dul phyir la la ni //
T02TD1676E:242b-46: rab no'i 'khor lo phyag na bsnams pa'i sku //
T02TD1676E:242b-47: la lar rab tu nges shing zhi ba yi //
T02TD1676E:243a-2: la lar rab 'bar chags pa padmo yi //
T02TD1676E:243a-3: rgyal po'i dam tshig bdag la grub par mdzod //
T02TD1676E:243a-4: hi zhes bya ba glu yi rgya //
T02TD1676E:243a-5: khams gsum rnam par rgyal bar byed //
T02TD1676E:243a-6: hi thams cad dbang phyug dam pa mi zad pa'i //
T02TD1676E:243a-7: gter mchog bdag la grub par mdzad du gsol //
T02TD1676E:243a-8: kun mchog rgyal mtshan rgyal ba bsgreng rdo rje //
T02TD1676E:243a-9: rin chen shin tu che ba bdag la mdzad //
T02TD1676E:243a-10: ka ka la lag dang gtso rgya yi dbyangs //
T02TD1676E:243a-11: de bzhin rab tu gdangs snyan dang //
T02TD1676E:243a-12: ka ha la yi glu yi rgya //
T02TD1676E:243a-13: 'joms pa thams cad rab sgrub pa'o //
T02TD1676E:243a-14: hi lar mkhas pa'i gzugs kyang 'dzin //
T02TD1676E:243a-15: la lar dus mtha' dus ltar drag / la lar rgyal dbang bzhin du zhi //
T02TD1676E:243a-16: la lar rta mchog sbyor bas 'grub //
T02TD1676E:243a-17: de dag sku yi glu yi mchog / phyag rgya sngags kyi sbyor bcas pa'o //
T02TD1676E:243a-18: tshogs sgrub chen po'i dus su ni //
T02TD1676E:243a-19: phyag rgya yi ni yan lag dag / brda dang sbyor ba sna tshogs kyis //
T02TD1676E:243a-20: 'khor lo rim bzhin bskor byas te //
T02TD1676E:243a-21: dpa' bo btung bas tshim 'gyur nas //
T02TD1676E:243a-22: bgegs bskrad spyang zhing byin gyis brlab //
T02TD1676E:243a-23: de yi dam tshig de 'byung ba'i //
T02TD1676E:243a-24: sdug pa dam tshig bdag rjes 'brang //
T02TD1676E:243a-25: shin tu sbyor dang sbyor chen po //
T02TD1676E:243a-26: thams cad bdag nyid dam tshig mchog //
T02TD1676E:243a-27: gcig bzhin du ni gcig spyod pa //
T02TD1676E:243a-28: lhan cig spyod pa rjes spyod drug / lha mo kun gyi longs spyod la //
T02TD1676E:243a-29: ci bde bar ni bsten par bya //
T02TD1676E:243a-30: de nas khrus byas dri zhim lus //
T02TD1676E:243a-31: ci 'byor pa yi gos dang rgyan //
T02TD1676E:243a-32: sna tshogs rnam par bgos nas ni //
T02TD1676E:243a-33: me tog phreng ldan kha dri zhim //
T02TD1676E:243a-34: sna tshogs kun gyi skal bzang pos //
T02TD1676E:243a-35: slong bas dal gyis dal gyis su //
T02TD1676E:243a-36: gos dgab pa yi sbyor ba yis //
T02TD1676E:243a-37: bdag gis dbyung ba bskul bar bya //
T02TD1676E:243a-38: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas nyi zla rnams //
T02TD1676E:243a-39: shar ba dag gis mthong ba yis //
T02TD1676E:243a-40: nges pa'i lam dang kun ldan pa //
T02TD1676E:243a-41: rnam par 'das pas rnam par brgyan //
T02TD1676E:243a-42: dbang bskur kun las byung ba yi //
T02TD1676E:243a-43: mchod pa'i sprin chen rnam bkod pa //
T02TD1676E:243a-44: rab 'byams tshogs rnams thams cad kyis //
T02TD1676E:243a-45: kun gyi bdag nyid mchod par byed //
T02TD1676E:243a-46: bdud rtsi rnam pa lnga po dag / so so'i phrad dang sbyar byas nas //
T02TD1676E:243a-47: tshogs kyi dbus su bzhag pa ni //
T02TD1676E:243a-48: ra sa yan kun slong ba'o //
T02TD1676E:243b-0: @243b dngos grub bskul tshig dbyangs kun blang //
T02TD1676E:243b-1: aom a'a:h'um h'um aom hi hri tr'am ham /
T02TD1676E:243b-2: he panytsa aa mri ta ra sa ya na siddhi /
T02TD1676E:243b-4: h'um aom hi hri hram ham /
T02TD1676E:243b-6: aom pa hu bi wai ta /
T02TD1676E:243b-8: aa she sha ne she sha /
T02TD1676E:243b-10: sarba ta th'a ga ta ca le pra tsa le /
T02TD1676E:243b-14: aom ba hu bi wi ta /
T02TD1676E:243b-25: aa she sha ni she sha //
T02TD1676E:243b-31: ru lu ru lu h'um bhyo h'um /
T02TD1676E:243b-32: sh'anting ku ru ba sham ku ru /
T02TD1676E:243b-36: mchog gi bdud rtsi don sbyar ba'i //
T02TD1676E:243b-37: gsang sngags yi ge bcu gcig pa //
T02TD1676E:243b-38: bdud rtse lnga par bcud len don //
T02TD1676E:243b-39: dngos grub gnas kun gsal bar byed //
T02TD1676E:243b-40: 'od dang du ba sprin dang sgra ;
T02TD1676E:243b-41: / lha mo gzugs ston brten par gnas //
T02TD1676E:243b-42: nye bar spyod pa'i bsnyen sgrub bzhi //
T02TD1676E:243b-43: yan lag bzhi yi gnas sbyor te //
T02TD1676E:243b-44: mtha' sngags bskul tshig 'brel pa yis //
T02TD1676E:243b-45: rigs kyi phrin las gsal bar 'grub //
T02TD1676E:243b-46: rang gi lha yi sbyor ldan pas //
T02TD1676E:243b-47: srin lag dang ni mthe bong rtses //
T02TD1676E:243b-48: zhi ba'i btung ba bzhin myang shing //
T02TD1676E:243b-49: lha gzhan la yang dbul bar bya //
T02TD1676E:243b-50: gnas kun thig les brgyan byas shing //
T02TD1676E:243b-51: rigs kyi dngos grub blang bar bya //
T02TD1676E:243b-52: de dus 'gro don rgya che dang //
T02TD1676E:243b-53: dbang bskur las kun brtsam bya zhing //
T02TD1676E:243b-54: bdag don 'gro ba'i gnas sbyor te //
T02TD1676E:243b-55: dam tshig sngom pa gzung bar bya //
T02TD1676E:243b-56: gling bu dang ni rgyud gcig dang //
T02TD1676E:243b-57: de bzhin rgyud mngas rgyud drug dang //
T02TD1676E:243b-58: sil snyan phyag rgyar bshad pa rnams //
T02TD1676E:243b-59: glu skad gong ma dang sbyar brdung //
T02TD1676E:243b-60: dza:h'um bam ho:ru tra ma tra /
T02TD1676E:243b-64: takki h'um dza:ki ni du ni h'um rum /
T02TD1676E:243b-69: da ri sha ya ban ta ghe na ghe /
T02TD1676E:243b-80: thal mo brdab pa brtag pa'o //
T02TD1676E:244a-8: h'um bhyo h'um bhyo h'um bhyo h'um bhyo h'um bhyo h'um bhyo /
T02TD1676E:244a-9: ru lu ru lu h'um bhyo /
T02TD1676E:244a-16: dpal padmo'i thal mo brdab pa'i rnga'o //
T02TD1676E:244a-18: ba ba ba ba ba ba ba /
T02TD1676E:244a-19: ta ta ta ta ta ta ta /
T02TD1676E:244a-27: tra tra tra tra tra tra tra /
T02TD1676E:244a-28: myur zhing rab tu myur ba'o //
T02TD1676E:244a-33: dpal rta mchog rnam par rol pa'o //
T02TD1676E:244a-34: ta ta pa ta ta ba ta ta ba /
T02TD1676E:244a-35: tat pa tat pa tat pa /
T02TD1676E:244a-37: shin tu myur ba'i rnga'i phyag rgya'o //
T02TD1676E:244a-38: lha rnams mnyes par bya ba dang //
T02TD1676E:244a-39: las rnams 'grub par bya ba'i phyir //
T02TD1676E:244a-40: thog ma bar skabs mtha' rnams su //
T02TD1676E:244a-41: spyin sreg drug gi las brtsam bya //
T02TD1676E:244a-42: dkyil 'khor chen po'i shar phyogs su //
T02TD1676E:244a-43: las kun ba dang rgyas pa brtsam //
T02TD1676E:244a-44: byang du zhi ba lhor mngon spyod //
T02TD1676E:244a-45: nub tu dbang dang dgug pa'i las //
T02TD1676E:244a-46: thab khung kun gyi nang rgya ru //
T02TD1676E:244a-47: khru gang zabs su phyed brkos shing //
T02TD1676E:244a-48: kha khyer rim gsum bskyed byas pa //
T02TD1676E:244a-49: rim bzhin sor ni bzhi bzhir gnas //
T02TD1676E:244a-50: zhi la zlum po rgyas gru bzhi //
T02TD1676E:244a-51: dbang la zla gam gru gsum drag / dkar ser dmar nag rim bzhin mdog / las kun dbyibs dang mdog kun ldan //
T02TD1676E:244a-52: dgug pa lcags kyu mchon [*ma chon?] cha'i tshogs //
T02TD1676E:244a-53: rang gi rigs mthun kha dog can //
T02TD1676E:244a-55: rdo rjes mtshan cing phred bas brgyan //
T02TD1676E:244a-56: so so'i rigs dang mthun pa yi //
T02TD1676E:244a-57: bud shing rang gi dbyibs su brtsig / sor bzhi brgyad dang bcu drug gnyis //
T02TD1676E:244a-58: yam shing me tog dri yis brgyan //
T02TD1676E:244a-59: rtse mo'i cha las rtse mo ste //
T02TD1676E:244a-60: so so'i mar gyis byug pa'o //
T02TD1676E:244a-61: thab gyi phyi rol 'khor dag tu //
T02TD1676E:244a-62: ku sha rgyan dang tshon cha dang //
T02TD1676E:244a-63: me long rnga ma yol bar bcas ;
T02TD1676E:244a-64: / tshon cha sna lnga'i thag pas bskor //
T02TD1676E:244a-65: g-yas su rdo rje dril bu dang //
T02TD1676E:244a-66: yam shing til dang rlung yab gzhag / g-yon du dri chu me tog dang //
T02TD1676E:244a-67: d'ur ba ku sha'i chun po gzhag / mdun du mchod pa rnam lnga dang //
T02TD1676E:244a-68: mchod rdzas gzhan yang gzhag par bya //
T02TD1676E:244b-0: mchod yon yan lag @244b brgyad ldan pa //
T02TD1676E:244b-1: dri sna me tog dkar po dang //
T02TD1676E:244b-2: zho dang d'ur bas bkang ba dang //
T02TD1676E:244b-3: 'bras dkar yungs kar mar dang zho //
T02TD1676E:244b-4: mchod rdzas kun gyi sna ba dgod //
T02TD1676E:244b-5: bgegs bsal bsrung spyang byin gyis brlab //
T02TD1676E:244b-6: rdo rje sems dpa'i ting 'dzin gyis //
T02TD1676E:244b-7: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor gsal byas nas //
T02TD1676E:244b-8: chas gos lnga po dbu rgyan phreng //
T02TD1676E:244b-9: phyag rgya lnga sogs rgyan gyis mchan //
T02TD1676E:244b-10: mdun du dpal mchog las byung ba'i //
T02TD1676E:244b-11: ram skyes las dang rjes mthun pa'i// dkar ser dmar gnag go rims bzhin //
T02TD1676E:244b-12: zhi sogs las mdzad me lha bskyed //
T02TD1676E:244b-13: mig gsum gdod bzhi rim pa can// gsus po che la phyag bzhi pa //
T02TD1676E:244b-14: mi 'jigs rgya phreng spyi blugs dang //
T02TD1676E:244b-15: dbyig pa srad bu'i phreng ba thogs //
T02TD1676E:244b-17: padma'i gdan la rnam par gnas //
T02TD1676E:244b-18: dbang bskur byin rlabs dbu rgyan bcas //
T02TD1676E:244b-20: dam tshig sems dpa'i gzugs 'dra ba'i//
T02TD1676E:244b-21: ye shes 'phrul pa spyan drangs nas //
T02TD1676E:244b-22: thab kyi logs su gzhag byas la //
T02TD1676E:244b-23: bsang gtor mchod yon zhabs bsil dang //
T02TD1676E:244b-24: nye reg phul te phyag rgya bzhi //
T02TD1676E:244b-25: gnyis su med par bstan par bya //
T02TD1676E:244b-26: aom ta ki h'um dza h'um /
T02TD1676E:244b-29: g-yas pas ku sha'i chung po bzung //
T02TD1676E:244b-30: phyogs rnams kun du bsang gtor bya //
T02TD1676E:244b-31: so so'i las dang mthun pa'i me //
T02TD1676E:244b-32: rlung yab ba dan dang bcas sbar //
T02TD1676E:244b-33: aom dzny'a na dzva la ram /
T02TD1676E:244b-34: lag gnyis mchod yon phyag rgya yis //
T02TD1676E:244b-35: dud chos blangs te dbul bar bya //
T02TD1676E:244b-36: dgang gzar blugs gzar tshad ldan la //
T02TD1676E:244b-37: mtshan ma'i ye shes brgyan byas te //
T02TD1676E:244b-38: 'od bcas mar khus bkang nas ni //
T02TD1676E:244b-39: lan gsum lha yi zhal du bstim //
T02TD1676E:244b-40: aom na ma:sa manta buddh'a n'am /
T02TD1676E:244b-43: mchod pa rnam pa lnga yi tshogs //
T02TD1676E:244b-44: so so'i sngags dang phyag rgyas dbul //
T02TD1676E:244b-47: aom sarba p'a pam nga ha na badzr'a ya sv'ah'a //
T02TD1676E:244b-48: p'a pa da ha na sv'ah'a //
T02TD1676E:244b-50: aom badzra a'a yu she sv'ah'a //
T02TD1676E:244b-51: d'ur ba'i myu gu mar gyis byung pa'o //
T02TD1676E:244b-52: aom badzra pushpe ye sv'a h'a //
T02TD1676E:244b-57: aom aa pra ti ha ta ni ha dha badzr'a ya sv'a h'a /
T02TD1676E:245a-2: aom pra bar satka pra titstsha ho zhes pa yang dang blugs so //
T02TD1676E:245a-3: nye reg la sogs byas nas ni //
T02TD1676E:245a-4: dpa' bo rdo rje dril 'khrol zhing //
T02TD1676E:245a-5: bstod pa'i phyag rgyas mnyes byas nas //
T02TD1676E:245a-6: gar dbyangs rol mos bskul bar bya //
T02TD1676E:245a-7: lag gnyis lto sbyor spyod byas te //
T02TD1676E:245a-8: rdzas rnams lan gsum spyang bar bya //
T02TD1676E:245a-11: ta ki ni hri da ya h'um phat /
T02TD1676E:245a-12: de nas dkyil 'khor gang yin pa'i //
T02TD1676E:245a-13: lha rnams me yi gnas su gzhug / gong ma'i dkyil 'khor rim pa bzhin //
T02TD1676E:245a-14: rang gnas gdan la legs bzhugs sam //
T02TD1676E:245a-15: ma 'brel me lha'i khang pa ru ;
T02TD1676E:245a-16: / dam tshig dkyil 'khor rim bzhin bsam //
T02TD1676E:245a-17: ye shes dkyil 'khor spyan drangs te //
T02TD1676E:245a-18: dgug gzhug la sogs gnyis med par //
T02TD1676E:245a-19: mchod bstod las rnams sngon bzhin las //
T02TD1676E:245a-20: gsang sngags mtha' sngags skul tshig bcas //
T02TD1676E:245a-21: aom lha yi me lha shin tu tshogs //
T02TD1676E:245a-22: lha yi dri yis nye bar byugs //
T02TD1676E:245a-23: me tog bzang po 'di bzhes la //
T02TD1676E:245a-24: gnas 'di nyid du bzhugs su gsol //
T02TD1676E:245a-25: aom mar me 'od zer 'bar ba ni //
T02TD1676E:245a-28: go la dgongs te bzhes su gso //
T02TD1676E:245a-29: aom tsandan ga pur bcas pa yi //
T02TD1676E:245a-30: dri mchog bdug spos dam pa yi //
T02TD1676E:245a-31: dbang po'i sgo rnams tshim pa'i mchog / byin gyis rlobs la bzhes su gsol //
T02TD1676E:245a-32: aom sna tshogs lha yi dri ldan pa //
T02TD1676E:245a-33: sna tshogs ga pur gyis ni brgyan //
T02TD1676E:245a-34: sna tshogs h'um las yang dag byung //
T02TD1676E:245a-35: dri mchog 'di dag bzhes su gsol //
T02TD1676E:245a-36: aom kha dog dri dang ror ldan pa'i //
T02TD1676E:245a-37: bza' ba'i bye brag sna tshogs dag / zhal zas phun sum tshogs pa'i gzhi //
T02TD1676E:245a-38: 'gro ba'i don du bzhes su gsol //
T02TD1676E:245a-39: lha rnams mnyes shing tshim pa dang //
T02TD1676E:245a-41: mchod bstod bskul tshig las byas te //
T02TD1676E:245a-42: snga ma'i dkyil 'khor gnas su dgod //
T02TD1676E:245a-43: gal te ma 'brel spyan drangs lha //
T02TD1676E:245a-44: thugs ka nas bton kha la bzhag / zhal bsil la sogs dbul byas te //
T02TD1676E:245a-45: sngar bzhin gshegs gsol bsdus pa dag / sngags dang phyag rgyas gshegs su gsol //
T02TD1676E:245a-46: aom khyed kyis sems can don kun mdzad //
T02TD1676E:245b-0: rjes @245b su mthun pa'i dngos grub stsol //
T02TD1676E:245b-1: sangs rgyas yul du gshegs nas kyang //
T02TD1676E:245b-2: slar yang byon par mdzad du gsol //
T02TD1676E:245b-5: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor bsdu byas nas //
T02TD1676E:245b-6: lhag mas me lha mchod byas te //
T02TD1676E:245b-7: sngar bzhin gshegs gsol bsdus pa dag / mnyam nyid rang la gnas par bya'o //
T02TD1676E:245b-8: de nas las kyi rdo rje yis //
T02TD1676E:245b-9: dkyil 'khor phyi rol mtshams dag tu //
T02TD1676E:245b-10: khor yug zlum po'i rim pa la //
T02TD1676E:245b-11: drags byed mkha' 'gro'i tshogs rnams kyi //
T02TD1676E:245b-12: pho brang gdan dang mchan ma'i rtags //
T02TD1676E:245b-13: rin chen rgyan tshogs phreng bar bcas //
T02TD1676E:245b-14: sna tshogs bza' btung gtor ma'i tshogs //
T02TD1676E:245b-15: lhag ma'i tshogs bcad dgram par bya //
T02TD1676E:245b-16: rdzas rnams tshogs nas dri yis bsang //
T02TD1676E:245b-17: bdud rtsi'i rgyun dbab spyang zhing bsrung //
T02TD1676E:245b-18: dbus kyi lha tshogs rdo rje'i steng //
T02TD1676E:245b-19: hi las rta mchog rgyal po bsgom //
T02TD1676E:245b-20: phrin las rnams bzhi'i bzhi'i dkyil 'khor la //
T02TD1676E:245b-21: dug gsum 'byung bzhi rang rtags phreng //
T02TD1676E:245b-22: sgo bzhi bar khyams phyi ro sgo //
T02TD1676E:245b-23: rang gi mtshan mas mdzes par byas //
T02TD1676E:245b-24: mdun du dbang phyug chen po ste //
T02TD1676E:245b-25: g-yas su chad pa brgya byin lha //
T02TD1676E:245b-27: chud ma bzhon pa la gnas pa'i //
T02TD1676E:245b-29: rang gi sa bon sdags las skyes //
T02TD1676E:245b-30: dbang ldan me lha'i rgyal po dang //
T02TD1676E:245b-31: srin po'i rgyal po rlung gi bdag //
T02TD1676E:245b-32: chung ma bzhon pa'i gdan dang bcas //
T02TD1676E:245b-33: lho 'am shar du lha chen brgyan //
T02TD1676E:245b-34: lho ru shin rje ma mo'i tshogs //
T02TD1676E:245b-35: nub phyogs pho nya klu yi 'khor //
T02TD1676E:245b-36: byang du gnod sbyin chen po brgyad //
T02TD1676E:245b-37: sgo bzhir nyi zla sa bdag che //
T02TD1676E:245b-38: sa yi lha mo gnas pa'o //
T02TD1676E:245b-39: phyi khyams ma tshogs dbang phyug rnams //
T02TD1676E:245b-40: sgo bzhir mkha' 'gro chen mo bzhi //
T02TD1676E:245b-41: kun kyang rgyan bcas cha lugs dang //
T02TD1676E:245b-42: lag cha bzhon par bcas pa yi //
T02TD1676E:245b-43: chung ma khyo dang bran tshogs g-yos //
T02TD1676E:245b-44: gsang sngags las bskyed gsal bar dgod //
T02TD1676E:245b-45: dgug cing gnas su gzhug byas nas //
T02TD1676E:245b-46: zil gnon dam tshig phyag rgya bstan //
T02TD1676E:245b-47: mtshad bstod las la bskul byas nas //
T02TD1676E:245b-48: rta mgrin phyag rgya rnam gnyis bcing //
T02TD1676E:246a-0: h'um khro las rnga tshan 'bar ba'i skur ston @246a * //
