T02TD1676E:249b-14: sna tshogs dbang phyug phrin las kyis //
T02TD1676E:249b-15: rtag tu rang gi don brtson zhing //
T02TD1676E:249b-16: drag po mkha' 'gro'i chogs bsdus pas //
T02TD1676E:249b-17: gzhan don las la rnam par rol //
T02TD1676E:249b-18: sprul pa yang sprul 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
T02TD1676E:249b-19: gsod don sha khrag las la brtson //
T02TD1676E:249b-20: shar gyi rdo rje sgyu 'phrul gtso //
T02TD1676E:249b-21: gzugs chen nam mkha'i gos gyon ma //
T02TD1676E:249b-22: keng rus rnam par 'gyur ba dang //
T02TD1676E:249b-23: mkha' chen 'dra ba'i sgyu ma che //
T02TD1676E:249b-24: rdo rje'i thog 'bebs mthu rtsal can //
T02TD1676E:249b-25: mun pa'i tshogs 'joms snang ba'i sku //
T02TD1676E:249b-26: rdo rje rigs tshogs mkha' 'gro'i rgyal //
T02TD1676E:249b-27: dkar mo rdo rje rtse gsum dang //
T02TD1676E:249b-28: 'khor lo gtun shing gri gug mtshon //
T02TD1676E:249b-29: mda' rnon lcags kyu zhags pa dang //
T02TD1676E:249b-30: ral gri thod dbyug mdung 'phen ma //
T02TD1676E:249b-31: mi mgo rgyu ma'i phreng ba thogs //
T02TD1676E:249b-33: gtum pa'i rngam tshig 'brug bzhin sgrogs //
T02TD1676E:249b-34: shar gyi gnas mchog lhun po'i rtse //
T02TD1676E:249b-35: dkyil 'khor 'bar ba'i las mdzod cig / lho phyogs rin chen 'od mdzes brgyan //
T02TD1676E:249b-36: byang chub gnas bsrung rdzu 'phrul che //
T02TD1676E:249b-37: khro gnyer 'jigs pa'i sprul pa can //
T02TD1676E:249b-38: gshin rje'i tshogs 'joms mche ba thogs //
T02TD1676E:249b-39: 'od chen khams gsum khyab pa mo //
T02TD1676E:249b-40: rin chen dbyug pa'i glu dbyangs sgrogs //
T02TD1676E:249b-42: 'khor lo sti ra me thab dang //
T02TD1676E:249b-43: bdud kyi khram shing zhags pa bdun //
T02TD1676E:249b-44: rtse gsum mgo thod dum bu dang //
T02TD1676E:249b-45: dra ba lcags kyu 'bar ba thogs //
T02TD1676E:250a-2: ban chen yi dvags gdan rnams su //
T02TD1676E:250a-3: sprul pa'i nyi ma'i 'od zer ltar //
T02TD1676E:250a-4: dam bcas phrin las skabs la bab //
T02TD1676E:250a-6: rdo rje keng rus gnas kun 'joms //
T02TD1676E:250a-7: shugs 'chang rlung gi grong khyer bdag / sgrub pa'i gsang 'dzin phyag rgya can //
T02TD1676E:250a-8: ro yi phreng bas bskyod pa'i gnas //
T02TD1676E:250a-9: mtshon cha glog gi phreng thogs ma //
T02TD1676E:250a-10: dmar po thod dbyig rgyu ma'i phreng //
T02TD1676E:250a-11: gri gug 'then thag zangs dung dang //
T02TD1676E:250a-12: mkha' lding mi snying khrag 'dzag ma //
T02TD1676E:250a-13: mda' yi me tog lcug ma dang //
T02TD1676E:250a-15: ro yi nags tshal lcug ma can //
T02TD1676E:250a-16: khams gsum 'khrug pa'i khrag mtsho nas //
T02TD1676E:250a-17: dbang po srid gsum chags mdzad spyon //
T02TD1676E:250a-18: byang gi rdo rje las mchog gtso //
T02TD1676E:250a-19: kun du bzang mo yid kyi shugs //
T02TD1676E:250a-20: rdo rje gnod byed dpa' mo'i mchog / dpal ldan bzang mo'i rgyan cha can //
T02TD1676E:250a-21: 'bar ba'i spyan can drag po'i gzugs //
T02TD1676E:250a-22: las rnams kun la mnga' mdzad rgyal //
T02TD1676E:250a-23: ljang gnag rdo rje rgya gram khrag / me ri 'bar bcas lcags kyu zhags //
T02TD1676E:250a-24: gnod sbyin dbyug pa bdud rtsi dang //
T02TD1676E:250a-25: be con zla dkyil thag mdung dri //
T02TD1676E:250a-27: rtse gsum pa dan mi yi rkang //
T02TD1676E:250a-28: gnod byed stobs mchog 'jigs pa'i ri //
T02TD1676E:250a-29: byang gi gtum 'phrul rol pa'i tshogs //
T02TD1676E:250a-30: ma mo mkha' 'gro gzugs can rnams //
T02TD1676E:250a-31: dam tshig mchog gi gnas grub mdzod //
T02TD1676E:250a-32: aom buddha d'a k'i ni man ba lim ta pra titstsha ho aom phat kh'a hi /
T02TD1676E:250a-33: aom badzra d'a k'i ni man ba lim tam pra titstsha ho h'um phat kh'a hi /
T02TD1676E:250a-34: aom ratna d'a k'i ni man ba lim tam pra titstsha ho hram phat kha hi /
T02TD1676E:250a-35: aom padma d'a k'i ni man pa lim ta pra titstsha ho hri phat kh'a hi /
T02TD1676E:250a-36: aom karma d'a k'i ni man ba lim ta pra titstsha ho ham phat kh'a hi /
T02TD1676E:250a-46: kh'a hi kh'a hi kh'a hi /
T02TD1676E:250a-47: aom ghu ru tro ha ka /
T02TD1676E:250a-48: sa ma ya pra sha kh'a hi /
T02TD1676E:250a-50: buddha kshe ta pra tishtam pa ya kh'a hi /
T02TD1676E:250a-51: padma'i phyag rgyas kha chus mchod pa'o //
T02TD1676E:250a-52: lag gnyis rgyab sbyar snying gar gtad //
T02TD1676E:250a-53: mdzub bsnol srin lag mig gi tshul //
T02TD1676E:250b-0: gung mtheg @250b gnyis gdangs rtse sbrang kha //
T02TD1676E:250b-1: mthe'u chung gyen du bsgreng ba'i rgyas //
T02TD1676E:250b-2: 'jig rten pa yi las tshogs rnams //
T02TD1676E:250b-3: phyogs kun dngos grub rgyas byed pa'o //
T02TD1676E:250b-4: aom padma ba mu karma siddhi h'um /
T02TD1676E:250b-5: phyag rgya bdun rol bsgyur byas te //
T02TD1676E:250b-6: mtheb gung mdzub srin gong bzhin sbyar //
T02TD1676E:250b-7: dngos grub mchog rnams dbang byas pas //
T02TD1676E:250b-8: rten byed mi 'bral kun spyod mdzod //
T02TD1676E:250b-9: aom padma ba mu khe aa be sha ya hr'i:/
T02TD1676E:250b-10: rdo rje khu tshur bcangs pa yi //
T02TD1676E:250b-11: mthe bo rtse bzhi mche ba'i tshul //
T02TD1676E:250b-12: mchod gtor phyogs kun gnas bsgyur bas //
T02TD1676E:250b-13: las kun bya ba mthar phyin 'gyur //
T02TD1676E:250b-16: sa ma ya bag sha h'um /
T02TD1676E:250b-17: aom ru lu ru lu h'um bhyo h'um /
T02TD1676E:250b-18: phyag rgya'i ting 'dzin sngags bcas ldan //
T02TD1676E:250b-19: gtor ma'i las bskul gnas su btang //
T02TD1676E:250b-20: slar log dkyil 'khor ma nyams blos //
T02TD1676E:250b-21: bkra shis dngos grub bskul bar bya //
T02TD1676E:250b-22: aom dngos grub dbang phyug yang dag bden ba'i stobs //
T02TD1676E:250b-23: phun sum tshogs pa kun du 'byung ba'i gzhi //
T02TD1676E:250b-24: stobs mchog mi 'jigs gdon bral 'tshe ba 'tshe ba ldan bkra shis mi 'gyur brtan par shog / aom sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam par sbyor ba yi //
T02TD1676E:250b-25: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde ba chen po'i mchog / dkyil 'khor phyag rgya gsang sngags sbyor ba'i mthus //
T02TD1676E:250b-26: rigs kun bkra shis mi 'gyur brtan par shog / aom thams cad dngos grub don tshogs rgya chen po //
T02TD1676E:250b-27: thun mong mngon shes rnam lnga sgo gsal zhing //
T02TD1676E:250b-28: gser 'gyur bum pa bcud len bdud rtsi'i tshogs //
T02TD1676E:250b-29: bcu drug bkra shis mi 'gyur brtan par shog / aom mtshan mchog dpe byad mi 'gyur brtan zhing brjid //
T02TD1676E:250b-30: bdud 'dul bkra shis gdugs mchog rgyal mtshan dung //
T02TD1676E:250b-31: 'khor lo dpal be'u gser nya bum pa mtshon //
T02TD1676E:250b-32: nye ba'i bkra shis mi 'gyur brtan par shog / aom zhi rgyas dbang drag mnan bzlog las rnams kun //
T02TD1676E:250b-33: thams cad skad cig mthu yis grub 'gyur zhing /
T02TD1676E:250b-34: bdag gzhan cha lugs gnas kun sbyor byed pa'i //
T02TD1676E:250b-35: phrin las bkra shis mi 'gyur brtan par shog / aom rgyal ba thams cad gnyis med mnyam pa'i dbyings //
T02TD1676E:250b-36: ye shes sku mchog rigs dang sprul pa'i tshogs //
T02TD1676E:250b-37: ma 'dres dngos grub 'bras bzang dpe dang bral //
T02TD1676E:251a-1: mi 'gyur bkra shis brtan par shog / las rdzogs rnal 'byor pho mo kun //
T02TD1676E:251a-2: lu gu rgyud kyi phyag rgyas 'brel //
T02TD1676E:251a-3: aom mi gnas ye shes thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
T02TD1676E:251a-4: 'gyur ba med pa lhun gyis grub pa dang //
T02TD1676E:251a-5: rab 'byam rgyal ba'i bka' la dbang thob nas //
T02TD1676E:251a-6: 'gro ba yongs kyi dpal du 'gyur bar shog /'di lta bu yi man ngag lung ston cing //
T02TD1676E:251a-7: bka' drin che ba'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen dang //
T02TD1676E:251a-8: srog gi lu gu rgyud kyi 'brel pa rnams //
T02TD1676E:251a-9: 'og min lhun gyis grub pa'i gnas mchog tu //
T02TD1676E:251a-10: dus gsum 'du 'bral med par 'grogs pa dang //
T02TD1676E:251a-11: gsang chen thugs kyi dkyil 'khor chen po ru //
T02TD1676E:251a-12: bla med sku gsung thugs mchog grub gyur nas //
T02TD1676E:251a-13: rgyal ba'i mdzad pas 'gro rnams sgrol byed shog / rang rig dkyil 'khor rgyas pa dang //
T02TD1676E:251a-14: phrin las bcu drug gnas 'jug cing //
T02TD1676E:251a-16: / bsam gtan bya ba'i las bzhin du //
T02TD1676E:251a-17: bdag gzhan don 'gyur du tshod shes //
T02TD1676E:251a-18: cho ga rten 'brel rdzogs par spyad //
T02TD1676E:251a-19: de yang rten gyi dbye ba yis //
T02TD1676E:251a-20: bsam gtan bzlas brjod sbyin sreg dang //
T02TD1676E:251a-22: mos sogs goms pa'i shugs kyis 'jug / dang por sbyor ba mthun pa'i las //
T02TD1676E:251a-23: sngon du 'gro ba'i cho ga rdzogs //
T02TD1676E:251a-24: las kyi yan lag dag byas na //
T02TD1676E:251a-25: rung zhing byin gyis brlabs ba tsam //
T02TD1676E:251a-26: gsang ba las dang mthun gnas su //
T02TD1676E:251a-27: grogs sogs dbang bskur byin brlabs ldan //
T02TD1676E:251a-28: mos pas byang chub mchog sems bskyad //
T02TD1676E:251a-29: dad brtsson blo gros 'gyur ba med //
T02TD1676E:251a-30: gsang ba'i phyag rgya rgya chen sgo //
T02TD1676E:251a-31: tshul bzhin the tshom med pas 'grub //
T02TD1676E:251a-32: de ltar byin rlabs myur ba'i mthus //
T02TD1676E:251a-33: las kyi rtog tshogs rab 'jig pa'o //
T02TD1676E:251a-34: sbyor ba ji snyed yod pa kun //
T02TD1676E:251a-35: byed pa rnam pa sna tshogs la //
T02TD1676E:251a-36: rdo rje sems dpa' dpal gyi rgyu //
T02TD1676E:251a-37: dngos grub thams cad rab grub pa'o //
T02TD1676E:251a-38: bya ba dang ni bzlog pa dang //
T02TD1676E:251a-39: khyad par du ni dbrog pa dag / yan lag kun du byed pa'i nang //
T02TD1676E:251a-40: des ni nor rnams kun kyang dbrog /'o byed 'khyud pa la sogs pas //
T02TD1676E:251b-0: khams gsum pa yang rgyas 'debs @251b so ;
T02TD1676E:251b-1: / thar par byed cing gsod par byed //
T02TD1676E:251b-2: sbyor ba'i longs spyod thams cad kyis //
T02TD1676E:251b-3: khams gsum po ni ma lus par //
T02TD1676E:251b-4: rgyas btab rmongs byas blangs nas su //
T02TD1676E:251b-5: gar byas nas ni za bar byed //
T02TD1676E:251b-6: sbyor ba kun gyi bde myong bas //
T02TD1676E:251b-7: khams gsum pa ni ma lus par //
T02TD1676E:251b-8: rgyas btab rmongs byas zos pa dang //
T02TD1676E:251b-9: thal bar gyur pa'ang 'tsho bar byed //
T02TD1676E:251b-10: sbyor ba thams cad phyag rgya yi //
T02TD1676E:251b-11: rigs mchog gtso bo'i lha mor bcas //
T02TD1676E:251b-12: sna tshogs phrin las ma lus la //
T02TD1676E:251b-13: rang gi tshul bzhin rnam par sbyar //
T02TD1676E:251b-14: ras dang gro ga shing sogs la //
T02TD1676E:251b-15: gur gum gi'u wang tshon sna las //
T02TD1676E:251b-16: bdag gzhan pho mo la dmigs te //
T02TD1676E:251b-17: rten gyi gsang sngags sbyor bcas bri //
T02TD1676E:251b-18: mu khyud phreng ba rim gsum nang //
T02TD1676E:251b-19: sna tshogs rdo rje'i lte ba la //
T02TD1676E:251b-21: rang gi mtshan mas brgyan par bri //
T02TD1676E:251b-22: 'khor lo lte ba rnams la ni //
T02TD1676E:251b-23: rigs bdag rtsa pa'i dkyil 'khor sngags //
T02TD1676E:251b-24: 'khor lo gnyis par yi ge brgya //
T02TD1676E:251b-25: sna tshogs mtshams bzhir zhal bzhi pa //
T02TD1676E:251b-26: mu khyud nang mar phreng ba'i sngags //
T02TD1676E:251b-27: gnyis par yi ge ma mo rnams //
T02TD1676E:251b-28: gsum pa rigs kyi mtshon cha phreng //
T02TD1676E:251b-29: bar mtshams bsgrub bya'i ming gsol 'debs //
T02TD1676E:251b-30: de la phreng ba'i gsang sngags che //
T02TD1676E:251b-31: rdo rje sems dpa'i sbyor ba gnyis //
T02TD1676E:251b-32: rigs gzhan dkyil 'khor phyag rgya'i tshogs //
T02TD1676E:251b-33: thams cad shar nas g-yas su bskor //
T02TD1676E:251b-34: aom a'a:h'um shr'i de ba ta /
T02TD1676E:251b-35: badzra satva sto tra na mo stu sti sarba buddha /
T02TD1676E:251b-36: sa ma yo g'i na ma h'um h'um sv'ah'a /
T02TD1676E:251b-37: aom a'a:h'um shr'i badzra sva dzyo stya te su r'a ga na mo sarba buddha sa ma yo g'i dzva la sam bh'a ra na ma h'um h'um sv'ah'a /
T02TD1676E:251b-38: aom a'a:h'um ma h'a r'a ga mu ga ta /
T02TD1676E:251b-40: sarba ca kra sa ma yo ga r'a ga ai ti na ma aom kham sv'ah'a /
T02TD1676E:251b-41: aom a'a:h'um ka ru na aa ma la kro ddha shr'i he ru ka /
T02TD1676E:251b-42: sarba badzrod sa ma yo g'i ni sto tra na mo stu ta na ma hi h'um phat sv'ah'a /
T02TD1676E:251b-43: aom a'a:h'um shr'i padma r'a ga shuddha shuddho sarba mah'a r'a ga padmo sa ma yo g'i ni na ma hi h'um sv'ah'a /
T02TD1676E:251b-44: aom a'a:h'um shr'i badzra bha ba ta ao dza nya totta ratna sa ma yo g'i ni na ma tram h'um sv'ah'a /
T02TD1676E:251b-45: aom a'a:h'um shr'i aashod pa ra kra ma sarba bi shva sa ma yo g'i ma h'a r'a ga na ma ham h'um sv'ah'a /
T02TD1676E:251b-46: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor gsal ldan pas //
T02TD1676E:251b-47: rten gyi sbyor ba rang nyid bzhin //
T02TD1676E:252a-2: byin brlabs dbang bskur shis byas la //
T02TD1676E:252a-3: mchod dbul bstod cing gsol ba gdab //
T02TD1676E:252a-4: grangs kyi bzlas brjod rdzogs pa dang //
T02TD1676E:252a-5: tshogs bsags bsrung ba la rob gdon //
T02TD1676E:252a-6: sgrub pos gzungs bzlas mchod par bya //
T02TD1676E:252a-7: sbyor ba'i dkyil 'khor gsal rdzogs pas //
T02TD1676E:252a-8: chas gos rgyan chas rdzas bsag cing //
T02TD1676E:252a-10: phyi rol dgra btegs bdud dpung tshogs //
T02TD1676E:252a-11: nyon mongs rnam rtog nang gi las //
T02TD1676E:252a-13: bsam gtan rigs kyi cho ga ltar ;
T02TD1676E:252a-14: / yang dag brtson pa mthu yis 'jig / sa chu me rlung 'byung sogs 'khrug / thams cad zhi ba'i gnas su 'gyur //
T02TD1676E:252a-15: las mchog khro bo'i sbyor bcas pas //
T02TD1676E:252a-16: gtor ma gos dang mar me zas //
T02TD1676E:252a-17: yungs kar thal chen sngags kyi mthugs //
T02TD1676E:252a-18: bgegs la bka' bsgo bskrad par bya ;
T02TD1676E:252a-19: / zhag bdun la sogs dus kyi mthar //
T02TD1676E:252a-20: sdig pa'i gzugs brnyan 'byung zhing spyang //
T02TD1676E:252a-21: me dang chu yis shis byas te //
T02TD1676E:252a-22: phyi nang las bzhin dag pa'i phyir //
T02TD1676E:252a-23: ming rus dag la gtan gzhag cing //
T02TD1676E:252a-24: sngags kyi chu yis khrus byas te //
T02TD1676E:252a-25: dri mchog me tog bzang ldan dang//
T02TD1676E:252a-26: gsang sngags 'khor los gnas kun brgyan //
T02TD1676E:252a-27: dbang po'i sgo rnams byin brlabs nas //
T02TD1676E:252a-28: gos byas phreng ba gdags par bya //
T02TD1676E:252a-29: dkyil 'khor gnas su rim pa bzhin //
T02TD1676E:252a-30: 'jug pa'i cho ga tshul bzhin du //
T02TD1676E:252a-31: gsang ba'i sngags blo ldan pa yis //
T02TD1676E:252a-32: ro la mchod rdzas cho ga rdzogs//
T02TD1676E:252a-33: dkyil 'khor chen por rigs dbang sogs //
T02TD1676E:252a-34: bya ba'i cho ga skabs kyi don //
T02TD1676E:252a-35: 'khor lo rdzogs pa'i gnas brtsams pas //
T02TD1676E:252a-36: bsreg khang rigs mchog pho brang du //
T02TD1676E:252a-37: ma lus dkyil 'khor gnyis med rdzogs //
T02TD1676E:252a-38: ye shes dkyil 'khor dgug gzhug bstim //
T02TD1676E:252a-39: rnal 'byor grogs sogs rgyan bcas pas //
T02TD1676E:252a-40: bza' btung rgyan dang bgo ba rnams //
T02TD1676E:252a-41: byin brlabs rim gyis lhar gsal zhing //
T02TD1676E:252a-42: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod chen dbul //
T02TD1676E:252a-43: las sngags mtha' rgyan 'brel pa'i mthus //
T02TD1676E:252a-44: stong gsum 'gro gnas spyang bar bya //
T02TD1676E:252b-0: me lha mnyes pas las rdzogs @252b te ;
T02TD1676E:252b-1: / dngos grub 'dod don gsol ba gdab //
T02TD1676E:252b-2: mnyam nyid mi g-yos bstod byas nas //
T02TD1676E:252b-3: smon lam rgya mtsho don mthar dbyung //
T02TD1676E:252b-4: dkyil 'khor rnam gsum rdzogs byas pas //
T02TD1676E:252b-5: bde chen byang chub sems nyid sku //
T02TD1676E:252b-6: sngags kyis dag pa'i sku gdung rnams //
T02TD1676E:252b-7: sku gsung thugs ldan phyag rgya che //
T02TD1676E:252b-8: bskal par mi gnas phyag rgya rdzogs //
T02TD1676E:252b-9: rgyan sogs mchod pas mnyes par bya //
T02TD1676E:252b-10: rdo rje sems dpa' dpal sbyor ba //
T02TD1676E:252b-11: ji ltar gzugs dang dbyibs ldan pas //
T02TD1676E:252b-12: dur khrod lha yig nas rnams dang //
T02TD1676E:252b-13: ma mo'i gnas kyi thal ba mchog / thams cad bral ba'i srung ba ni//
T02TD1676E:252b-14: thig le'am so so'i ris gsum bya //
T02TD1676E:252b-15: phyogs mtshams nam mkha' sa bcings na //
T02TD1676E:252b-16: srung ba kun gyi bla med pa'o //
T02TD1676E:252b-18: lha rdzas zhi ba'i chu mchog gis //
T02TD1676E:252b-19: gtor ba dang ni blugs pa dang //
T02TD1676E:252b-20: khrus byas pa dang phog pa yis //
T02TD1676E:252b-21: phyogs mtshams nam mkha' sa bcings na //
T02TD1676E:252b-22: srung ba kun gyi bla med pa'o //
T02TD1676E:252b-23: mi yi thod pa'i nang du ni //
T02TD1676E:252b-24: yungs kar bskyed nas blang bar bya //
T02TD1676E:252b-25: bza' btung lus la byugs pa dang //
T02TD1676E:252b-26: phyogs bcur gtor bas bsrung bar 'gyur //
T02TD1676E:252b-27: dpa' bo gcig pa'i rten rnams kyis //
T02TD1676E:252b-28: sbyor ba gsum ldan srung ba'i mchog / de bzhin dkyil 'khor rgyas pas kyang //
T02TD1676E:252b-29: thams cad rgyas 'debs rdor sems mchog / sangs rgyas kun bdag sbyor ldan pas //
T02TD1676E:252b-30: phyogs bcu legs pa'i 'khor lo'i tshul //
T02TD1676E:252b-31: bla dang 'og tu byin brlabs nas //
T02TD1676E:252b-32: bsrungs pas sangs rgyas kun dgongs 'gyur //
T02TD1676E:252b-33: he ru dpal gyi rnams 'phrul pas //
T02TD1676E:252b-34: thams cad kun du kun gyi bdag / thams cad bsrung ba mi 'gyur che //
T02TD1676E:252b-35: mi mthun gdon sogs mod la zhi //
T02TD1676E:252b-38: 'bar bas blta ba'i tshul zhugs na //
T02TD1676E:252b-40: rdo rje khu tshur gnyis bcings nas //
T02TD1676E:252b-41: go cha bgo ba'i tshul du bya //
T02TD1676E:252b-42: 'di yis srung ba byas nas ni //
T02TD1676E:252b-43: rdo rje sems dpa' dpal dang 'dra //
T02TD1676E:252b-44: mi chod pa dang mi phyed pa'i //
T02TD1676E:252b-45: rdo rje'i sku ni rab tu 'grub //
T02TD1676E:252b-46: dus rnams kun du 'gro gzhan dag / bsod nams tshe 'phel longs spyod tshogs //
T02TD1676E:253a-1: bde gshegs 'khor lo sgyur rgyal stobs //
T02TD1676E:253a-2: lha dbang klu yi dbang sogs kyis //
T02TD1676E:253a-3: 'dod yon rin chen gter sogs dpal //
T02TD1676E:253a-4: lang tsho tshe dbang nad med bde //
T02TD1676E:253a-6: 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad rin chen phreng //
T02TD1676E:253a-7: mu khyud yi ge'i phreng bas mdzes //
T02TD1676E:253a-8: rigs mchog lha yi mtshan ma sngags //
T02TD1676E:253a-9: dkyil 'khor rgyas pa'i tshul du dgod //
T02TD1676E:253a-10: bsam bya bris shing bkod pa dag / byin brlabs brtan par 'gyur med gnas //
T02TD1676E:253a-11: chos sems pa yi tshul ston cing //
T02TD1676E:253a-12: rdo rje khu tshur gnyis dag dang //
T02TD1676E:253a-13: zhi sogs lta bas bltas na ni //
T02TD1676E:253a-14: rims du gnad kun rnams par sel //
T02TD1676E:253a-15: rdo rje khu tshur gnyis bcings nas //
T02TD1676E:253a-16: mthe'u chung lcags kyu lta bur sbrel //
T02TD1676E:253a-17: mdzub mo bsnyams pa'i rtse mo mnan //
T02TD1676E:253a-18: nad rnams thams cad zlog par byed //
T02TD1676E:253a-19: yongs su bsgyur te bteg nas su //
T02TD1676E:253a-20: dpral bar legs par gzhag par bya //
T02TD1676E:253a-21: ma lus lus pa med pa yi //
T02TD1676E:253a-22: sdug bsngal thams cad sel bar byed //
T02TD1676E:253a-23: rdo rje bsdams pa byas pa las //
T02TD1676E:253a-24: mdzum mo phan tshun mngon phyogs pa //
T02TD1676E:253a-25: zug rdu kun las grol 'gyur zhing //
T02TD1676E:253a-26: nad rnams kun gyi gnod pa med //
T02TD1676E:253a-27: grub pa dpal gyi spyan bcings nas //
T02TD1676E:253a-28: de yi phyir mig long bas mthong //
T02TD1676E:253a-29: sbyor ldan khu tshur dam pa yis //
T02TD1676E:253a-30: slad nas kha nas drang ste btung //
T02TD1676E:253a-31: de bzhin rims gnod dug rnams kun //
T02TD1676E:253a-32: sbyor ldan khu tshur tshul gyis btung //
T02TD1676E:253a-33: aom sarba ta th'a garbbha ta mis ho //
T02TD1676E:253a-34: 'di ni rna bar bzlas pa'i mchog zug rdu med cing 'bar ba'i mchog / lag g-yas sems dpa'i gtsug tor bcing //
T02TD1676E:253a-35: byis pa nad med bde bar bsrung //
T02TD1676E:253a-36: g-yas pa klu'i mgo gdengs ka brgya //
T02TD1676E:253a-38: dug gi las rnams 'dul byed de //
T02TD1676E:253a-39: 'chi ba'ang 'tsho bar byed pa'i mchog / g-yas pa'i mthe bo gung mo gnyis //
T02TD1676E:253a-40: g-yon pa'i khu tshur bcings pa yi //
T02TD1676E:253a-41: gung mo la ni reg byas te //
T02TD1676E:253a-42: gdon rnams kun las thal bar 'gyur //
T02TD1676E:253a-43: ba dan gsum po gnyis bcings nas //
T02TD1676E:253a-44: gung mo gnyis ni mdud par bcings //
T02TD1676E:253a-45: mdzub mo mthe'u chung rtse mo can //
T02TD1676E:253b-0: @253b rdo rje'i phyag rgya yongs bsgyur bteg / smin mtshams bzhag pas mkha' 'gro yi //
T02TD1676E:253b-1: las rnams ma lus lus med 'grub //
T02TD1676E:253b-2: sbyor ba sngags dang phyag rgya'i mthus //
T02TD1676E:253b-3: glang po bya rta 'gro ba'i tshogs //
T02TD1676E:253b-4: skyed tshal me tog ldu ma ra rnams //
T02TD1676E:253b-5: thams cad gso ba bla na med //
T02TD1676E:253b-6: thams cad bdag nyid kun sbyor ba'i //
T02TD1676E:253b-8: thun mong khams gsum las las byung //
T02TD1676E:253b-10: mchog gi phyag rgya ye shes sku //
T02TD1676E:253b-12: chags pa gnyis tshul longs spyad pas //
T02TD1676E:253b-14: khu tshur snying gar bcings pa ni //
T02TD1676E:253b-15: bud med phyag rgyar de bshad de //
T02TD1676E:253b-16: bud med sbyor ba ma lus pa //
T02TD1676E:253b-17: lus pa med pa thams cad 'grub //
T02TD1676E:253b-18: g-yon pa 'bying ba'i tshul du byas //
T02TD1676E:253b-19: lag g-yas bdag gi snying gar ni //
T02TD1676E:253b-20: gyen du drang ba'i tshul byas nas //
T02TD1676E:253b-21: bud med thams cad dbang du gyur //
T02TD1676E:253b-23: g-yon pa brdeg pa'i khu tshur dang //
T02TD1676E:253b-24: g-yas pa ldang ba 'grub pa dang //
T02TD1676E:253b-25: sangs rgyas dbang phyug ting 'dzin bya //
T02TD1676E:253b-26: g-yon pa dril bu sgra sgrogs shing //
T02TD1676E:253b-27: g-yas pa yi ni lag pa yis //
T02TD1676E:253b-28: rdo rje gyen du gsor zhing bskor //
T02TD1676E:253b-29: sgyu ma thams cad dbyung bar bya //
T02TD1676E:253b-30: lag pa g-yon pa brla la gzhag / lag pa g-yas pa'i mdzub mo yi //
T02TD1676E:253b-31: sbyor ba sngags kyi mdangs bcas pa //
T02TD1676E:253b-32: mi dge'i las rnams sel bar byed //
T02TD1676E:253b-33: bdag gi snying gar 'dren tshul du //
T02TD1676E:253b-34: g-yon pa nor bu rin chen 'dzin //
T02TD1676E:253b-35: g-yas nas de rdzogs rin chen bdun //
T02TD1676E:253b-36: bsam pa thams cad yongs rdzogs byed //
T02TD1676E:253b-37: bdag gi snying gar 'dren tshul du //
T02TD1676E:253b-39: g-yas pa rdo rje 'gying ba yis //
T02TD1676E:253b-40: dbang phyug dam pa thob par 'gyur //
T02TD1676E:253b-41: drag po'i las kyis 'dul mdzad pa'i //
T02TD1676E:253b-42: mtshon cha gsang sngags spu gris so //
T02TD1676E:253b-43: gnod gdug phyi nang dgra bgegs sogs //
T02TD1676E:253b-44: thal bar gyur pa'ang 'ching bar byed //
T02TD1676E:253b-45: mtshon cha lnga yi phyag rgya yis //
T02TD1676E:253b-47: dbyibs dang bde blag sbyor ba dang //
T02TD1676E:253b-48: kun du sbyor dang 'dren dang myur //
T02TD1676E:254a-2: dag po'i las rnams kun la sbyor //
T02TD1676E:254a-3: drag shul sbyor bas gnon pa yi //
T02TD1676E:254a-5: rkang pa brkyang dang gnon pa dang //
T02TD1676E:254a-6: bskum nas 'degs pa'i stabs dag gis //
T02TD1676E:254a-7: g-yas g-yon sbyor ba'i phyag rgya ches //
T02TD1676E:254a-8: gzugs rnams thams cad mnan par bya //
T02TD1676E:254a-9: sdig med stobs kyis ngo mngon du //
T02TD1676E:254a-11: byang chub pha rol phyin sogs dang //
T02TD1676E:254a-12: lha chen tshogs bcas mnan byas te //
T02TD1676E:254a-13: dga' sdug lha mo'i tshogs bcas dang //
T02TD1676E:254a-14: yon tan longs spyod spyad par bya'o //
T02TD1676E:254a-15: rdo rje snying po gzhan 'joms byed //
T02TD1676E:254a-16: phyir bzlog rnam par rgyal ba'i mthus //
T02TD1676E:254a-17: 'khor lo sngags phreng phyag rgya dang //
T02TD1676E:254a-18: sbyor ba kun gyis spro byed pas //
T02TD1676E:254a-19: nyam nga lag dang bde phyogs dang //
T02TD1676E:254a-20: thad ka de bzhin gyen du 'degs //
T02TD1676E:254a-21: 'di dag bzlog pa'i phyag rgya ste ;
T02TD1676E:254a-22: / gnas gsum dag ni bzlog par bya //
T02TD1676E:254a-23: mar ma bdud rtsi rdzas rnams kyis //
T02TD1676E:254a-24: dngos grub blangs nas lha rnams la //
T02TD1676E:254a-25: mchod bstod gtong rag bro gar dang //
T02TD1676E:254a-26: dga' ba'i 'gying bcas blang bar bya //
T02TD1676E:254a-27: smin ma mig dang so dang mchu //
T02TD1676E:254a-28: kha dang lus dang rkang lag gis //
T02TD1676E:254a-29: cha lugs bzhin du gar byed pas //
T02TD1676E:254a-30: phyag rgya yongs su grol ba yis //
T02TD1676E:254a-31: dkyil 'khor rgyas pa la dmigs nas //
T02TD1676E:254a-32: ye shes dkyil 'khor rim pa bzhin //
T02TD1676E:254a-33: rdzogs par phyung ste mdun bzhag nas //
T02TD1676E:254a-34: rim bzhin mchod bstod gshegs su gsol //
T02TD1676E:254a-35: phyag rgya sngags bcas tshigs bcad kyis //
T02TD1676E:254a-36: dgyes shing brtan par 'gro la gzigs //
T02TD1676E:254a-37: phyi rol ba rten gnas bcas //
T02TD1676E:254a-38: dam tshig dkyil 'khor rim bzhin bsdu //
T02TD1676E:254a-39: slar nyid bde ba chen po'i sku //
T02TD1676E:254a-40: thams cad phyag rgya yab yum gnas //
T02TD1676E:254a-41: dpal ldan g-yon pa 'gying dang bcas //
T02TD1676E:254a-42: dpal ldan lag pa g-yas pa yis //
T02TD1676E:254a-43: padmo khu tshur dpral bar bzhag / bdag gi mig ni gyen du blta //
T02TD1676E:254a-44: kam ham rin chen rgya gram gnyis //
T02TD1676E:254a-45: spyi bo snying ga'i gnas rnams spro //
T02TD1676E:254a-46: aom tum rdo rje khu tshur gyis //
T02TD1676E:254a-47: go cha bgos pa bcings par bya //
T02TD1676E:254a-48: spyi bo dang ni dpral ba gnyis //
T02TD1676E:254a-49: glo gnyis dang ni rgyab tu gnyis //
T02TD1676E:254a-50: rdo rje phreng bas bcings pa dang //
T02TD1676E:254b-0: sangs rgyas @254b gtsug gi nor bu dag / dar dpyangs tshul du bcings na ni //
T02TD1676E:254b-1: bsgyings dang bcas pas mtha' nas dgrol //
T02TD1676E:254b-2: dar dpyangs dkar dmar bzhi 'phur zhing //
T02TD1676E:254b-3: thal mo brdabs pas brtan par bya //
T02TD1676E:254b-4: rdzas rnams legs par bkrol nas kyang //
T02TD1676E:254b-5: rdul tshon chu bo chen por dor //
T02TD1676E:254b-6: ba yi rnam lngas legs byug cing //
T02TD1676E:254b-7: mchod rdzas rten sogs ci mang sbed //
T02TD1676E:254b-8: khro bo mchod bstod phur ba bton //
T02TD1676E:254b-9: bdud rtsis khrus gsol gzi byin bskyed //
T02TD1676E:254b-10: phyogs skyong rgyal po gsol bskyed mchod //
T02TD1676E:254b-11: mnyes byas zhi sems gshegs su gsol //
T02TD1676E:254b-12: rang gi lha yi sbyor ldan pas //
T02TD1676E:254b-13: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor bkang byas te //
T02TD1676E:254b-14: brda yi mtshams la sogs pa dgrol //
T02TD1676E:254b-15: srung mtshogs mchod gtor rang gtang //
T02TD1676E:254b-16: spyod lam ma nyams dkyil 'khor blos //
T02TD1676E:254b-17: mdzad spyod tshogs chen gnyis su brtag / bkra shis rgya chen gdon bya zhing //
T02TD1676E:254b-18: pha rol phyin sogs mchod sbyin bsgrags //
T02TD1676E:254b-19: mtshan rtog bdud rnams 'joms mdzad cing //
T02TD1676E:254b-20: bsnyen sgrub kun gyi don gsal sbyor //
T02TD1676E:254b-21: tshogs dbang dkyil 'khor las la mkhas //
T02TD1676E:254b-22: dngos grub gding ldan rgyal po bzhi //
T02TD1676E:254b-23: sku gsung thugs lam mnyams par //
T02TD1676E:254b-24: dus kun rgyun bzlas rgyun sbrel zhing //
T02TD1676E:254b-25: dngos kun sbyor ba'i las kun mkhas ;
T02TD1676E:254b-26: / gong ma'i gtsang 'chang rgyal theb las //
T02TD1676E:254b-27: mtshams bcad bskang so'i dngos spyang bsham //
T02TD1676E:254b-28: gtor dang las brtson mkha' 'gro bskang //
T02TD1676E:254b-29: bar skabs dkyil 'khor dbyibs gso mchod //
T02TD1676E:254b-30: thun mtshams bzlas brjod las rdo rje //
T02TD1676E:254b-31: spyan yangs lha gsal gsang sngags gdon //
T02TD1676E:254b-32: gus pas rtag tu lha mnyes brtson //
T02TD1676E:254b-33: grogs kyis bsgo ba'i las sbyin spyod //
T02TD1676E:254b-34: rtog bral gzung thub phyag rgya gsal //
T02TD1676E:254b-35: nges don zab mo'i gsang ba mchog / rim mam yang na cig car du //
T02TD1676E:254b-36: mchog gi rnal 'byor sbyangs pa'i mthus //
T02TD1676E:254b-37: tshe 'dis bde gshegs yul la sbyor //
T02TD1676E:254b-38: dka' ba kun gyis ma rnyed pa'i //
T02TD1676E:254b-39: dam pa'i nor bu rin po che //
T02TD1676E:254b-40: gang gi drin gyis bdag la rnyed //
T02TD1676E:254b-41: ya mtshan rmad byung ston pa'i gnas //
T02TD1676E:254b-42: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam sbyor ba //
T02TD1676E:254b-43: rnal 'byor dbang phyug bde chen po //
T02TD1676E:254b-44: 'di la khrus dang bsdams mi dgos //
T02TD1676E:255a-0: @255a * // dka' thub dka' ba spyad mi dgos //
T02TD1676E:255a-1: dka' thub sdom pa med pa dang //
T02TD1676E:255a-2: bde ba dang ni dga' bas 'grub //
T02TD1676E:255a-3: de bas ji ltar 'dod spyod cing //
T02TD1676E:255a-4: kun za de bzhin thams cad spyod //
T02TD1676E:255a-5: spyod pa ci dkar 'dod par byed //
T02TD1676E:255a-6: g-yo ba dag kyang ci dgar byed //
T02TD1676E:255a-7: langs pa dang ni 'dug pa dang //
T02TD1676E:255a-8: 'chag gam ji ltar gnas kyang rung //
T02TD1676E:255a-9: dgod dam rab tu smra ba dang //
T02TD1676E:255a-10: gang la ji ltar spyod kyang rung //
T02TD1676E:255a-11: dkyil 'khor du yang ma zhugs pa'am //
T02TD1676E:255a-12: sgrib pa kun dang ldan pa yang //
T02TD1676E:255a-13: rang gi lhar ni bdag sbyor na //
T02TD1676E:255a-16: thams cad 'grub par byed pas na //
T02TD1676E:255a-17: dan zos ngan spyod thams cad kyis //
T02TD1676E:255a-18: nyes pa dag tu yang mi 'gyur //
T02TD1676E:255a-19: bud med kun gyi sgyu ma'i rgya //
T02TD1676E:255a-20: 'di ni gnyis med theg pa'i mchog / sgyu ma dag ni thams cad pas //
T02TD1676E:255a-21: bud med sgyu ma khyad par che ;
T02TD1676E:255a-22: / ngo bo nyid kyi mthu dag dang //
T02TD1676E:255a-23: rang bzhin gyis ni de 'grub pa'o //
T02TD1676E:255a-25: gus par byed pa dag tu 'gyur //
T02TD1676E:255a-26: chags med chags dang bral ba min //
T02TD1676E:255a-27: dbu mar yang ni mi dmigs so //
T02TD1676E:255a-28: thams cad ma lus phyag rgya yi //
T02TD1676E:255a-29: thams cad ma lus bde mchog yin //
T02TD1676E:255a-30: byang chub sems ni rdo rje ste //
T02TD1676E:255a-31: sangs rgyas kun gyi bdag nyid yin //
T02TD1676E:255a-32: bde ba thams cad bdag sbyor bas //
T02TD1676E:255a-33: sangs rgyas thams cad thob par 'gyur //
T02TD1676E:255a-34: rdo rje sems dpa' bdag sbyor bas //
T02TD1676E:255a-35: dbab pa thams cad rab tu 'grub //
T02TD1676E:255a-36: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam sbyor ba //
T02TD1676E:255a-37: rnal 'byor dbang phyug bde ba'i mchog / de bas bde ba nyid kyi phyir //
T02TD1676E:255a-38: sangs rgyas bde ba kun thob bo //
T02TD1676E:255a-39: kun du kun nas thams cad ni //
T02TD1676E:255a-40: bdag nyid rtag tu rnam pa kun //
T02TD1676E:255a-41: sangs rgyas la sogs brtan g-yo kun / kun gyi dngos por bdag gyur to //
T02TD1676E:255a-42: sems dang sems dpa' ting 'dzin dang //
T02TD1676E:255a-43: byang chub spyod pa sna tshogs nyid //
T02TD1676E:255a-44: de bzhin bdud dang bdud las rgyal //
T02TD1676E:255a-45: de ni byang chub sangs rgyas yin //
T02TD1676E:255a-46: rdo rje rdo rje 'dzin nyid dang //
T02TD1676E:255a-48: nor bu nor bu 'dzin nyid dang //
T02TD1676E:255a-49: de dag gi yang rigs yin no //
T02TD1676E:255b-0: @255b dngos grub rlabs chen phrin las tshogs //
T02TD1676E:255b-1: grangs med rgya chen don spyod pas //
T02TD1676E:255b-2: bdag gzhan bya ba kun rdzogs par //
T02TD1676E:255b-3: ye shes 'khor lo tshogs chen sa //
T02TD1676E:255b-5: mchog gi bsnyen sgrub phyag rgya bzhi //
T02TD1676E:255b-6: zung 'jug gnyis med rdzogs pa'i mthus//
T02TD1676E:255b-7: dngos grub rgya chen zab mo mtshan //
T02TD1676E:255b-8: lha mo kun dang mnyam sbyor ba //
T02TD1676E:255b-9: skal bzang mchog ni 'dod pa ste //
T02TD1676E:255b-10: yang dag sbyor ba bde myong ba //
T02TD1676E:255b-11: 'dod chags ther zug brtan pa can //
T02TD1676E:255b-12: sangs rgyas kun gyi gzugs chen dang //
T02TD1676E:255b-13: dbyangs dang dri dang ro dag kyang //
T02TD1676E:255b-14: sangs rgyas kun gyi reg bya'i mchog / bdag gi spyad par de spyod do //
T02TD1676E:255b-15: dkyil 'khor rgya chen brtan pa'i blos //
T02TD1676E:255b-16: rigs mchog mnyes pa'i tshul la spyad //
T02TD1676E:255b-17: cung zad sbyor ba klog pa na //
T02TD1676E:255b-18: sgo gsum bsod nams tshogs 'gyur ba'i //
T02TD1676E:255b-19: pha rol phyin drug smon lam sogs //
T02TD1676E:255b-20: 'gro don spyod pa rgya chen brtsam //
T02TD1676E:255b-21: sangs rgyas kun gyi bdag nyid kyi //
T02TD1676E:255b-23: rdo rje sems dpa'i dpal tshe dang //
T02TD1676E:255b-24: lang tsho nad med bde mchog grub //
T02TD1676E:255b-25: kun du kun nas thams cad du //
T02TD1676E:255b-26: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam sbyor ba //
T02TD1676E:255b-27: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde ba'i mchog / rtag tu de ni 'grub par 'gyur //
T02TD1676E:255b-28: 'di yis sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
T02TD1676E:255b-29: dpa' bo rnams dang thams cad dang //
T02TD1676E:255b-30: rdo rje 'dzin pa thams cad du //
T02TD1676E:255b-32: bdag don mi gnas mya ngan 'das //
T02TD1676E:255b-33: rigs drug dkyil 'khor rgya chen dang //
T02TD1676E:255b-34: gzhan don 'jig rten bde longs spyod //
T02TD1676E:255b-35: lha chen kun gyi rgyal srid tshogs //
T02TD1676E:255b-36: thams cad mar mdzad dbang bsgyur zhing //
T02TD1676E:255b-37: 'dod don gzhan la spyir par mdzad //
T02TD1676E:255b-38: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' yang //
T02TD1676E:255b-39: phrogs nas kyang ni sbyin mdzad na //
T02TD1676E:255b-40: las mchog dag ni rab 'byams dang //
T02TD1676E:255b-41: dngos grub gzhan lta smos ci dgos //
T02TD1676E:255b-42: mdzas spyod mtha' yas sngags tshul dag / las dang 'bras bu'i rjes 'gro byed //
T02TD1676E:255b-43: yan lag bzhi yi don snang ba //
T02TD1676E:255b-45: rten gyi sgrub pa snang ba bzhi //
T02TD1676E:255b-46: bsnyen sgrub phyag rgya lam rim dang //
T02TD1676E:255b-47: sa yi khyad par dngos grub 'bras //
T02TD1676E:255b-48: phrin las bzhi snang bcu drug tshogs //
T02TD1676E:256a-1: ba bla na med pa'i tshul //
T02TD1676E:256a-2: sum cu rtsa gnyis brgya nyi shu //
T02TD1676E:256a-3: rtsa brgyad yang dag grub pa'i gzhung //
T02TD1676E:256a-4: sgrub gzhung rgyas 'bring bsdus pa dang //
T02TD1676E:256a-5: shin tu bsdus pa'i ngang tshul can //
T02TD1676E:256a-6: go rims gnas skabs dbye bar shes //
T02TD1676E:256a-7: thog mar sgrub blo phun tshogs pas //
T02TD1676E:256a-8: rten gyi yan lag bzhi ldan 'jug / tshogs bsags rnal 'byor sbyor rnal 'byor //
T02TD1676E:256a-10: rim bzhin goms pa gsal ba'i sgo //
T02TD1676E:256a-11: dang por sbyor dang brtan pa dang //
T02TD1676E:256a-12: yang dag ye shes rnam par grol //
T02TD1676E:256a-13: mtshan ma rtags kyis goms byas pa'i //
T02TD1676E:256a-14: bcu drug 'jug pa'i bye brag gis //
T02TD1676E:256a-15: theg chen nyes don zung sdud sbyor //
T02TD1676E:256a-16: 'gro drug rang rgyud brtags pa'i tshul //
T02TD1676E:256a-17: theg dman snang ba phyogs gcig pa //
T02TD1676E:256a-18: blo gros zab mo rgya chen don //
T02TD1676E:256a-20: snang ba tshul mthun khyad par can //
T02TD1676E:256a-21: rnam pa'i chags bsal mtha' las grol //
T02TD1676E:256a-22: nyams myang rim gyis zhen chags bral //
T02TD1676E:256a-23: snang ba bzhi las bcu drug tshogs //
T02TD1676E:256a-24: bdag nyid gzhan tshogs gnyis kar 'brel //
T02TD1676E:256a-25: chags sdang btang snyoms tshul gyis 'jug / sdug bsngal kun 'byung 'gog lam dang //
T02TD1676E:256a-27: bden gnyis rnam shes bden brdzun brtag / sgyu ma gnyis su med pa'i dngos //
T02TD1676E:256a-29: zung 'jug bde ba chen po'i dbyings //
T02TD1676E:256a-30: sku gsum mdzad pa mdzad pa yis //
T02TD1676E:256a-31: theg pa'i snang ba ma 'gags pa'o //
T02TD1676E:256a-32: bsnyen pa las la sbyor byas nas //
T02TD1676E:256a-33: nye bsnyen gsal bar gyur pa las //
T02TD1676E:256a-34: sgrub pa snga ma'i gnas 'gyur te //
T02TD1676E:256a-35: sgrub chen 'bras bu la spyod pa'o //
T02TD1676E:256a-36: rim 'jug bsnyen sgrub bcu gnyis kyis //
T02TD1676E:256a-37: dkyil 'khor rgya chen gnas sbyor zhing //
T02TD1676E:256a-38: zung 'jug bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhis //
T02TD1676E:256a-39: zab mo'i dkyil 'khor gsal bar snang //
T02TD1676E:256a-40: tshad med phyag rgya dman pa'i rgya //
T02TD1676E:256a-41: gsang ba'i phyag rgya mchog gi rgyas //
T02TD1676E:256a-42: gsal 'debs rgyal po mchog gi sku //
T02TD1676E:256a-43: bzhi yis bcu drug rdzogs byed pa'o //
T02TD1676E:256a-44: dang po sku gsal brtan pa dang //
T02TD1676E:256a-45: dam tshig ye shes gnyis med mnyes //
T02TD1676E:256a-46: sku gsung thugs mchog byin brlabs mthus //
T02TD1676E:256b-0: bde gshegs @256b rigs mchog ye shes sbyor //
T02TD1676E:256b-1: thabs kyis rgya che lam bgrod cing //
T02TD1676E:256b-2: shes rab zab mo'i lam la 'jug / zung du 'brel pas phyag rgya'i lam //
T02TD1676E:256b-3: gnyis med bgrod pa'i lam mchog yin //
T02TD1676E:256b-4: rgyu rkyen gnyis med tshogs gnyis rdzogs //
T02TD1676E:256b-5: tshul bzhis bcu drug lam du 'gyur //
T02TD1676E:256b-6: tshogs drug rnam par sbyor ba yis //
T02TD1676E:256b-7: yon tan tshogs rdzogs don gsal sa //
T02TD1676E:256b-8: rig 'dzin sangs rgyas sa yi mthar //
T02TD1676E:256b-9: bzhi las bdun drug brgyad du snang //
T02TD1676E:256b-10: rgyu 'bras dbyi bas bcu drug tshogs //
T02TD1676E:256b-11: rim sbyar cig car thob pa'i tshul //
T02TD1676E:256b-12: mos spyod lam la sbyor ba dang //
T02TD1676E:256b-13: sar chud las la spyod pa dang //
T02TD1676E:256b-14: rnam smin phyag rgya chen po dang //
T02TD1676E:256b-15: bya ba mthar phyin sangs rgyas sa //
T02TD1676E:256b-17: de nas sangs rgyas sa drug rdzogs //
T02TD1676E:256b-18: 'jig rten thun mong bdag don dang //
T02TD1676E:256b-19: gzhan don mchog 'gyur dngos grub bzang //
T02TD1676E:256b-20: bdag gzhan las snang sgo bzhi nas //
T02TD1676E:256b-21: bcu drug tshogs la longs spyod mdzad //
T02TD1676E:256b-22: mkha' 'gro tshogs med stobs ldan zhing //
T02TD1676E:256b-23: mi mthun rkyen gyis 'jig pa med //
T02TD1676E:256b-24: ral gri mig sman rkang mgyogs bum //
T02TD1676E:256b-25: bdud rtsi'i bcud len rig 'dzin gser //
T02TD1676E:256b-26: sku gsung thugs sogs mi 'jigs stobs //
T02TD1676E:256b-27: phra zhing khyab mdzad dpal gyi gzhi //
T02TD1676E:256b-28: kun du brtan pas bdag gzhan don //
T02TD1676E:256b-29: zhi rgyas dbang dang mngon spyod rdzogs //
T02TD1676E:256b-30: phrin las bzhi spyod bcu drug tshogs //
T02TD1676E:256b-32: mnyes shing srung mdzad btang dang grol //
T02TD1676E:256b-33: gso ba stobs 'phel rgyal byed brtan //
T02TD1676E:256b-34: dgug cing rengs shing rmongs pa dang //
T02TD1676E:256b-35: dbye mnan bskrad dang pham byed pa'o //
T02TD1676E:256b-36: dam pas rgyud don rgya chen tshogs //
T02TD1676E:256b-37: pad mdzes nyi mas rgyas ltar byas //
T02TD1676E:256b-38: bde mchog mkha' 'gro'i don bstan las //
T02TD1676E:256b-39: khyad par lhag pa gzhan du med //
T02TD1676E:256b-40: de nyid cung zhing gsal ba'i phyir //
T02TD1676E:256b-42: rtogs par sla don mtha' gnyis bral //
T02TD1676E:256b-43: mkha' 'gro'i tshogs rnams bzod par mdzod //
T02TD1676E:256b-44: kun mchog rgya chen dri med dge //
T02TD1676E:256b-45: ston ka'i zla gsal sgrib bral ltar //
T02TD1676E:256b-46: 'gro kun sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
T02TD1676E:257a-0: mnyam par sbyor ba'i gnas thob shog / yan lag bzhi'i don @257a * //
T02TD1676E:257a-1: snang bar byed pa zhes bya ba slob dpon mkhas shing dngos grub brnyes pa h'um mdzad grags pas mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD1676E:257a-3: // / mnga' bdag btsan po byang chub sems dpa'i bkas dpal bsam yas kyi 'chim phu ru dkyil 'khor chen po'i slob dpon pandi ta dpal rdo rje bzhad pa dang //
T02TD1676E:257a-4: sgra bsgyur gyi lo ts'a ba chen po rma rin chen mchog gis dbang sgrub dang bcas par bsgyur cing bshad nas gtan la phab ba'o//
